Moi eitu karone apuni ke Crete te chari jaise, manu khan ke thik koribole, sobcity te bura khan ke girja laga solawta kori rakhi dibole pothaise.
Aru solawta khan to golti nathaka hobo lage, aru ekta maiki laga mota, aru bacha khan bhi adat beya aru kotha namana eneka nohobo lage.
