karone bisi manu khan, missa koi thogi thaka, aru utu khan sunnot kora khan ke ase
Heitu khan laga mukh bondho kori debo lage, utu khan he sorom laga kamai pabo bhabi kena ji nuhua kotha koi aru sikhai kena ghor-ghor ke nimila kore thake.
Taikhan te ekjon prophets asele koi rekhise, Crektans manu to sabdin missa koi thaka aru satan laga janwar aru alsi khakua ase
