Sapha khan nimite hole sob bostu sapha ase, kintu sapha-nathaka aru biswas nokora khan nimite hole eku be sapha nohoi, taikhan laga dimak aru bhabona te bhi sob letra ase.
Taikhan Isor ke jane koi, kintu kam te hole taike nohobo koi kelemane, taikhan kotha nahuna aru namana aru bhal kam karone thik nohoi.
Kintu apuni, ki kotha koi itu tu biswas laga kotha hobo lage.
Bura manu ke gusa na-uthi kena, biswas morom namro para thakibole sikhai dibi.
Buri maiki khan Isor ke kenika mani thakibo, golti nathaka aru modu nakhai kene aru ke tu bhal ase utu sikhabo aru Isor ke sanman kuribo.
Eitu nishena jawan maiki ke tai laga mota aru bacha ke keneka morom kuribo eitu sikhai dibi,
Aru nijor mota laga kotha mani thakibo, sapa hoi nijor ghor kam te bhal thaka, tenehloe pobitro kitab hinsa nohobo.
Aru eitu nishina jawan manu ke bhal kam kuribole samjai debe.
Apuni laga sob kam te bhal he dikhai dibi. Aru apuni ki sikhai ase eitu hosa aru safa para kua kotha hobo lage.
