Aru tai moi laga ekjon chokora hobo”?
Kintu aru jetiya Isor poila jonom kora bachha ke duniya te ane, Tar koi, “Sob Isor laga duth khan Tar ke mohima koribi.”
Aru sorgoduth khan ke Tar pora koi,
“Tar he ekjon ase kun he sorgoduth laga aatma khan ke bonai,
Aru Tar laga sewak khan ke juie laga agh ke bonai.”
Kintu Tar laga Chokora ke koi,
“Tumi laga sinhasan Isor, hodai nimite ase.
Apuni laga raijyo tu dhramik ase aru apuni thik niyom pora he manu khan ke bichar kore.
Apuni bhal kaam he khusi pai aru kanun laga niyom nathaka ke ghin kore.
Etu nimite Isor, apuni laga Isor, apuni ke khusi laga tel dhali kene basi loise
Aru etu apuni logote thaka khan pora bhi bisi dangor ahse.”
“Shuru te, Probhu, apuni prithibi bonai se.
Aru sorgo tu apuni laga hath laga kaam ase.
Tai khan harai jabo, kintu apuni hodai thakibo.
Apuni tai khan ke kapur bandhi diya nisina kori dibo,
Aru tai khan kapur bodli kori kene rakhi diya nisina thaki jabo.
Kintu apuni eke ase,
Aru apuni laga din aru sal ketiya bhi khotom nohobo.”
Kintu kun tu homoi te Isor Tar laga duth khan ke eneka koisile,
“Moi laga dyna hath te bohibi
Jetiya tak moi tumi laga dusman khan ke tumi laga theng nichete narakhe”?
Sewa kori thaka kiman sorgoduth khan ase tai khan aatma nohoi, aru manu khan poritran pabole khan ke sai dibole nimite pothai dise nohoi?
Etu nimite moi khan ki hunise etu bhal pora buji lobole lage, eneka korile moi khan biya rasta te najabo.
Jodi etu kotha khan kun tu sorgoduth pora koise aru etu kotha khan sob thik ase koi kene janise, aru kun manu biya rasta te jai aru kotha namane tai khan sajai pabo koi kene janise,
tetiya hoile iman dangor poritran laga kotha jodi amikhan ninda korile, amikhan keneka polabo paribo? Etu jibon laga kotha tu aghe te Probhu pora moi khan ke janai dise aru kun manu hunise etu thik ahse koi kene moi khan ke jani bole dise.
Isor bhi etu kotha khan laga sob gawahi dise, alag-alag chin khan pora, asurit kaam pora, aru Tar laga echa hisabte sob ke Pobitro Aatma laga alag-alag vardan dise.
Isor pora sorgoduth khan ke prithibi te ki hobole ase etu khan kuwa nai, etu kun tu kotha moi khan etiya koi ase.
Kintu, kunba pora kunba jagate gawahi dise aru koise,
“Manu ki ase, ki Tar nimite apuni eman bhabana kori ase?
Nohoile manu laga bacha, apuni jun nimite eman chinta kori ahse?
Apuni manu ke sorgoduth pora olop he niche kori dise;
apuni tai ke mohima aru sonman laga mukut lagai dise.
Apuni Tar laga theng nichete sob kaam khan rakhi dise.” Aru sob Tar laga nichete thaki jaise, Isor pora Tar laga nichete rakhi nadiya eku nai. Kintu moi khan etiya bhi bisi kaam Tar laga nichete ahhi kene nai koi kene dikha nai.
Kintu moi khan Jisu ke dikhise, kun ke sorgoduth laga nichete olop din nimite rakhise, mohima aru sonman laga mukut lagai dise, Tai dukh aru kosta korikene moribole, etu pora he Isor laga anugrah pora Tar sob nimite moribo.
Kelemane, Tar kun karone sob jinis tu ahse, aru kun pora sob jinis ulabole dise, bisi putro khan ke mohima te ahnibole, dukh kosto pora taikhan laga poritran laga cholawta ke mohima te ahnibole, Tar he yogya thakise.
Kelemane kun pora sapha kori diye aru kun sapha hoi jai tai khan sob tu eke ase. Etu nimite, Tar pora tai khan ke bhai mati bole nimite sorom nakhai.
Tar koi,
“Moi tumi khan laga naam bhai khan majote koi dibo,
Moi manu majot pora tumi khan nimite gana koribo.”
