Arubi,
“Sabi, moi yate ase aru moi laga bachha khan bhi ase kun ke Isor pora moi ke dise.”
Etu nimite, bacha khan kun moi laga gaw aru khun te bhag loise, tai moi lagote bhag ase, etu pora tai mora ke jiti lobo aru Tar laga mora pora jinda huwa laga takot te bhag thakibo, aru, saitan ke harai dibo.
Aru etu khan sob tu mora laga bhoi pora tai khan laga pura jibon bandhi kene thakise etu manu khan ke azad kori dibo.
Tar sorgo te thaka duth khan nimite chinta kora nai; kintu, Abraham laga bacha khan nimite chinta ase.
Etu karone sob kaam te Tar laga bhai khan nisina hobole nimite dorkar thakise, aru etu pora Tar ekjon dayalu aru bisasi moha purohit hobo aru Isor laga ki kaam ase etu sob pura koribo, aru manu laga sob paap tu sapha kori dibo.
Aru kelemane Tar nijor bhi dukh paise aru porikha korise, Tar kun manu porikha te giri ase tai ke madot koribole paribo.
Etu nimite, pobitro bhai khan, apuni khan sorgo raijyo te bhag hobole matise. Jisu ke bhabibi, jun ase moi khan pora shikar kora laga pasonir aru moha purohit.
Tar ke kun pora basi loise kaam koribole nimite Tar hodai bisas pora kotha mani kene thakise, jeneka Moses pora Isor laga ghor te hodai bisasi hoi kene thakise.
Kelemane Moses pora bhi dangor sonman aru mahima Tar laga ase, jeneka ekta ghor pora bhi etu ghor bona manu laga bisi sonman aru mahima thake.
Kelemane ghor tu kunba pora bonai kene thake, kintu etu ekjon kun sob bonaise Tar Isor ase.
Moses bhi Isor laga pura ghor te bisasi ekjon sewak thakise, etu kotha laga gawahi khan kun ahhi bole laga din te hobole ahse etu kobole nimite.
Kintu Khrista ekta bisaskorta Putro ahse kun Isor laga ghor pura tu sai ahse. Moi khan Tar laga ghor ahse aru jodi moi khan ke ki akha te matise etu te phutani kori kene mon dangor pora dhuri thaki ahse koile.
Etu nimite, Pobitro Aatma pora bhi eneka koise:
“Ajhi, jodi apuni Tar laga awaj hune
Mon tan nokoribi ,
Aru beya kaam nokoribi,
Jongol te thaka homoi te porikha kori kene sa nisina.
Tumi khan laga baba khan pora moi ke porikha kori kene kotha mana nai,
Tai khan moi ki kaam korise etu sob dikhise
chalis sal tak. Etu nimite moi manu khan uporte khusi thaka nai.
Moi koise, ‘Tai khan hodai mon pora biya kaam kori kene jai,
Aru tai khan moi pora bhal rasta dikhai diya tu najane.’
Moi laga ghusa pora kosom kha nisina he ahse:
‘Moi thaka aru aram kora jaga te tai khan ketiya bhi jabo naparibo.’”
Hosiyar hoi jabi, bhai khan, apuni khan laga mon te bisas nokora laga biya bhabona nahibole nimite, kun tu pora apuni ke jinda Isor pora dur loi jai.
Kelemane moi khan Khrista laga kaam te sathi hoi jaise jodi moi khan shuru pora antim tak Tar logote bisasi hoi kene thake.
Etu khan nimite koi dise,
“Ahji, jodi apuni Tar laga awaj hune,
apuni laga mon tan nokoribi,
aru biya rasta te najabi.”
Kelemane kun huni kene kotha mananai? Tai khan sob ke Moses pora he Egypt pora ulai kene ahnanai naki?
Aru kun logote Tar chalis sal tak khong uthi kene thakise? Paap kora manu khan logote nohoi naki, kun laga mora gaw tu jongol te giri kene thakise?
Aru kun logote Tar kosom khaisile tai khan Tar laga aram kora jaga te ghusi bole naparibo koi kene, kun manu kotha namani kene ase tai khan ke nohoile aru etu kotha kun ke koisile?
Moi khan dikhise bisas nathaka nimite tai khan tate ghusi bole paranai.
Etu nimite, moi khan bhoi kori kene thakibo jetiya tak Isor laga kosom moi khan logote ahse aram laga jaga te ghusi bole paribo nimite, jodi kunba manu tate ponchibole napara hoise eneka nahobole nimite.
Kelemane tai khan ke koi diya nisina moi khan ke bhi bhal khobor tu koi dise. Kintu ki kotha koi dise etu pora tai khan nimite eku laab huwa nai, kelemane kun manu bisas pora hunise tai khan logote mon mili kene thaka nai.
Kelemane moi khan kun bisas korise aram laga jaga te ghusi bole parise, Tar pora kuwa nisina,
“Moi laga ghusa te kosom kha nisina,
Tar khan moi laga aram jaga te ketiya bhi ghusibole naparibo.”
Aru jodi bhi, shristi shuru kora homoi pora Tar laga kaam sob pura kori dise.
Kelemane Tar kunba jaga te sath din laga kotha tu koi dise:
“Aru Isor bhi sob kaam kori kena sath din te aram kori sile.”
Aru bhi eneka likha ase,
“Tai khan moi laga aram kora jaga te ghusi bole naparibo.”
Etu karone, tate ghusi bole para kunba aru bhi ase, aru kunba manu susamachar tu hunise hoilebhi tai khan kotha namana nimite tate ghusi bole paranai.
Isor pora aru ekta din ke eneka mati dise “Ahji.” Bisi din pichete,Tar David logote kotha korise, aghe te kuwa nisina,
“Ahji jodi tumi Tar laga awaj hunile,
apuni laga mon tan nokoribi.”
Aru jodi Joshua pora tai khan ke aram dise koile, etu pichete Isor pora aru bhi alag din laga kotha nokobole thakise.
Etu nimite ahji bhi Isor laga manu khan nimite Tar laga din mani bole karone rakhi dise.
Kelemane kun Tar laga aram jaga te ghusi bole parise tai nijor ke sob kaam pora aram pai loise, jeneka Isor Tar laga kaam pora aram loisile.
Kelemane Isor laga kotha tu jinda ahse aru dui phale dhar thakar talwar nisina kaam kore. Duita aatma aru jibon bhitorte bhi ghusi kene, jurai aru hardi khan ke bhag koribo pare, aru manu laga mon te ki bhabona ahse etu sob bhi janibole pare.
Isor aghe shristi te bona bostu khan kot-te bhi lukabole napare. Kintu, sob khula-khuli ase aru Tar ke amikhan hisab dibole lage.
Etu nimite, moi khan logote dangor moha purohit ase kun sorgo tu par kori kene ahise, Jisu kun Isor laga Chokora ase, etu nimite moi khan laga bisaskhan tu dhori kene rakhibo.
Kelemane moi khan laga komjor bujibole napara laga moha purohit nai, kintu amikhan pora dukh pa nisina, Tar ekjon ase kun ke porikha korisile, Tar laga eku paap nathakilebhi.
Etu nimite ahhibi, moi khan mon dangor korikene Tar laga anugraha thaka sinhasan usorte jabo, eneka korile moi khan daya pabo aru dukh homoi te modot koribole anugrah pabo.
Kelemane sob moha purohit tu, manu khan majot pora he basi loi, Isor laga kotha aru kaam khan koi kene janai dibole nimite basi loi, etu pora Tar tai khan ke GIFTS aru paap laga bolidan dibo.
Kun manu najani kene thaki ahse aur beya rasta te berai ahse tai khan ke morom pora loi kene ahni bole nimite, kelemane Tai bhi komzur ase.
Etu nimite,Tar paap laga bolidan dibole lagise, Tar manu khan nimite keneka korise, etu nisina nijor nimite bhi korise.
Tar nijor nimite kunba ke etu sonman lobole diya nai. Kintu Tar ke Isor pora mati loise, jeneka Aaron ke mati loisele.
Thik etu nisina, Khrista pora Tar nijor ke moha purohit bonai kene sonman kora nai. Kintu, etu ekjon kun kotha korise Tar pora koise,
“Tumi moi laga Putro ahse; ahji moi Tumi laga Baba hoise.”
Eitu nisina dusra jaga te bhi koi kena ase,
“Tumi hodai nimite purohit ase
Melchizedek laga pichete te.”
Gaw mangso pora thaka homoi te, Khrista pora Tar laga prathana aru binti kandi kene aru suku pani ulai kene Tar ke bacha bole pora ekjon ke mora pora bachai dibole nimite koise, aru Tar laga prathana hunise kelemane Tar bhal jibon thakise.
Aru Tar Isor laga bacha thakilebhi, keneka kotha manibo lage, etu Tar laga dukh pora Tar shikise.
Tar sob pora bhal hoi jaise, aru kun manu Tar laga kotha mani kene thake, tai khan nimite sorgo te jabole laga rasta hoi jaise.
Tar ke Isor pora moha purohit bonai dise Melchizedek pora kuwa nisina.
Moi khan etu nimite aru bisi kobole ase, kintu sob bujai dibole nimite tan ahse kelemane etu kotha khan sob huni kene bhi tumi khan nahuna manu nisina hoi jaise.
Kelemane etiya laga homoi te tumi khan shikai diya manu hobole lagise, hoilebi tumi khan ke Isor laga ki kotha ahse etu khan shikai dibole lagi ase. Tumi khan tan bhat khabo nohoi kene, etiya bhi dudh he khai ase!
Kelemane kun etiya bhi dudh khai ase tai Isor laga dharmik kotha te komjor ase, kelemane tai etiya bhi chutu bacha ase.
Kintu tan bhat tu dangor manu khan nimite ase, kelemane tai khan bhal aru biya tu ki ase etu khan sob bhal pora jani kene shiki loise.
Etu nimite, Khrista laga shuru kotha ki asele, etu ke chari kene dangor hoija manu khan nisina aghe te jabo. Mora kaam khan pora ghurabole laga aru Isor ke bisas koribole laga kotha laga FOUNDATION aru nabonabo,
baptisma laga kotha shikai diya nisina, manu uporte hath rakha khan, mora khan ponuruthan hoi ja khan, aru anonto bichar laga kotha khan.
Moi khan etu khan bhi koribo jodi Isor pora etu koribole nimite moi khan ke koi.
Kelemane kun manu poila etu khan jani loise, kun khan sorgo laga asirbad jani loise aru Pobitro Aatma te bhag ase,
hoile bhi kun giri jaise- tai khan aru bhi mon ghura bole tu tan ahse. Kelemane tai khan nijor nimite aru bhi Isor laga Putro ke crus te morai dise, aru Tar ke manu usorte sorom khelai dise.
Kelemane etu mati pani gira homoi te pani tu khai loi, aru etu mati pora bhal kheti ulai, aru etu pora Isor laga bhal asirbad tu pai loi.
Kintu kun tu mati te kata aru jongol ulai etu mati kaam nai aru tai shrap dibole ahse. Aru jolabole nimite he hoi jai.
Kintu moi khan apuni khan nimite bhal kaam koribole nimite bhabona chinta kori ase, morom te thaka khan, anonto jibon laga ki kotha ase jodi bhi moi khan eneka pora koi ase.
Kelemane Isor to unyai kora Isor nohoi, apuni laga kaam kora khan aru Tar laga naam ke apuni pora morom kora tu pahori najabo, apuni Tar laga dharmik manu khan ke sewa kora aru etiya bhi tai khan laga sewa kori thaka nisina.
Moi khan laga etu he sob pora dangor echa ase apuni antim tak eneka kori thakibo, etu pora apuni laga akha thik rakhibole nimite.
Etu khan sob tu apuni alchi nokoribole nimite ase, kintu aatma te thaka manu khan laga bisas aru mon chutu kori kene thaka tu sai kene apuni bhi Isor pora ki kosom dise etu laga bhag hobo.
Jetiya Isor pora Abraham logote kosom disele,Tar nijor ke loi kene kosom dise, kelemane Tar pora upor te thaka laga kosom khabole nimite aru kun bhi nai.
Tar koise, “Moi tumi ke asirbad koribo, aru moi tumi ke bisi dangor bonai dibo.”
Etu nisina he, Abraham dorjo kori kene roki thaka nisina Isor pora tai ke ki kosom disele etu tai paise.
Kelemane manu khan tu kun taikhan nijor pora dangor ase taikhan laga naam loi kene he kosom khai. Etu pora he tai khan majote mon nimili kene thaka tu khotom hoi jai, kosom diya tu hoile ekjon uporte bharosa kori bole nimite kuwa nisina ahse.
Jetiya Isor pora Tar laga manu khan nimite ki kosom dise etu eku bodla-bodli nai koikene sapha pora dikhai dibole nimite korise, Tar etu kosom tu ji hoilebi pabo koikene vachan dise.
Tar duita bodli koribole napara laga kaam pora eneka korise- Isor tu ketiya bhi misa kotha nokoi- moi khan, kun lukabole nimite polai jaisile, Tar pora moi khan ke ki akha dise tate mon dangor hoikene thik pora dhuri rakhi bo nimite.
Moi khan etu akha thaka tu moi khan laga aatma ke nahila jagate rakhibole aru bharosa thaka jaga te rakhibo nimite ase, kun tu purdah laga bhitor jaga te bhi ghusi bole pare,
kot-te Jisu, kun moi khan laga aghe te jaise, Tar moi khan laga bodli etu jaga te jaise. Tar ekta moha purohit hoi jaise hodai nimite Melchizedek purohit laga hisab nisina.
Etu nimite Melchizedek, Salem laga raja, Isor laga Moha Purohit, jetiya Abraham raja khan ke khotom kori kene ahhi thakise tai ke lok paise aru asirbad korise.
Abraham bhi tai laga dos bhag sob tu tai ke di dise. Tai laga poila nam laga matlab tu hoile “dharmic laga raja,” aru bhi “Salem laga raja,” etu motlob tu hoile, “shanti laga raja.”
Tai laga baba thaka nai, aru ama bhi nai, tai laga eku khandan nai, tai nimite tai jibon laga shuru aru jibon laga anth bhi nai. Kintu, Isor laga Putro nisina bonai dise, tai hodai nimite ekta purohit thakise.
Kintu sabi etu manu kiman dangor thakise, Abraham pora lorai kori kene ki jitise aru loi loise etu laga dos bhag tai ke di dise.
Aru Levi laga chokora khan kun ke purohit kori bole nimite bachi loise tai khan ke kanun laga niyom hisab te jai kene manu khan logote daan aru dos bhag utha bole nimite dise, etu hoile, tai khan laga bhai khan logote, jodi bhi tai khan Abraham laga gaw pora ahise.
Kintu Melchizedek, tai laga khandan tai khan pora bisari kene panai, hoilebhi Abraham pora tai te dos bhag dise, aru kun manu logote kosom di kene thakise tai ke asirbad dise.
Kintu eku jhagara nokori kene, ekjon chutu manu ke dangor manu pora asirbad dise.
Etu karone, jinda thaka manu dos bhag pai, kintu etu pora tai jinda thaki ase koi kene gawahi diye.
Aru, kotha kori thaka nisina, Levi, kun bhi dos bhag tu paise, tai bhi jai kene Abraham ke dos bhag tu di dise,
kelemane Levi etu homoi te tai laga khandan laga naam pora thakise jetiya Melchizedek Abraham ke lok paisile.
Jodi sob bhal kaam khan Levi laga purohit khan pora he hoise koile (etu pora manu khan niyom aru kanun paise), tetiya hoile kele aru dusra ekjon purohit ahhibole nimite kaam thakise Melchizedek laga niyom hisab te, aru Aaron laga niyom hisab te matibole dorkar nathaka hoise?
Etu kotha khan kun ekjon nimite koi ase tai dusra jat laga ase, kun manu bhi jai kene etu bolidan diya jaga te sewa koranai.
Moi khan laga Probhu Judah laga khandan pora ahise koi kene sapha pora jani loise, aru Moses pora bhi etu purohit laga jat nimite eku kotha kora nai.
Aru etu bisi sapha hoi jaise, jodi kunba aru ekta purohit Melchizedek nisana ulai jai.
Tai ekta purohit hoise, ki laga khandan pora ahise etu laga niyom kanun sai kene nohoi, kintu tai laga takot aru ketiya bhi bhangai dibole napara jibon sai kene tai ke purohit bonai se.
Kelemane Isor laga kotha te bhi eneka gawahi di ase:
“Tumi hodai nimite purohit ase Melchizedek laga niyom hisab te.”
Purana niyom aru kaam khan hatai dise kelemane etu khan komjor aru eku kaam laga nai,
(niyom aru kanun pora eku kaam tu bhal bonai dibole napare), aru bhal akha laga kotha tu manu khan ke koi dise, etu pora moi khan Isor usorte ahhe.
Aru etu kaam kosom khai kene koranai! Kelemane kosom noloi kene he tai khan purohit hoi jaise,
kintu Jisu kosom khai kene he purohit hoise, Isor pora Tar ke koise,
“Probhu pora kosom khaise aru Tar mon bodli nokoribo:
‘Tumi hodai nimite purohit ase.’”
Etu nisina he, Jisu pora moi khan nimite bhal kaam koribole nimite rasta khuli dise.
Prothom laga purohit khan bisi manu thakise, kintu mori ja nimite tai khan laga ginti nathaka hoise.
Kintu Jisu hodai nimite jinda ase, Tar pora purohit laga naam tu uthai kene ketiya bhi loi jabole naparibo.
Etu karone kun manu Tar usorte Isor ke pabole nimite bisari kene ahhe, Tar pora tai khan ke bacha bole pare, kelemane Tar tai khan nimite manu aru Isor laga majote hodai kotha kori diye.
Eneka moha purohit thaka tu amikhan nimite bhal ase. Tar pobitro ase, eku golti nai, sapha, paapi manu khan pora alag, aru sorgo pora bhi untcha hoi jaise.
Tar laga eku dorkar nai, ekta purohit hisab te hodai bolidan bibole nimite, pohila tai nijor laga paap pora, etu pichete manu laga paap pora. Kelemane Tar ekbar pora he sob kaam tu kori dise, jetiya Tar nijor ke bolidan kori dise.
Kelemane kanun pora komjor manu khan nimite moha purohit ke basi loi. Kintu kosom laga kotha, kun tu kanun pora ahise, Purtro ke basi loise, kun ke sob phale pora hodai nimite bhal bonai dise.
Etiya moi khan ki kobole mon ase etu laga motlab tu hoile eneka ase: Moi khan logote Moha Purohit ase kun sinhasan laga dyna hath te sorgo laga mohan jaga te bohi ase.
Tar pobitro jaga laga ekjon sewak ase aru Probhu laga hosa pora aradhana kora jaga ase, manu pora bona nohoi.
Kelemane sob moha purohit khan ke tofa aru bolidan dibole nimite bachi loise. Etu nimite eneka koribole dorkar ase kiba ekta tai pora bhi bolidan dibole nimite ahnibo lage.
Etiya jodi Khrista prithibi te ase koile, Tar ekta purohit nohobole thakise, kanun laga niyom hisab te bolidan dibole nimite tate manu khan thakise.
Tai khan sorgo te thaka laga saya ki dikhi ase etu ke sewa kora he ahse, jeneka Moses ke Isor pora mana korise jetiya tai aradhana kora laga jaga bona bole thakise. Isor he koise, “Sabi tumi ke pahar uporte loi jai kene keneka dikhai dise etu nisina he bonabi.”
Kintu etiya Khrista bhal kaam tu paise, jeneka Tar manu aru Isor laga majote ekta kotha kori kene milai diya manu hoise kun tu ahha laga bhal din nimite kori dise.
Jodi prothom laga niyom te eku golti nai koile, tetiya hoile aru dusra niyom dibole nimite eku dorkar nai.
