Moi laga kanun tai khan laga bhabona te rakhi dibo,
aru tai khan laga mon te likhi dibo.
Moi tai khan laga Isor hobo,
aru tai khan Moi laga manu hobo.
Tai khan ketiya bhi nijor laga ghor usor thaka manu
aru kokai bhai khan ke nishikabo, aru kobo, ‘Probhu ke janibi.’
Kelemane tai khan Moi ke janibo,
sob se chutu pora loi kene sob se dangor tak.
Kelemane tai khan beya kaam kori kene thakise koile bhi Moi tai khan uporte morom thakibo,
Aru tai khan laga paap Moi aru ketiya bhi yaad nokoribo.”
Etu niyom ke “notun” mata nisina, Tar pora prothom niyom tu bodli kori dise, aru kun tu purana aru eku kaam nathake hoise, etu joldi harai jabo.
Etu nisina prothom laga COVENANT/niyom te bhi prithibi te aradhana koribole thakise aru aradhana kora pobitro jaga bhi thakisele.
Dusra purdah laga pichete aru bhi ekta kamra thakise, aru etu ke pobitro pora bhi bisi pobitro koi matise.
Tate dhuwa jolaikene aradhana koribole laga suna pora bona pobitro jaga thakise. Etu laga bhitor te vachan laga ARK thakise kuntu pura suna pora lipai kene thakise. Etu laga bhitorte manna ke dhori kene thaka laga suna pora bona kolsi ekta thakise, Aaron laga lathi pora notun pata ulai thakise, aru vachan/COVENANT rakha laga mez khan thakise.
Aru etu dangor niyom/vachan/covenant laga uporte, mohima pora bhorta thaka Cherubim pora sapha kori diya laga dhakna ke bon kori kene thakise, kintu etiya etu kotha khan bhal pora koi dibole nimite homoi huwanai.
Jetiya etu khan sob tayar kori kene rakhi dise, tetiya purohit hodai tombu ghor laga bahar kamra te jai aru ta te ki kaam koribole lage tai khan jai kene kore.
Kintu khali moha purohit hai dusra kamra te ghusikene, sal te khali ek bar, tai pora nijor nimite bolidan diya laga khun aru manu khan najani kene paap kura laga daan loikene jai.
Pobitro Aatma pora pobitro jaga te jabole nimite rasta tu dikhai diya nai jetiya tak prothom laga tambu khara kori thakise.
Etiya laga homoi nimite etu ekta chin ase, juntu te tofa aru bolidan duijon bhi dile bhi aradhana kori thaka manu laga mon ekdum bhal se sapha kuribole napare.
Tai khan khali kha luwa aru nijor gaw ke sapha rakhibole laga niyom khan nimite mon di thakise, juntu thakise jetiya tak notun niyom laga homoi tu ahhi janai.
Kintu Khrista ekta moha purohit nisina bhal kaam koribole nimite ahise. Tar dangor ula aru bhal ula tambu te jaise kun tu manu laga hath pora bona nohoi, ekjon kun etu shristi te bona laga nohoi.
Tar sob pora pobitro jaga te jaise, saguli aru guru laga bacha khun pora nohoi, kintu Tar nijor laga khun pora amikhan nimite anonto poritran anidise.
Kelemane jodi saguli aru mota goru laga khun aru bacha napa goru laga khun pora kun paap te giri kene letera hoi ase tai khan uporte dhali dile Isor usorte paap pora maph pai koile,
tetiya hoile Khrista laga khun tu aru bhi kiman bhal hobo,Tar anonto aatma pora nijor ke Isor usorte eku golti nokori kene Tar laga jibon tu bolidan kori dise, apuni ke sapha kori dise aru mora laga kaam pora bachai kene jinda Isor ke sewa koribole nimite dise?
Etu karone, Tar manu aru Isor majote notun niyom ase, etu pora kun ke mati loise tai khan anonto jibon laga asirbad pabo, prothom laga niyom te paap pora maph pabole nimite ki niyom thakise etu hatai kene Tar manu khan ke paap pora bachai dibole nimite nijor ke mori bole dise.
Kelemane kun jaga te echa ase, kun manu etu nimite morise tai hosa ase koi kene dikhai dibole lagibo.
Kelemane mora manu laga echa likhi thaka tu, tar mora pichete he kaam kore, kilekoile etu laga eku kaam nai jetiya tak kuntu manu etu likhi se tai jinda ase.
Etu nimite prothom laga niyom bhi khun noloikene shuru kori diya nai.
Jetiya Moses pora manu khan logote niyom laga hukum khan koi dise, tai saguli aru goru laga khun loise, pani pora, lal shuta, aru dawai bona laga pata loi kene, likhi kene rakha niyom laga duita kitab te aru manu khan uporte dhali dise.
Tetiya tai koise, “Etu Isor laga niyom mana laga khun ase aru etu apuni khan mani kene thakibole nimite hukum di ase.”
Etu nisina, tai tambu uporte khun dhali dise aru tate chola laga kiman saman thakise etu khan te bhi dhali dise.
Niyom laga hisab te sob tu khun pora sapha kori dise, aru khun ulai kene nidiya tak paap pora maph napabo.
Etu nimite eneka koribole dorkar ase aru sorgote bhi kiman saman ase etu khan ke bhi eneka pora he sapha koribole lage. Hoilebhi, sorgo te thaka saman khan ke etu pora bhi bhal bolidan pora sapha kori bole lage.
Kelemane Khrista bhi hath pora bonai kene rakha dangor pobitro jaga te ghusa nai, etu hosa ekjon laga sabole eke thaka dikhai diya nisina he ase. Kintu Tar nijor pora he sorgote ghusise, aru Isor laga usorte moi khan karone etiya jaga bonabole nimite jaise.
Tar tate aru nijor ke daan dibole nimite ghusanai, moha purohit khan pora kora nisina, kun sal te ekbar pobitro jaga te khun laga bolidan loi kena ekjon-ekjon nimite ghusi thakise.
Jodi eneka he ase koile, Tar prithibi laga shuru pora bar-bar jai kene nijor ke dukh pabole nimite dibole thakise. Kintu Tar nijor pora ahhi kene etu antim homoi te nijor jibon tu manu khan nimite bolidan kori dise.
Jeneka manu bhi ekbar moribole lage, aru etu pichete bichar kora laga homoi ahibo,
etu nisina, Khrista ke bhi manu laga paap bukhibole nimite dise, aru ekbar ahhibole ase kun manu Tar nimite pura mon pora rukhi ase, aru paap tu bukhibole nimite nohoi, kintu poritron dibole nimite ahhibo.
Nohoile, bolidan kora tu rukhi jabole asile naki? Kelemane ek bar bolidan diya pora he manu khan sapha hobo le asile, aru paap laga bhabona ekubi nathakibo le asile.
Kintu sal-sal pichete utu boldian khan di thaka tu taikhan laga paap thaka tu yaad kori diya he ashe.
Kelemane saguli aru goru laga khun pora paap tu sapha kori dibole napare.
Etu nimite jetiya Khrista prithibi te ahise, Tar koise,
“Bolidan aru daan khan apuni echa nokore,
kintu ekta gaw moi nimite tayar kori diya tu he echa kore;
jolai kene daan kora aru paap laga daan diya pora apuni khusi napai.
Tetiya moi koise, ‘Sabi moi yate ase- moi nimite kitab te likha nisina- apuni laga kaam koribole nimite, O Isor.’”
Tar uporte kuwa nisina, “Bolidan, aru daan, aru jolai kene diya daan, aru paap laga daan apuni echa nokore. Aru eneka manu pora kori thakile bhi apuni khusi napai” (niyom hisabte daan di thaka),
tetiya Tar koise, “Sabi moi yate apuni laga echa koribole nimite ase.” Tar shuru te ki niyom kori thakise etu hatai kene dusra notun niyom shuru kori dise.
Etu laga echa pora, moi khan ke Jisu Khrista laga gaw daan diya karone paap pora hodai nimite sapha kori dise.
Aru sob purohit khara kori kene hodai din Isor usorte tai laga niyom kori thake. Tai bolidan kori thaka laga daan tu bar-bar kori thake- kintu etu bolidan kori thakile bhi paap tu ketiya bhi harai najai.
Kintu jetiya Khrista pora sob paap laga bolidan ekbar pora dise, Tar Isor laga dyna hath te bohise.
Etu homoi pora, Tar rukhi ase ketiya Tar laga dusman khan ke paw nichete girai dibo.
Ekta bolidan diya pora Tar sob ke paap pora hodai nimite sapha kori dise.
Aru Pobitro Aatma pora bhi moi khan ke etu gawahi diye. Tar pora poila etu koise,
“Etu laga niyom tai khan logote bonabo,
Utu din pichete moi, Probhu pora koi ase.
Moi laga kanun tai khan laga mon te rakhibo,
Aru tai khan laga bhabona te likhi dibo.”
Aru tetiya,
“Tai khan laga paap aru beya kaam khan aru moi yaad nokoribo.”
Jun jaga te etu khan pora maph pabo, tate aru paap laga bolidan dibole nimite dorkar nai.
Etu karone, bhai khan, Jisu laga khun pora moi khan pobitro jaga te jabole nimite pura akha ase.
Tar pora amikhan nimite ekta notun aru jinda thaka rasta khuli dise aru purdah bhi hatai dise, juntu Tar laga gaw duara hoise.
Kelemane moi khan logote dangor purohit Isor laga ghor te ase,
Moi khan akha pora paap tu shikar kori kene thaka tu hili bole nadikene jor pora dhori lobo, kelemane Isor, kun kosom dise, Tar hosa aru bhal ase.
Aru moi khan ekjon-ekjon ke bhal kaam kori kene morom pora thakibole nimite mon dangor kori dibo.
Moi khan ekjon-ekjon ke lok kori thakibole nimite bon nokoribo, kelemane kunba manu khan eneka kore. Hoilebhi, moi khan ekjon-ekjon ke mon dangor kori dibo, aru apuni khan din tu usor ahhi ja tu dikhibo.
Jodi moi khan hosa kotha tu jani kene pichete bhi paap kaam kori kene jai thakile, tetiya hoile paap pora apuni nimite bolidan diya tu hoile eku kaam nohobo.
Kintu, bichar laga din te ki hobole ase etu bhoi kori kene thakibole nimite olop he bhabona kori kene ase, aru Isor laga dushman khan ke juie pora julai dibo.
Kun manu Moses laga kanun namani kene thake tai khan mori jai duijon tinjon laga gawahi pora.
Kun manu Isor laga Chokora ke theng nichete chipai dise tai laga sajai tu kiman dangor hobo, aru notun niyom laga khun ke hisab koranai- etu khun pora tai ke sapha kori dise- aru Kripa laga Aatma ke opman kori dise?
Kelemane moi khan jani ase etu kun pora koise, “Badla tu moi laga ase; moi tai khan ki korise etu wapas dibo.” Aru bhi, “Probhu pora tai laga manu khan ke bichar koribo.”
Jinda Isor laga hath te giri bole nimite bhoi ase!
Kintu poila laga din tu yaad koribi, jetiya, apuni ke khusi kori diya pichete, tumi laga jibon te dangor dukh ahhe.
Apuni ke manu usorte ketiya ba sorom khelai kene dukh pabole ieye, aru kunba homoi te kun dukh paisile tai khan logote sathi kori kene thaki jai.
Kelemane apuni koidi ghorte thaka manu khan ke kiman morom dikhaise, aru apuni khan laga sompoti khan jobor josti pora loi ja bhi apuni khan khushi pora mani loise. Apuni jane apuni nimite etu pora bhi bhal ketiya bhi khotom nokora laga dhun rakhi kene ase.
Etu nimite apuni laga bharosa ketiya bhi harabole nidibi, kelemane etu te he apuni laga dangor enam rakhi kene ase.
Kelemane apuni khan nomro hobole lagi ase, etu pora apuni asirbad pabo, apuni Isor laga echa kori luwa pichete.
“Kelemane olop homoi te,
ekjon kun ahibole ase Tar deri nohoi kene ahhi jabo.
Kintu moi laga dharmik khan bisas pora jinda thakibo,
aru jodi tai pichete jai kene giri jai, Moi laga aatma tai uporte ketiya bhi khusi napabo.”
Kintu moi beya kaam pora giri kene pichete ja manu nohoi. Kintu, moi khan bisas pora aatma tu bachai kene rakha manu ase.
Bisas mane ki tu akha kore juntu nidikhile bhi pabole ase koi kene jane.
Aru etu nimite he baba khan ke Isor pora bachi loise.
Bisas pora he etu pura shrisi tu Isor laga hukum pora bonai dise koi kene moi khan jane, etu nimite ki saman dikhi ase etu khan nidikha laga saman pora bonanai.
Bisas pora Abel he Cain pora bhi bhal daan Isor ke dise, etu pora tai ke dharmik bonai dise, aru Isor pora tai laga daan dikhi kene bhal kotha koise, aru bisas pora he ahji tak Abel kotha kore, jodi bhi tai mori jaise hoilebhi.
Bisas pora he Enoch ke sorgote uthai kene loi jaise aru tai mora tu dikhanai, tai Isor ke khusi korise koi kene gawahi dise.
Etiya bisas nathakile Isor ke khusi koribole naparibo. Kelemane kun Isor usorte ahhe Tar jinda ase koi ken bisas koribole lage aru kun manu Tar ke bisare tai khan ke enam dibo.
Bisas pora Noah ke, ki tu dikhanai etu laga kotha khan janibole dise, Isor ke bhoi korikene thaka nimite tai laga ghor manu khan ke bachai lobole nimite pani laga jahas bonabole nimite dise. Etu kori kene, tai prithibi ke girai dise aru bisas pora dharmik korta laga ekjon manu hoi jaise.
Bisas pora tai Isor pora kosom diya laga jaga te jai kene dusra jat laga manu nisina thakise.
Kelemane tai ekta bhal pora bona laga citi ke sai thakise, aru kun etu bonaise tai tu hoile Isor ase.
Bisas pora, Sarah bhi bacha bukhibole parise, tai buri hoi jaile bhi, kelemane Isor pora ki kosom dise etu uporte bisas korise.
Etu nimite, ekjon manu pora- aru tai moribole he thakise- akash te gonti koribole napara tara nisina tai laga khandan khan jonom hoise, aru samundar kinar te balu thaka nisina gonti koribole napara laga thakise.
Bisas pora tai khan sob mori jaise etu kosom tu napai kene, kintu tai khan ke dur pora dikhi kene salam dise, aru koise tai khan dusra manu laga desh te thaki ase aru prithibi te nijor manu pora dur hoi kene ase.
Kelemane kun manu khan eneka kotha kore tai khan nijor laga ghor bonabole bisari ase.
Jodi tai khan kun tu desh pora ulai kene jaise etu bhabi thakise koile, tai khan tate aru bhi wapas jabole paribo thakise.
Kintu, tai khan etu pora bhi bhal desh nimite echa korise, etu hoile, sorgote thaka ula. Etu nimite Isor tu sorom nokore tai khan laga Isor ase kobole, kelemane Tar pora tai khan nimite ekta citi bonai kene rakhise.
Bisas pora he Abraham, jetiya taike porikha korise, Isak ke bolidan dibole taiyar hoise. Tai bhi kun Isor pora asirbad paise tai laga ekta bacha thaka ke bhi bolidan koribole thakise.
Tai ke eneka koisele, “Isak laga naam pora he tumi laga khandan laga naam matibo.”
Abraham jani thakise Isor pora Isak ke mora pora jinda koribole paribo, aru bhabona nisina, tai Isak ke etu jaga pora wapas pai loise.
Bisas pora he, ki tu ahhibole ase etu nimite, Isak pora Jakob aru Esau ke asirbad dise.
Bisas pora, jetiya Jakob mori bole thakise, Joseph laga sob bacha khan ke tai asirbad dise, aru mohima korise, tai laga lathi uporte khara kori kene.
Bisas pora Joseph, jetiya tai mori bole thakise, tai laga chokora khan ke koise aru tai mora pichete Egypt pora tai laga hardi khan loi kene Israel te rakhibole nimite koise.
Bisas pora Moses, jetiya jonom loisele, tai laga baba ama pora tin mohina tak tai ke lukai kene rakhise kelemane tai sabole bisi sundur thakise, aru raja pora ki hukum dise etu nimite tai khan bhoi koranai.
Bisas pora Moses, jetiya tai dangor hoi jaise, tai nijor ke Pharoah laga chukuri laga chokora kobole nimite mana korise.
Kintu, tai nijor ke Isor manu khan karone dukh pabole nimite bachi loise, paap laga kaam pora khusi diya khan sob chari kene Isor ke sewa korise.
Tai eneka koise Jisu Khrista laga dhun tu Egypt laga dhun pora bhi bisi dangor ase. Kelemane tai laga suku tu tai laga enam pabole nimite sai thakise.
Bisas pora Moses Egypt chari kene jaise. Tai raja laga ghusa ke eku hisab kora nai, tai dukh pai thakise kun ba ekjon kun ke nadikhe etu ke dikhi thaka nisina dorjo korise.
Bisas pora tai Israel manu khan ke Par-Huwa aru khun dhali diya din manaise, etu pora prothom jonom kora bacha khan ke morai diya laga aatma ahhi kene tai khan ke nachubo nimite.
Bisas pora tai khan dangor samundar tu ekta sukha mati te jai thaka nisina par koribole parise. Jetiya Egypt khan eneka koribole bisarise, tai khan ke pani pora khai loise.
Bisas pora Jericho laga dewar khan giri jaise, jetiya tai khan sath din tak ta te ghuri kene thakise.
Bisas pora Rahab ekta beyobichari tai dusra beya kaam kori kene thaka manu khan nisina mora nai, kelemane tai shanti pora jasus kora sipoi khan ke modot kora nimite.
Etu pora aru moi bisi ki kobo? Jodi moi Gideon, Barak, Samson, Jephtath, David, Samuel aru dusra bhawadi khan laga kotha kore tetiya hoile homoi pora etu khan laga sob kotha koribole naponchibo.
Bisas pora tai khan raijyo tu jiti loise, niyai laga kaam korise, aru asirbad paise. Tai khan bagh laga mukh bhi bon kori dise,
juie laga takot tu bhujai dise, aru talwar laga dhar pora polabole parise, bimar pora bhal hoi jaise, lorai kora homoi te takot hoi jaise, aru dusra desh laga sipahi khan ke harai dise.
Aru dusra kunba khan to ninda kori kene pitise aru luha rosi pora bandhi kene bandhi-ghor te humai dise.
Tai khan ke pathor marise, aru tai khan ke kati kene diu ta bonai dise, tai khan ke porikha korise, aru tai khan ke talwar pora morai dise. Tai khan saguli aru bhera laga chamra pindhise, aru bisi gorib hoi jaise, chinta bhabona bisi hoi jaise, aru manu khan pora tai khan ke beya kori thakise.
Etu duniya tu tai khan nimite eku yogya laga thaka nai. Tai khan jongol aru pahar khan te berai thakise, aru mati laga nichete jai kene thakise.
Tai khan laga bisas nimite manu khan pora mohima dise, hoilebhi tai khan ashirbad pa nai.
Isor he moi khan nimite kiba ekta bhal bhabona kori kene ase, aru moi khan nohoile, etu khan sob tu bhal kori dibole napare.
Etu karone, moi khan logote gawahi laga badal churi kene ase, moi khan laga uporte paap lagi kene thaka aru paap pora bhari hoi kene thaka khan pichete chari dibo. Moi khan nimite ki rakhi kene ase etu ke sai kene polabo.
Moi khan Jisu laga kotha hunibo, bisas suru kora aru bhal kori diya ekjon. Kelemane kun tu khusi Tar laga aghe te rakhi disele, Tar crus tu loise, manu khan pora Tar ke beya pai kene sorom khilai dise, aru Isor laga sinhasan usorte Tar dyna hath te bohi ahse.
Etu nimite Tar ke bhabibi, Tar ekjon kun nijor uporte paap laga sob beya kaam khan bukhise, etu nimite apuni ketiya bhi mon te dukh napabo aru chari nidibo.
Apuni khan paap logote lorai kora tu khun ulabole tak dukh pa nohoi.
Aru apuni khan ke bacha koi kene mon dangor kori dikene mata tu apunikhan pahori jaise:
“Moi laga bacha, Probhu pora ki bhal rasta te jabole nimite shikai ase etu ke dhamali nabhabi bi,
Aru jetiya Tar apuni ke bhal rasta te jabole nimite shikai tetiya alchi nokoribi.
Kelemane Isor kun ke morom kore tai ke bhal rasta te jabole nimite shikai,
aru kun chokora Tar pai tai ke sajai diye.
Dukh pai thaka tu hoile bhal rasta te jabole nimite ase. Isor pora apuni logote Tar nijor laga bacha nisina he sai. Eneka kun chokora ase tai laga baba pora bhal rasta te jabole nimite nashikai?
Jodi apuni khan ke bhal rasta tu shikai diya nai, jeneka sob manu etu nishika laga kaam te bhag loi kene ase, tetiya hoile apuni bhal niyom pora jonom nokora bacha ase aru apuni Isor laga bacha nohoi.
Etu nisina, moikhan laga prithibi te thaka baba pora shikai diya kotha tu moi khan bisi adar kore aru tai ke sonman diye. Tetiya hoile aatma te thaka baba ke moi khan sai kene kiman adar kori kene thakibole lage?
Moi khan laga prithibi te thaka pora kiman tak shikabole pare tai shikai diye. Kintu Isor moi khan bhal hobole nimite shikai diye, etu pora moi khan bhi tai laga pobitro te thakibo.
Sob homoi te bhal rasta te jabole nimite shikai diya tu khusi laga nohobo bi pare, kintu dukh pai. Kintu pichete shanti laga bhal phol aru dharmik hoi jabole hoijai kun manu ke etu nimite shikai kene rakhi dise.
Etu nimite apuni laga hath giri kene thaka tu takot kori lobi aru apuni laga komjor theng bhi takot kori lobi.
Apuni laga theng nimite rasta tu shida bonai lobi, etu pora apuni berabole napari kene bikhai thaka tu bhal hoi jabo.
Sob manu logote shanti pora thakibi, aru pobitro hoi kene thakibi etu nohoile kun bhi Probhu ke dikhibole naparibo.
Sabi Isor laga anugrah pora kun bhi komti hoi kene nathaki bo nimite, etu pora tita laga jor kun logote bhi ulai kene digdar nakoribo nimite, aru etu pora bisi manu letera hoi jabole pare.
Sabi Esau nisina beyobichari aru beya kaam kora manu nathakibole nimite, kun ekbar laga khana nimite tai nijor laga naam tu bikiri kori dise.
Apuni khan jane etu pichete bhi, jetiya tai asirbad pabole nimite echa korisile, tai ke tyag koridise, kelemane tai mon ghurabole nimite aru homoi panai, tai kandi kene suku pani ulai le bhi eku panai.
Apuni khan kiba ekta chubole para laga usorte ahha nohoi, joli thaka juie, andhera, eku nidikha hoi ja, dangor mon dukh aru tufan,
Kelemane tai khan ke ki hukum disele etu mani kene thakibole paranai: “Jodi ekta janwar etu pahar ke chui diye, etu ke pathor maribo lage.”
Etu dikhi bole bisi bhoi laga thakise aru Moses pora koise, “Moi bhoi lagi ase aru moi bhoi pora kapi ase.”
Hoilebi, tumi Zion pahar te aru Isor laga citi te ahise, sorgo laga Jerusalem, aru dos hazar sorgoduth khan khusi kori thaka jaga te,
aru prothom bacha jonom kori kene manu khan joma kora jaga te, aru Isor logote, sob ke bichar kora ekjon, aru dharmik manu laga aatma khan logote kun ke bhal bonai dise,
aru Jisu, manu aru Isor majote notun niyom pora kotha kori diya ekjon, aru ulai kene dhali deya khun kun tu Abel laga khun pora bhi bhal ase.
Sabi apuni logote kun pora kotha kori ase Tar ke mana nokoribo nimite. Kelemane tai khan polabole pora nai jetiya tai khan Isor ke mana korise kun etu prithibi te tai khan ke beya rasta te najabole koise, tetiya hoile moi khan Tar kun sorgo pora koi ase Tar laga usor pora keneka polabole paribo.
Ekta homoi te, Tar laga awaj pora prithibi tu hilai dise. Kintu etiya kosom khai kene koise, “Aru ekbar khali etu prithibi tu he nohoi, kintu sorgo bhi hilai dibo.”
Kintu etu kotha khan, “aru ekbar,” laga motlab ase ki tu hilaise etu hatai dibole, aru etu hoile, ki tu bonai disele, kun tu hilai diya nai etu thakibo.
Etu nimite, moi khan ketiya bhi hilabole napara laga raijyo tu pai ahse, moi khan etu ke mani kene thakibo, etu pora moi khan Isor ke aradhana kori kene Tar ke khusi koribo, sonman aru adar di kene.
Moi khan laga Isor tu hoile jolai diya laga juie ahse.
Bhai kokai laga morom hodai thakibole dibi.
Manu ke bhal pora sai dibole nimite napahoribi, etu pora, kunba manu najani kene sorgoduth khan ke bhi sai dise.
Koidi ghor te thaka manu khan ke yaad koribi, tai khan logote thaka nisina. Kun manu ke bhal pora sa nai tai ke bhi yaad koribi, apuni tai laga gaw bhitor te thaka nisina.
Sadi kora tu son manu pora sonman koribi, aru sadi laga bisna tu sapha rakhibi, kelemane Isor pora beyobichari kaam kora manu khan ke bichar koribo.
Apuni khan laga niom te poisa laga morom pora dur hoi kene thakibi. Apuni logote ki ase etu pora khusi hoi kene thakibi, kelemane Isor Tar nijor pora koise, “Moi tumi khan ke ketiya bhi nacharibo, aru moi tumi khan ke ketiya bhi beya napabo.”
Etu nimite moi khan bisas pora koi,
“Moi khan ke modot kura Probhu ase; moi bhi nokoribo.
Manu pora moi ke ki koribole paribo?”
Apuni laga cholawta khan ke mani kene thakibi, kun apuni khan ke Isor laga kotha tu koi diye, aru tai khan apuni logote keneka thake etu sai lobi, aru tai khan bisas te thaka nisina thakibi.
Jisu Khrista kali, ahji aru hodai nimite eke ase.
Apuni khan ke alag niyom aru kanun pora shikai diya kotha khan huni kene harai najabi. Kelemane apuni laga mon tu anugrah pora takot kori kene rakha tu hai bhal ase, kun manu kha luwa laga pichete jai tai khan etu pora madot napabo.
Moi khan laga ekta eneka jaga ase kun manu ke sewa kore tai khan tate khabole naparibo.
Paap pora maph pabole nimite janwar ke moraise aru tai laga khun loi kene moha purohit khan pobitro jaga te jaise, kintu tai khan laga gaw tu bahar te loi jai kene jolai dise.
Jisu bhi citi laga dorja bahar te jai kene dukh paisile, Tar nijor laga khun pora manu khan ke sapha kori dibole nimite.
Etu nimite moi khan ghor pora bahar te ulai kene Tar logote jabo, Tar nimite sorom bukhibole karone.
Kelemane yate moi khan nimite hodai thakibole laga citi nai. Kintu, moi ki tu ahhibole ase etu nimite sai kene rukhi ase.
Kintu moi khan manu nimite bhal kaam koribole nimite alchi nokoribo, kelemane Isor eneka kora laga bolidan diya tu he khusi pai.
Apuni khan laga cholawta pora ke koi ase etu mani kene thakibi, kelemane tai khan apunikhan laga aatma nimite sikhai ase, kelekoile etu sob laga hisab tu taikhan nijor pora dibole ase. Apuni laga cholawta khan khusi pora etu kaam koribole nimite tai khan laga kotha mani kene thakibi, tai khan ke beya napabi, kelemane apuni eneka korile apuni laga eku laab nohobo.
Moi khan nimite prathana koribi, kelemane moi khan sapha mon loi kene sob bhal kaam kori thaki kene zinda thakibole nimite echa kori ase.
Kintu moi apuni khan ke etu pora bhi bisi koribole nimite mon dangor kori di ase, etu pora moi bhi apuni khan logote joldi ahhibole paribo.
Etiya Isor laga shanti, kun ke mora pora loi kene manu khan nimite ahnise, moi khan laga Probhu Jisu, ketiya bhi khotom nokora notun niyom laga khun pora,
sob bhal kaam pora Tar laga kaam koribole nimite apuni khan ke bhorta kori dibi, moi khan logote kaam kori kene Tar ke khusi koribole nimite, Jisu Khrista laga naam pora, Tar laga mohima hodai nimite thakibole dibo. Amen.
Etiya moi apuni khan laga mon dangor kori di ase, bhai khan, mon dangor kora laga kotha khan loi kene thakibi, olop kotha pora he moi apuni khan ke likhi di ase.
Moi khan laga bhai Timothy ke chari dise koi kene janise, tai ke loi kene moi apuni khan ke joldi sabole ahhibo.
Apuni khan laga cholawta aru sob dharmik manu khan ke salam dibi. Aru kunkhan Italy pora ase tai khan bhi apunikhan ke salam di ahse.
Apuni khan sob logote asirbad thakibole dibi.
James, Probhu Jisu Khrista aru Isor laga ekjon sewak, barohta jat khan ke kun dukh te ahse: Salam!
Sob tu khusi ahse etu bhabibi, moi laga bhai khan, jetiya apuni alag-alag dukh pai.
Apuni jane apuni ke porikha kora tu bisas te dangor koribole nimite ahse.
Kaam pora ki dukh paise etu pura hobole dibi, etu pora apuni khan pura hoi jabo, aru eku pora bhi komti nathakibo.
Jodi kunba manu gyan lage, Isor logote mangi lobi, aru Tar kun ke ki lage etu hisab te khusi pora diye, aru Tar pora tai khan ke dibo.
Kintu tai bisas pora mangibi, mon te eku bhabona nokori kene. Kelemane kun manu bhabona kori kene mange tai tu hoile samundar laga hawa pora ekta jaga pora dusra jaga te loi ja nisina ahse.
Eneka manu Probhu pora kiba pabo koi kene bhabona nokoribi.
Eneka manu tu duita mon thaka manu tu, sob rasta te thik nathake.
Kintu gorib bhai tai laga untcha sonman nimite phutani koribi,
kintu dhuni manu tai laga niche sonman nimite, kelemane tai nijor tu jongol laga phul nisina ghas logote harai jabo.
Kelemane suryo tu gorom diye aru ghas khan ke bhi sukhai diye. Ghas laga phul khan giri jai, aru tai sundur dikhi thaka tu harai jai. Etu nisina, rasta te jai thaka homoi te dhoni manu khan bhi harai jabo.
Etu manu ashirbad ahse kun porikha tu jiti loi. Jetiya tai etu porikha tu par kori loi, tai jibon laga mukut pai jabo, kun manu Isor ke morom kore tai khan nimite itu kosom di kene ahse.
Kun bhi tai logote porikha ahha homoi te eneka nokobi, ''Moi ke Isor pora porikha kori ahse,'' kelemane Isor ke beya pora porikha nokore, aru Tar nijor bhi dusra ke porikha nokore.
Kintu sob manu nijor laga echa pora he porikha te gire, etu pora tai ke tani kene beya kaam koribole nimite loi jai.
Jetiya echa khan mon te ulai, etu paap ke jonom diye, aru jetiya paap tu pura dangor hoi jai, etu mora ke jonom diye.
Nijor ke thokai nidibi, moi laga morom bhai khan.
Isor pora moi khan ke hosa laga kotha pora jonom dibole bachi loise, etu pora moi khan Tar bona laga shristi bhirtote prothom ula phal hobole dise.
Apuni khan etu jane, moi laga bhai khan: Sob manu joldi pora hunibi, aste pora kotha kobi, aru khong nauthibi.
Kelemane manu laga khong pora Isor laga dharmik kaam nacholai.
Etu nimite sob paap laga kaam khan chari dibi. Aru nomro hoi kene Isor laga kotha mon te rakhibi, etu pora apuni laga aatma bachai lobole paribo.
Kintu kotha huna nisina kaam bhi kori bi khali huni kene nathakibi, eneka kora tu nijor ke thokai diya he ahse.
Jodi kunba Isor laga kotha tu hune kintu kaam nokore, tai eneka manu ahse kun nijor laga chehera tu jai kene ayina te sai.
Tai nijor ke bhal pora sai loi aru jetiya bahar te ulai kene jai tai keneka dikhe etu pahori jai.
Kintu etu manu kun bhal pora sai kene kanun mani thake, aru eneka kori thake, khali huni kene pahorija nohoi, kintu kaam bhi kore, etu manu tai laga sob kaam te ashirbad pabo.
Jodi kunba nijor ke dhorom mani kene thaka manu ahse bhabe, hoilebi tai laga jiba tu rukhai kene narakhe, aru nijor laga mon tu thokai diye, tetiya hoile tai laga dhorom tu eku kaam nai.
Dhorom kun tu sapha aru Baba Isor usor te bhal ahse etu baba nathaka manu aru mota nathaka manu khan ke dukh pai kene thaka homoi te modot koribole nimite ahse, aru etu prithibi pora nijor ke dag nathaki kene rakhi bole nimite ahse.
Moi laga bhai khan, moi khan laga bisas tu Probhu Jisu Khrista logote bon kori kene narakhibi, mohima laga Probhu, apuni kun ke bhal lage etu ke sai kene.
Jodi kunba manu apuni khan joma kori thaka jaga te suna aru bhal kapra lagai kene ahhe, aru tate ekjon gorib manu bhi letera kapor lagai kene ahhe.
Kintu jodi apuni bhal kapra lagai kene thaka manu ke koi ahse, “Apuni yate bhal jaga te bohibi,” kintu gorib manu ke koi, “Apuni tate khara koribi” aru “Moi laga paw te bohibi,”
apuni khan nijor majote bichar kori ahse nohoi? Apuni beya bhabona loi kene bichar kora manu hoi ahse nohoi?
Hunibi, moi laga morom bhai khan, Isor he prithibi laga gorib manu ke bisas te dhuni hobole diya nohoi aru kun manu Tar ke morom kore tai khan ke Tar laga raijyo te jaga diye nohoi?
Kintu apuni gorib manu ke hisab kora nai! Etu dhuni manu khan pora he apuni ke dukh diya nohoi? Aru tai khan he apunikhan ke bichar koribole bichar ghor te loi jai nohoi?
Apunikhan ke kuntu bhal naam pora matise, etu naam ke sorom khilai dise nohoi?
Jodi, apuni, Isor laga kanun khan mani kene thake, “Apuni laga ghor usorte thaka manu ke nijor nisina morom koribo,” tetiya apuni bhal kori ahse.
Kintu jodi apuni bhal pai thaka manu ke he sai, apuni paap kori ahse, aru apuni ekta kanun bhangai diya manu ahse.
Kun manu pura kanun tu mane, hoilebi tai chutu jaga ekta te girijai, tetiya tai pura kanun bhangai diya manu ahse.
Kelemane etu ekjon kun eneka koise, “Beyobichari nokoribi,” tai pora etu bhi koise, “Manu ke morai nidibi.” Kintu jodi apuni beyobichari nokore, kintu manu ke morai diye, tetiya hoile apuni kanun bhanga manu ahse.
Etu karne amikhan ke mukti diya kanun pora bichar koribole thaka nimite, ki koi ase etu nijor pora bhi koribi.
Kelemane bichar tu etu manu khan logote ahhe kun daya tu dikhai diya nai. Daya he bichar uporte jiti loi.
Ki tu bhal ahse, moi laga bhai khan, jodi kunba manu koi tai logote bisas ahse, kintu tai logote kaam tu nai? Tetiya hoile etu bisas pora tai ke bacha bole paribo?
Jodi ekjon bhai aru bhoini beya kapor lagai kene ahse aru khabole nimite napai kene thaki ahse.
Etiya ekjon pora tai khan ke eneka koise, “Shanti pora jabi, bhorta hoi kene bhal pora thakibi.” Kintu jodi apuni tai khan laga gaw pora ki lage etu nidiye, tetiya hoile ki bhal ahse?
Kunba pora eneka kobole pare, “Apuni logote bisas ahse, aru moi logote kaam ahse.” Apuni kaam nathaki kene bisas tu dikhai dibi, aru moi laga kaam pora apuni ke bisas tu dikhai dibo.
Apuni bisas kore ki Isor ekta ahse; apuni bhal pora jane. Saitan khan bhi etu jane, aru tai khan bhoi pora kape.
Kintu apuni janibole mon ahse, okora manu khan, bisas logote kaam nathakile eku laab nai?
Moi khan laga baba Abraham pora jetiya tai laga chokora Isak ke daan dibole nimite thakise, tai laga kaam pora tai ke JUSTIFY korise nohoi?
Apuni sabi tai laga bisas aru tai laga kaam milise, aru tai laga kaam pora bisas tu aru bisi hoi jaise.
Isor laga kotha eneka koi kene pura hoise, “Kintu Abraham Isor ke bisas korise, aru etu pora tai dharmik ahse koi kene manise,” aru tai ke Isor laga sathi matise.
Apuni sabi ekta manu laga kaam pora he tai ke JUSTIFY kore, khali tai laga bisas pora he nohoi.
Kintu etu nisina pora he, Rahab bhi tai laga kaam pora bichar kora nai naki, jetiya tai Isor manu khan ke matise aru dusra rasta pora pothai dise?
Etu nisia, ekta gaw te aatma nathakile gaw tu mora ahse, etu nisina bisas logote kaam nathakile etu bisas tu mora ahse.
Apuni khan sob shikai diya manu hobole napare, moi laga bhai khan, kelemane apuni khan jane moi khan kun manu khan ke shikai tai khan bisi kara pora bichar koribo.
Moi khan sob bisi raasta pora giri jai. Jodi kunba manu tai laga kotha pora nigirile, tai ekta bhal manu ahse, aru tai laga pura gaw tu cholai kene jabole pare.
Etiya jodi moi khan ghora laga mukh te kotha mani bole nimite rusi lagai diye, moi khan tai laga pura gaw tu chola bole pare.
Aru ekta jahas ke bhi sabi, tai khan eman dangor ahse aru hawa pora tai khan ke loi jai, kun tu jaga te chola manu pora loi jabole mon kore tate loi jai.
Etu nisina jiba tu gaw laga ekta chutu bhag he ahse, kintu bisi dangor kotha khan koi kene phutani kore. Aru sabi keneka kori kene ekta chutu juie pora dangor jongol julai diye.
Etu jiba bhi juie nisina he ahse, paap pora bhorta thaka prithibi. Etu jiba moi khan laga gaw majote ahse, pura gaw tu dag hoi jai aru jibon te juie jolai diye. Kintu etu juie norok pora he ahhe.
Sob kisim laga jongol janwar, chiriya, aru mati te bera puka khan, aru samundar te thaka khan sob tu manu pora he cholai thake.
Kintu kun manu bhi tai nijor laga jiba tu dhori kene rakhi bole napare. Etu ekta aram nathaka saitan ahse, morai diya laga zeher pora bhorta.
Etu pora moi khan Baba Isor aru Probhu ke dhonyabad diye, aru etu pora moi khan manu ke beya koi, kun ke Isor nisina bonai dise.
Etu mukh pora ashirbad aru shrap bhi ulai. Moi laga bhai khan, eneka kaam khan nohobole lage.
Jhorna laga ekta mukh pora ula pani tu mitha aru tita pani ekbar te ulabole pare?
Ekta dimoru laga ghas pora, moilaga bhai khan, oliv ulabole pare naki? Nohoile, angur laga ghas pora khajur ulabole pare? Nimok laga pani pora ketiabhi mitha pani hobole napare.
Apuni khan majote kun gyani aru bhuji bole para manu ahse? Etu manu tai laga bhal jibon aru kaam pora bhal gyan tu dikhai dibi.
Kintu jodi apuni laga mon te lalchi aru beya kaam khan ahse, tetiya hosa laga kotha tu loi kene misa aru phutani nokoribi.
Etu upor pora ahha laga gyan nohoi. Kintu, etu prithibi, aatma te nathaka, aru saitan laga kaam ahse.
Kun jaga te lalchi aru kiba pabole laga echa thake, tate beya kaam koribole aru chinta thake.
Kintu upor pora ahha gyan tu sob se pohila, sapha ahse, aru pichete, shanti aru morom ahse, sob logote mili bole pare, daya pora bhorta aru bhal phal dhure, sob kaam te bhal aru eku chalak nokore.
Apuni khan majote kothe pora larai jhakara khan ahhe? Etu apuni khan laga echa pora nohoi kun tu apuni khan laga manu khan majote lorai kori kene thake?
Apuni echa kore, kintu apuni napai. Apuni thokai di kene morai, aru etu apuni bukhibole napare. Apuni lorai jhagara kore. Apuni etu napai kelemane apuni namange.
Apuni mange kintu apuni napai kelemane apuni bhal pora namange, apuni nijor laga echa nimite he kore.
Tumi beyobichari kori thaka khan! Apuni najane niki prithibi logote sathi kori thaka tu Isor laga birodh te ahse? Etu nimite kun manu prithibi logote sathi kori kene thakibo tai Isor laga dushman ahse.
Apuni bhabe naki Isor kotha tu ene koi ahse, “Etu aatma moi khan laga bhitorte thaki bole diya tu bisi lalchi kori ahse”?
Kintu Isor porom anugrah bisi diye, Isor kotha te koi ahse, “Phutani kori thaka manu ke Isor tu hatai diye, kintu chutu hoi kene thaka khan ke ashirbad kore.”
Isor logote sob rakhidibi. Aru saitan ke khedai dibi, tetiya tai apuni pora polai jabo.
Isor usorte ahibi, aru Tar bhi apuni laga usorte ahibo. Apuni khan laga hath sapha koribi, papi manu khan, aru mon khan sapha kori lobi, duita mon hoi thaka khan.
Mon dukh kori kena kandi bi! Apuni hasi thaka tu dukh te bodli koribi aru khusi pai thaka tu chinta te bodli kori lobi.
Probhu laga usorte nijor ke chutu koribi, aru Tar apuni ke uthai dibo.
Ejon-ekjon laga beya kotha nokoribi, bhai khan. Kun manu tai laga bhai birodh te kotha kore aru kanun laga birodh te kotha kori kene bichar kore aru kanun ke bichar kore. Kintu jodi apuni kanun ke bichar kore, apuni kanun mani thaka manu nohoi, kintu ekta bichar kora manu ahse.
Khali ekjon hai kanun diya aru bichar kore. Tar he ahse kun bachabole pare aru khotom bhi koribole pare. Kintu apuni kun ahse, kun nijor laga usorte thaka manu ke bichar kore?
Etiya hunibi, apuni kun eneka koi, “Aji nohoile kali moi khan etu jaga te jabo, aru olop sal tate thakibo, kam koribo, aru poisa kamabo.”
Apuni khan kun kali ki hobole ahse etu najane, apuni laga jibon tu ki ahse? Kelemane apuni ekta dhuwa nisina ahse kuntu olop deri nimite ulai aru pichete harai jai.
Hoilebi, apuni eneka kobole lage, “Jodi Probhu echa kore, tetiya moi khan etu koribo.”
Kintu etiya apuni laga kori bole thaka kaam khan nimite apuni phutani kori ahse.
Kun manu bhal kaam koribole jane hoile bhi nokore, tai nimite etu paap ahse.
Etiya ahibi, apuni khan kun dhoni ahse, kandi kene hala koribi kelemane apuni logote dukh ahhibole ahse.
Apuni laga dhan khan puchi jaise, aru apuni laga kapra khan puka pora khai dise.
Apuni laga suna aru chandi khan beya hoi jaise aru etu mamor lagi kene thaka khan pora apuni laga gawahi dibo. Apuni laga gaw tu juie pora khai diya nisina hoi jabo. Apuni antim din nimite apuni laga dhan khan joma kori kene rakhi ahse.
Sabi, kaam kora manu khan laga tangkha pora kandi ahse- kun manu apuni laga kheti te kaam korise tai khan laga tangkha apuni khan pora nidi kene rakhise, Mohan Probhu laga kan te kheti kora manu khan laga kandi thaka tu ponchise.
Apuni khan etu prithibi laga khusi aru aram pora thakise. Apuni khan morai diya laga din nimite nijor laga mon tu tan kori kena rakhise.
Apuni khan dharmic manu ke beya kotha kori kene morai dise. Tar apuni khan ke eneka koribole rukha nai.
Nomro hoi kene thakibi, bhai khan, jetiya tak Probhu nahe. Sabi, kheti kora manu khan mati pora tai khan kaam kora laga kheti ulabole nimite rokhi thake. Tai nomro hoi kene rokhi thake, joldi aru deri hoilebi jetiya tak pani nigire.
Apuni bhi, dorjo koribi. Apuni laga mon tu takot kori lobi, kelemane Probhu ahhibole tu usor hoise.
Manu laga biya ekjon-ekjon logote nokobi, bhai khan, eneka korile apuni logote bichar nokoribo. Sabi, bichar kora ekjon dorja te khara kori ahse.
Sabi, kun khan dorjo korise, taikhan tu dhonyo ase koikene amikhan bisas kore. Apuni khan Job pora dukh pa tu hunise, aru apuni khan Probhu laga ki echa ahse etu jane, Tar kiman morom kore aru kiman dayalu ahse. dukh aru dikdar pora kaam khan kori thake.
Kintu etu khan sob pora bhi upor, moi laga bhai khan, apuni kosom nakhabi, sorgo aru prithibi laga naam pora, aru dusra kosom khan khai kene. Kintu, apuni laga “Hoi” tu “Hoi” hobole dibi aru apuni laga “Nohoi” tu “Nohoi” hobole dibi, etu pora apuni khan bichar te nigiribo.
Kunba manu apuni khan majote dukh pai ahse naki? Tai prathana koribi. Kunba manu khusi ahse naki? Tai gana kori kene mohima dibi.
Kunba manu apuni khan majote bimar ahse naki? Tai girja laga cholawta khan ke matibi, aru tai uporte prathana koribole dibi. Probhu laga naam te tai uporte tel lagai dibi.
Bisas laga prathana ekta bimar manu ke bhal koribo, aru Probhu pora tai ke uthai dibo. Jodi tai paap korise, Isor he tai ke maph kori dibo.
Ekjon-ekjon logote paap shikar koribi, aru ek dusra nimite prathana koribi, etu pora apuni changai hoi jabo. Ekta dharmik manu laga prathana bisi takot ahse aru etu kaam kore.
Elijah bhi moi khan nisina ekta manu thakise.Tai mon di kene pani nigiri bole nimite prathana korise, aru tin sal choi mohina tak etu jaga te pani giranai.
Tetiya Elijah aru bi prathana korise, aru sorgo pora pani dise, aru prithibi pora phal ulaise.
Moi laga bhai khan, jodi kunba manu apuni khan majote hosa tu najani kene thaki ahse, aru kunba pora tai ke loi ase,
etu manu janibole lage kun manu paapi ekjon rasta harai kene berai ahse tai laga aatma ke mora pora bachai kene ase, tai kiman paap korise etu khan sob maph hoi jabo.
Peter, Jisu Khrista laga ekjon pasonir, aru kiman manu dusra desh te jai kene thaki ase, bachi luwa khan, Pontus, Galatia, Cappadocia, Asia, aru Bithynia te thaki ase.
Aru kun khan ke Baba Isor gyan pora mati kene rakhi ase, Aatma laga kotha mani kene thakibole nimite alag kori kene rakhi ase aru Jisu Khrista laga khun pora sapha kori dise. Anugrah tumi khan logote hobole dibi, aru shanti hodai tumi khan uporte bisi bhorta hoi thakibole dibi.
Baba Isor aru Probhu Jisu Khrista laga mahima hodai hobole dibi! Tar laga dangor morom te, Tar moi khan ke notun jonom dise aru Jisu Khrista ke mora pora jinda kori kene moi khan ke bisas te jinda thakibole nimite ekta akha rakhi dise.
Aru etu Jibon ketiya bhi naharabole laga dise, aru tate eku dagi nathakibolo, aru ketiyabi harai najabo. Etu moi khan nimite sorgote rakhi di kene ahse.
Apuni khan ke Isor laga hokti aru bisas pora bachai kene rakhi ase, jetiya tak anonto jibon kun tu apuni khan nimite tayar kori kene ase etu antim homoi te dikhai nadiye.
Apuni khan etu sob nimite bisi khusi kori kene ase, etiya nimite, aru olop din tak, jodi dorkar hoi, apuni khan digdar pa homoi te mon dukh pabo.
Etu sob tu apuni laga bisas tu dikhai dibole nimite ase, aru etu harai juwa laga suna pora bhi bisi dam laga ase. Jodi bhi apuni ke jui pora porikha kore, apuni laga bisas mohima pora pabo, aru prosansa, aru adar hobo jetiya Jisu Khrista ke apuni khan dikhibo.
Apuni khan Tar ke dikha nai, kintu Tar ke morom kore. Apuni khan etiya Tar ke dikhanai, Kintu Tar ke bisas kore aru kobole napara laga anondo aru khusi pora Tar ke mohima diye.
Apuni khan etiya nijor bisas pora parinam pai ase, juntu ase apunikhan aatma laga poritron.
Bhaobadi khan anonto jibon ki ase koi kene bhal pora bisari se, aru tai khan Isor kotha apuni khan nimite koi dise.
Tai khan janibole nimite bisari se kun ke Khrista laga Aatma pora ki koi ase. Aatma pora tai khan ke Jisu Khrista keneka dukh pabole ase etu koi dise aru etu pichete ki hobole ase etu khan sob tai khan ke janai dise.
Tai khan nijor ke sewa kora nai koi kene koi dise, kintu apuni khan, Isor laga kotha prochar kora manu sorgo pora Pobitro Aatma loi kene jetiya tai khan apuni ke etu kotha kun tu etiya huni ase etu khan sob koise- etu kotha khan sorgoduth khan bhi sabole mon korise.
Etu nimite apuni khan laga mon taiyar kori lobi. Nisa nahobi. Apuni khan laga akha pura Tar laga mohima te rakhibi Jetiya Jisu Khrista ahibo tetiya sob tu dikhai dibo.
Ekta kotha mani kene thaka bacha nisina, poila te najani kene thaka nisina nijor te duniya laga echa te nathakibi.
Kintu kun apuni ke matise Tar pobitro thaka nisina, apuni bhi, apuni laga sob kaam te pobitro thakibi.
Kelemane eneka likha ase, “Pobitro thakibi, kele mane Moi pobitro ase.”
Apuni khan jane harai ja laga suna chandi pora apuni khan ke bachai luwa nai kintu apuni laga okora kaam khan ki tu apuni khan laga baba khan pora apunikhan sikhise.
Kintu, apuni khan ke Jisu Khrista laga khun pora bachai loise, aru Tar ekta jokom aru dagi nathaka memna nisina ase.
Tar ke etu prithibi shuru nahuwa aghe pora bachi loise, kintu Tar ke etu antim homoi te apuni khan ke dikhai dise.
Tar nimite apuni khan Isor ke bisas kore, kun Tar ke mora pora jinda kori dise aru sob mohima dise, etu pora apuni laga bisas aru akha Isor uporte hodai thakibole nimite.
Apuni khan nijor pora apunikhan laga aatma ke hosa kotha mana pora bisi sapha kori loise. Aru etu sob nijor kokai bhai ke morom kori kene thakibole nimite; etu nimite ekjon-ekjon ke sapha mon pora morom kori kene thakibi.
Apuni khan nutun jonom hoise, harai ja laga bijon pora nahoi, kintu ketiya bhi nahara laga bijon pora, aru hodai jinda thaka Isor laga kotha pora.
Kelemane,
“Sob gaw mangso ghas nisina ase,
Aru tai laga sob mohima jongol te ulai thaka phul nisina ase,
Etu ghas sukhi jai, aru phul khan giri jai,
Kintu Probhu laga kotha hodai nimite thake.”
Etu Isor laga kotha apuni khan nimite koi dise.
Etu nimite sob beya kaam khan chari dibi, aru sob thokai diya kaam aru manu logote dusmani kori thaka khan aru kiman beya bhabona mon te rakhi ase etu khan chari dibi.
Ekta notun jonom kori kene thaka bacha nisina, aatma laga ekdum sapha thaka dudh nimite echa koribi, etu pora apuni portiron pabole aru bisi echa koribo,
jodi apuni Probhu laga morom khai saise koile.
Tar logote ahibi kun ekta jinda pathor ase jun ke manu khan pora chari disele, kintu Isor hei Tai ke bachi loise aru Isor nimite sob pora daam laga ase.
Apuni khan bhi ekta jinda pathor nisina ase kun ke aatma laga ghor bonai dise, etu pora moi khan Isor laga pobitro puhorit hobo aru Jisu Khrista ekta te aatma laga bolidan kori kene thakibo.
Etu nimite, Isor laga kotha te eneka koi ase:
“Sabi, Moi Zion te kinar laga pathor dhali ase,
bachi kene aru bisi daam laga.
Kun manu Tar ke bisas kore tai ketiya bhi sorom nakhabo.”
Apuni khan kun bisas kore tai nimite sonman pabo. Kintu jun kotha namane,
“Juntu pathor ghor bona manukhan pora phelai dise, etu he kinar laga pathor matha hoi jaise”-
Aru
“Ekta rasta bon kori diya pathor
aru kuntu tai khan ke giribole diye.”
Kintu apuni ekta bachi luwa manu ase, ekta bhal purohit, ekta pobitro desh, Isor laga manu khan, etu pora apuni khan Tar laga asurit kaam khan manu ke koi dibo kun hai apuni ke andhera pora mati kene ujala te loi anise.
Ekta homoi te apuni khan Tar laga manu thaka nai,
Kintu etiya apuni khan Isor laga manu hoi jaise.
Apuni khan pohila te daya pa nai,
Kintu etiya tu daya paise.
Morom laga bhai khan, Moi apuni khan ke dusra desh laga manu khan ke mata nisina mangso laga echa pora dur thakibole nimite matise, kun tu pora apuni laga aatma logote lorai kori ase.
Dusra jat manu khan logote apuni khan bhal kaam kori kene dikhai dibi, etu pora jodi tai khan apuni pora beya kaam kori thaka nisina kotha kore, tai khan apuni laga bhal kaam tu dikhibo aru Isor ahha laga din te Tar ke mohima dibo.
Manu pora ki adhikar cholai ase etu Probhu nimite mani kene thakibi. Prithibi laga raja khan ke mani kene thakibi,
Aru cholawta khan ke, kun tai ke pothai se beya kaam kora manu khan ke sajai dibole nimite aru kun bhal kaam kore taikhan ke prosansa koribi.
Kelemane etu Isor laga echa ase, etu pora apuni ki bhal kaam kori ase etu dikhi kene okora manu khan laga kaam nathaka kotha ke chup koribole paribo.
Ekta azad manu nisina, apuni laga azadi ke beya kaam khan lukai dibole nimite nocholabi, kintu Isor laga sewak nisina thakibi.
Sob manu ke sonman koribi. Bhai kokai ke morom koribi. Isor ke bhoi koribi. Aru raja ke sonman koribi.
Sewak khan, malik ke sob kaam pora sewa koribi. Khali bhal aru morom kora malik ke he sewa nokoribi, kintu kun malik beya ase tai ke bhi sewa koribi.
Kelemane etu bisi asis kotha ase ekjon nimite jodi tai logote anyayi hoi thaka nimite dukh dikdar pai thakilebi tai kaam khan kori thake, kelekoile tai Isor ke jani loise.
Apuni khan laga ki laab ase jodi apuni paap kori kene aru etu laga sajai bhi pai? Kintu jodi apuni bhal kaam kori kene etu pora sajai pa homoi te dukh pai, eneka korile he apuni Isor usorte mohima pabole yogya ase.
Kelemane etu nimite he apuni ke matise, aru Khrista bhi apuni nimite dukh paise. Tar laga jibon pora apuni khan bhal rasta te berabole nimite dikhai dise.
“Tar eku paap kaam kora nai,
aru Tar laga mukh pora ketiya bi beya kotha ulanai.”
Jetiya Tar ke beya kotha khan koisile, Tar wapas tai khan ke beya kotha koi kene jawab diyanai. Jetiya Tar dukh paise, Tar tai khan ke wapas dukh pabole nimite dhomki diyanai, kintu Tar kun bhal pora bichar kore tai ke nijor jibon tu di dise.
Tar moi khan laga paap tu uthai kene nijor gaw tu crus te moribole dise, etu pora moi khan paap te eku bhag nathakibole nimite, aru moi khan dharmik jibon loi kene jinda thakibo. Tar laga ghaw pora moi khan changai paise.
Kelemane apuni khan harai ja bhera nisina berai thakise, kintu etiya apuni bhera rukha manu logote wapas ahhi jaise aru apuni khan laga aatma bachai diya malik usorte ahise.
Etu nisina, shadi kora maiki khan nijor laga mota logote bhal kori kene thakibi. Eneka korile kunba mota kun Isor laga kotha namani kene ase, tai khan ke eku kotha nokoi kene jiti lobole paribo, tai khan maiki laga adat sai kene.
Kelemane tai khan apuni laga bhal kaam aru adat khan dikhibo.
Apuni laga sundur tu bahar laga saman pora nidikhabi, suna laga mala lagai kene, aru bhal sundur kapur khan lagai kene.
Kintu apuni laga bhal aru bhitor mon tu he dikhai dibi, aru ketiya bhi khotom nokora sundur aru shanti thaka aatma tu dikhai dibi, etu he Isor usorte bisi daam laga ase.
Kelemane poila te pobitro maiki khan kun Isor ke mohima kore tai khan eneka korise, tai khan laga mota ke pura di dise.
Etu nisina, shadi kora mota khan nijor maiki logote mili kene thakibi, aru tai khan komjor ase koi kene tai khan ke bhal pora sabi, apuni laga maiki ke. Apuni khan tai khan ke sonman dibi aru jibon te asirbad ana ekjon ase koi kene tai khan logote bhal pora thakibi eneka korile apuni laga prathana te ketiyabi digdar nahobo.
Kintu etiya, apuni khan sob, ekta bhabona hoi jabi, nomro koribi, kokai bhai ke morom koribi, mon tu shanti rakhibi, aru chutu hoi kene thakibi.
Manu pora beya kaam korile wapas aru beya kaam korikene nadikhabi aru apunike sorom khelai diya kotha koile aru wapas tai ke sorom nakhilabi. Kintu manu pora ki koilebi, tai ke asirbad dibi, kelemane etu nimite apuni ke mati loise, etu pora apuni asirbad pabo.
Kelemane, “Kun manu jibon tu morom kore aru bhal din dekhibole mon ahse
Tai nijor laga jiba ke beya kotha pora rukhai kene rakibi aru tai laga mukh pora beya kotha ula bole nidibi.
Kintu tai nijor ke beya kaam pora dur hoi kene thakibole dibi aru ki bhal kaam ase etu koribi.
Tai ke shanti bisari bole dibi aru etu te thakibole nimite kosis koribi.
Probhu laga suku dramik manu ke he sai thake, aru Tar laga kan tai khan pora ki koi etu hune.
Kintu kun manu Probhu laga birodh te beya kaam kore taikhan usor pora Tar laga chehera hatai diye.”
Kun manu apuni dukh koribole dibo nimite kaam kore jodi apuni bhal kaam kore?
Kintu apuni dharmik aru bhal kori kene dukh pai thakile bhi, apuni asirbad ase. Etu nimite tai khan apuni ke bhoi khelai lebhi, bhoi nokoribi, aru chinta nokoribi.
Kintu, hodai Probhu Khrista ke apuni laga mon te pobitro rakhibi. Aru hodai jowab dibole nimite tayar thakibi jodi manu khan apuni ke Isor apuni nimite ke ase etu kotha hudile.
Kintu eneka sob kotha khan apuni nomro aru manu ke sonman dikene koribi. Jetiya tai khan apuni ke kotha hude, etu homoi te apuni laga bhabona sapha rakhibi, aru kun manu apuni laga bhal jibon dekhi kene apuni ke sorom khelai, tai Khrista apuni logote ase koi kene sorom hoi jabo.
Kelemane etu bhal ase, jodi Isor echa kore, apuni beya kori kene thaka pora bhal kaam kori kene dukh pai thaka tu he bhal ase.
Kelemane Khrista bhi paap nimite bisi dukh paise. Tar ekjon dramik thakise kintu moi khan nimite dukh paise, etu pora moi khan ke Isor usorte anibole nimite. Tar ke gaw mangso te morai dise, kintu Aatma pora Tar ke jinda kori dise.
Aru Aatma pora, Tar aatma khan logote prochar koribole jaise kun eitya koidi ghor te thaki ase.
Tai khan kotha namani kene thakise Noah laga din te jetia Isor taikhan ke rokhi thakisele, jetiya etu din te dangor ekta naw bonai thakise, Isor he olop manu ke bachai loise- etu hoile ath-ta aatma ke pani pora bachai dise.
Etu etiya moi khan nimite bachai diya laga ekta baptisma laga chin ase- jeneka moi khan laga gaw pora moila dulai eneka nohoi, kintu Isor usorte bhal bhabona loi kene thakibole nimite aru etu sob tu Jisu Khrista RESURRECT huwa laga nam te.
Khrista tu Jisu laga dyna hath ase. Tar sorgo te jaise. Sorgoduth, aru adhikar, aru sob takot Tar usorte ahibole lage.
Etu nisina, jeneka Khrista mangso te dukh paise, etu nisina apuni bhi nijor ke eneka bhabona pora tayar koribi. Kelemane kun manu mangso pora dukh paise tai pap pora bachai loise.
Etu nimite, ekjon manu, tai mangso pora jinda thaka homoi te, manu laga echa pora jinda nathake kintu Isor pora ki echa kore etu te hai jinda thake.
Kelemane apuni laga pura homoi tu Isor najana manu pora kori thakise eneka hai korise, duniya laga khusi kori kene thakise, nisa hoi kene beraise, nisa pora khusi korise, duniya laga rong tamasha te thakise aru sob beya letera kam kori kene thakise.
Etu nimite, taikhan bhabise kile tu apuni taikhan logote beya kam te mila nai, etu nimite he tai khan apuni laga beya kotha koi thake.
Tai khan ki kotha aru kam korise etu laga sob hisab dibole lagibo jetiya Tar mora aru jinda khan laga bichar koribole nimite homoi ahhibo.
Etu nimite Isor laga kotha mora manu khan logote bhi prochar kori dise, kelemane, tai khan ke manu laga gaw mongso hisab te bichar korise koilebhi, tai khan aatma te jinda thakibo jeneka Isor ase.
Kintu etu sob laga khotom huwa laga homoi ahi ase. Etu nimite nijor laga bhabona sapha rakhibi, aru keneka prathana kori ase etu nisina nijor laga sob kam khan sida rakhibi.
Aru kunba manu apuni logote modot mangi kene ahile tai ke eku beya nokoi kene bhal pora sabi.
Kelemane sob manu bhi ashirbad pai kene ase, ekjon-ekjon ke modot koribole nimite etu cholabi, ari Isor laga morom thaka nisina sob kam te bisas pora koribi.
Jodi kunba manu kotha kore, tai laga kotha tu Isor laga kotha hai kobole dibi. Jodi kunba sewa kore, Isor pora ki di ase etu laga hisab te hai koribole dibi. Etu khan koribi kelemane etu sob kam te Isor laga mohima hobole dibi. Jisu Khrista laga namte aru etu pora Jisu Khrista laga mohima aru takot hodai nimite hobole dibi. Amen.
Morom bhai khan, juie pora apuni khan logote porikha kora nisina apuni khan etu dekhi kene alag bhabona nokoribi, kiba ekta alag kam apuni logote hoi thaka nisina.
Kintu, apuni khan kiman Khrista laga dukh te bhag lobo khusi koribi, kelemane eneka korile apuni khan Tar ke aru dikhai diya te Tar laga mohima sai kene anondo hobo.
Jodi apuni ke Khrista laga naam karne sorom khelai diye, apuni asirbad ase, kelemane mohima laga Aatma aru Isor laga Aatma apuni uporte thaki ase.
Kintu apuni khan kun bhi manu morai diya ekjon nisina, ekta chor nisina, paap kaam kori kene thaka manu nisina, aru manu laga majote jai kene kotha dhali diya manu nisina eneka laga kaam khan kori kene dukh napabi.
Kintu kunba manu Khristan hoi kene dukh pai, tai ke sorom pabo nadibi; hoilebi, Isor laga naam loi kene Tar ke mohima koribo dibi.
Kelemane Isor laga ghor pora he bichar shuru koribole laga homoi ahhise. Jodi etu moi khan logot pora shuru hoi, tenehoile Isor laga susamachar namani kene thaka khan nimite keneka hobo?
Aru “Jodi dramik manu khan bachibole tan ase koile,
paapi manu aru Isor ke bhoi nokora manu logote ki hobo?”
Etu nimite kun Isor laga echa te thaki kene dukh pabo tai khan nijor laga aatma tu kun sob bonai dise Tar ke he di dibo.
Etu nimite, moi pora bisi umor thaka cholawta khan mon dangor kori di ase, Moi, bhi ekjon cholawta aru Khrista laga dukh te bhag luwa ekjon gawah ase, aru moi bhi Tar ke dikhai diya homoi te Tar laga mohima sabole nimite thakibo:
Isor laga bhera khan ke cholai kene loi jai manu ekjon hobi, ekta dangor manu pora sewa kora nisina nohoi- aru apuni eneka koribole lage koi kene nahoi, kintu apuni nijor laga echa pora kori bole nimite, Isor pora apuni ke sewa koribole nimite diya nisina- sorom khabole laga laab nimite nahoi kintu nijor laga mon echa pora.
Manu khan uporte apuni ekta malik nisina hukum nocholabi kun apuni laga bharosa te thaki ase. Kintu, apuni laga bhera khan ke bhal kam tu hai dikhai dibi.
Aru jetiya asol Bhera Rukha laga Malik ahhibo aru nijor ke dikhai dibo, tetiya apuni ketiya bhi beya nohua mohima laga mukut pabo.
Etu nisina, jawan manu khan apuni khan apuni khan pora dangor umor te dangor thaka manu khan laga kotha mani kene thakibi. Apuni khan sob, morom laga kapur pora nijor ke lagai lobi aru ekjon-ekjon laga sewa koribi. Kelemane Isor phutani kora manu ke bhal napai, kintu kun nomro kore taikhan ke anugrah diye.
Etu nimite Isor laga hokti thaka hath nichete nijor ke chutu kori lobi etu pora apuni ke Tai thik homoi te uthai kene rakhi dibi.
Apuni laga sob dukh chinta Tar uporte di dibi, kelemane Tar hai apuni nimite chinta kore.
Shanti rakhibi, aru sai thakibi. Apuni laga dusman Saitan ekta hala kori ke thaka bagh nisina rukhi ase, kun ke khabole paribo etu sai ase.
Tai usorte khara hoi jabi. Apuni laga bisas tu takot korilobi. Apuni jani ase apuni laga bisasi manu khan etu prithibi te apuni khan dukh pai ase tai khan bhu eneka he dukh pai ase.
Kintu apuni khan olop din dukh pa pichete, sob asirbad diya laga Isor kun apunike Tar laga anondo jibon aru Khrista logote thakibole nimite matise, sob tu bhal kori dibo, apuni ke bonai lobo, aru apunike takot dibo.
Etu sob adhikar Tar laga hodai aru hodai nimite hobole dibi. Amen.
Moi Silvanus ekjon bisas te thaka bhai ase koi kene mane, aru moi apuni khan nimite bhal kori kene bujibole likhi dise. Moi apuni khan laga mon dangor kori di ase aru moi apuni khan logote ki likhise etu he Isor laga hosa asirbad ase. Aru apuni khan etu te he khara kori bi.
Etu maiki kun Babylon te ase, kun ke apuni logote mati loise, apuni khan ke salam di ase. Aru Mark, moi laga chokora pora apuni khan ke salam di ase.
Ekjon-ekjon ke morom laga chuma pora salam dibi.
Simon Peter, ekjon sewak aru Jisu Khrista laga pasonir, etu manu khan nimite kun moi khan nisina eke bisas tu paise, Isor laga DIVINE bisas pora aru jibon bachai diya Jisu Khrista nam te.
Ashirbad aru shanti apuni khan logote bisi hobole dibi Probhu Jisu au Isor laga gyan pora.
Kelemane Tar laga mohan takot aru jibon laga bhal kam khan moi khan ke dise aru etu sob Isor laga gyan pora he hoise.Tar laga mohima aru asirbad pora moi khan ke mati loise.
Etu pora, Tar moi khan ke asol aru dangor kosom dise, etu nimite etu khan sai kene moi khan bhi Isor laga bhal kam te bhag lobo, prithibi laga beya kam pora polai kene ahha nisina kun tu pap laga beya echa pora hoi.
Kintu etu khan nimite, apuni laga bisas te sob bhal kam tu he ahnibole bisaribi; aru bhal kam te gyan bhi dhali kene cholabi;
gyan pora nijor ke thik pora rakhibi; aru beya kam pora thik rakhibole nimite nomro hoi kene thakibi; aru nomro hoi kene bhal rasta te jabi;
bhal kam kori kene nijor bhai ke bhi morom koribi; aru bhal rasta bhai khan ke morom pora dikhai dibi.
Jodi etu khan apuni laga bhitor te thake, apuni Probhu Jisu Khrista laga gyan te ketiya bhi khali nathakibo.
Kintu kun manu logote etu khan nai tai ekta andha manu nisina he ase tai suku komjor thaka nisina ase, tai pahori jaise tai laga poila pap kam kori kene thaka sob tu maph koridisele.
Etu nimite, bhai khan, apunike ki nimite matise aru bachi lua tu bhal pora sai lobi, jodi apuni khan etu kore, apuni ketiya bhi nigiribo.
Etu pora apuni laga jibon bachai diya Probhu Jisu Khrista laga anonto raijyo te dhun pora bhorta hoi kene jabole paribo.
Etu karone moi apuni khan ke etu kotha khan kobole nimite hodai tayar thakibo, apuni khan etu janile bhi, aru etiya thaka nisina bisas te thakile bhi.
Moi apuni khan ke etu koi diya tu bhal ase, moi jiman din tak etu jaga te thakibo, etu kotha khan koi kene apuni ke bhabona koribole dibo.
Kelemane moi jani ase bisi joldi moi etu jaga tu chari bole lagibo, moi ke Probhu Jisu Khrista pora etu khan sob tu dikhai dise.
Kintu moi naja age te apuni khan sob mon te etu kotha khan rakhi thakibole nimite sob kam tu bhal pora sai lobo.
Kelemane moi khan chalak pora etu kotha khan kuwa nai jetiya moi khan pora apuni khan ke Probhu Jisu Khrista aru ahhibole laga kotha janibole dise, kintu moi khan Tar laga mohan kam kori diya laga gawah ase.
Kelemane Tar Baba Isor pora sonman aru mohima paise jetiya Tar logote ekta awaj ahhi kene mohima pora koise, “Etu moi laga morom chokora ase, Tar uporte moi bisi khusi ase.”
Moi khan nijor hunise etu awaj sorgo pora ahhi thaka jetiya moi khan Tar logote etu pobitro pahar te thakise.
Kelemane etu Isor laga kotha moi khan nimite aru bhi bhal bonai dise, aru apuni khan etu kotha te mon dile apuni nimite bhal hoithakibo, jetiya tak rati khotom nohoi kene aru phojir laga tara apunikhan laga mon te na ulai.
Etu sob pora bhi upor, apuni khan janibole lage Isor laga pobitro kotha tu kunba manu laga nijor echa pora nokoi.
Kelemane Isor laga kotha khan manu laga echa pora ana nai, kintu Isor he manu khan ke koise jetiya tai khan Pobitro Aatma pora bhorta thakise.
Kintu misa laga bhawadi khan bhi manu khan logote ahise, aru etu misa laga bhawadi khan apuni logote bhi ahibo. Tai khan lukai kene beya kam khan tai khan logote anibo, aru tai khan hosa malik ke mana koribo kun pora tai khan ke anise. Tai khan nijor uporte bhi dukh khan ani ase.
Bisi manu tai khan laga beya kam te piche koribo, aru etu pora hosa laga kotha khan ke misa bonai dibo.
Tai khan laga nijor laab nimite misa kotha koi kene thokai dibo. Bisi din pora tai khan uporte bodnam tu alchi pora thaka nohoi, aru tai khan noksan hobole tu ghumai ja nohoi.
Kelemane kun sorgoduth Tar laga kotha mananai tai khan ke bhi charanai. Kintu tai khan ke Tartarus laga niche te phelai dise aru loha pora andhera jaga te bandhi dise jetiya tak bichar laga din nahibo.
Aru, Tar pohila laga duniya ke bhi chara nai. Kintu, Tar Noah ke bachai kene rakhise, tai ekta dharmik manu thakise, aru tai logote sath jon thakise, jetiya Isor pora bisas nokora manu khan uporte dangor ban-pani anise.
Kintu Tar dharmic Lot ke bachai loise, kun ke niom nathaka manu laga beya kam aru bhabona pora dukh disele.
Aru dharmik manu khan, kun tai khan laga majote bisi din pora thaki ase, tai khan laga beya kam khan huni kene aru dikhi kene tai khan laga dharmik aatma te dukh pai thakise.
Probhu jane bhal manu khan ke keneka kori kene dukh pora ulai anibo, aru bisas nokora manu khan ke bichar kora laga din te ki sajai dibo.
Kintu etu khan sob tu hosa ase kun beya kam kori kene thake tai khan mangso laga echa pora Isor laga adhikar tu noloi. Mon dangor aru nijor echa pora thaka, tai khan mohima te thaka Isor laga beya kotha kobole nimite bhoi nokore.
Kintu etu sorgoduth kun logote dangor takot ase aru tai khan uporte sorom khilai diya laga bichar Probhu logote ahhibole nadiye.
Kintu etu khan, gyan nathaka janwar nisina ase, tai khan ke dhori kene khotom kori dibole nimite he bonaise. Aru, tai khan ki nubuje etu ke he sorom khelai ase. Tai khan laga beya te he tai khan ke khotom kori dibo.
Tai khan ki beya kam korise etu laga enam pabo. Tai khan bhabe din te ki aram pai ase etu he bhal ase. Tai khan misa kuwa aru daghi thaka manu ase. Tai khan manu ke thokai di kene khusi pai jetiya tai khan apuni logote bohi thake.
Tai khan suku ase hoilebhi beya pora bhorta hoi kene ase, aru tai khan kiman pap kori thakile bhi etu pora bhorta nohoi. Tai khan aatma komjor thaka manu khan ke beya kam koribole nimite mate, aru tai khan laga mon tu beya kam khan koribole nimite he shikai deye. Tai khan shrap thaka bacha khan ase!
Tai khan bhal rasta tu chari kene Balaam Beor laga chokora laga pichete jaise, kun dharmik nathaka laga laab tu lobole bhal pai.
Kintu tai nijor laga pap pora sajai paise- ekta kotha koribole napara gadha manu laga awaj te kotha korile dimak thik nathaka bhawadi ke rukhai diya nisina ahse.
Etu manu khan pani nathaka laga khali jhorna nisina he ase aru jetiya dangor hawa ahhe dhuwa ke urai kene loi ja manu khan nisina he ahse. Aru dukh laga andhera pora tai khan ke bandhi loi.
Kelemane tai khan matlab nathaka laga kotha kore. Tai khan gaw mangso laga echa pora manu khan ke mate. Tai khan kun manu beya aru dukh pora polabole mon kore tai khan ke prithibi laga echa khan dikhai kene mate.
Tai khan kosom dise tai khan ke beya pora ajad koribole nimite, kintu tai khan nijor bhi beya kam laga sewak khan ahse. Ki pora manu khan ke bachai lobole parise, etu nimite tai pap laga sewak hoi jaise.
Jodi tai khan Probhu Jisu Khrista laga gyan pora etu prithibi laga beya kam khan pora polai jabole pare, kintu arubi etu laga pap te phasi kene giri jai, tai khan laga pohila te ki dukh paise etu pora bhi bisi beya hobo.
Kelemane tai khan nimite dharmik laga rasta najani kene thaka tu he bhal thakise, tai khan pobitro niyom laga kotha khan jana pichete he namani kene thaka pora tu.
Etu hosa kotha tu tai khan logote hoise: “Ekta kuta nijor laga ulti khai, aru dhulai kene rakha gahori aru bhi mati te wapas jai.”
Morom laga bhai khan, etu moi laga dusra chithi apuni khan ke likhi ase; aru etu duita te bhi apuni khan laga bhal bhabona khan uthai dibole nimite likhi ahse,
Probhu aru jibon diya Isor pora Tar laga pasonir aru pobitro bhawadi khan ke ki hukum dise aru kotha khan koise apuni khan sob etu khan mon te rakhi kene thakibi.
Etu pohila jani lobi, misa kuwa manu khan ses laga din te ahhibo. Tai khan sorom khilabo aru tai khan nijor laga echa hisab te chuli kene jabo.
Tai khan kobo,''Tar ahibole kuwa laga kosom tu kote ase? Etu kotha tu rukhi kene moi khan laga baba khan bhi mori jaise, sob tu eke hoi kene ase, etu prithibi bona shuru homoi pora.”
Kelemane tai khan nijor echa pora etu pahori jaise, poila te sorgo tu thakise koi kene, aru prithibi tu pani pora he bonaise aru pani tu Isor laga kotha pora he bonaise,
aru etu kam khan pora, aage laga duniya tu khotom kori dise, dangor ban-pani ahhi kene.
Kintu etiya sorgo aru prithibi ke juie pora Tar laga hukum pora he bachai kene rakhi ase. Tai khan ke Isor najani kene thaka manu aru bichar kora laga din nimite he bachai kene rakhi ase.
Kintu etu ekta kotha apuni khan napahoribo lage, morom bhai khan, Probhu nimite ek di tu hazar sal nisina he ahse, aru hazar sal tu ek din nisina he ase.
Probhu pora ki kosom dise etu aaste pora loi najai, kunba manu bisi aaste ase koi kene koi thake. Kintu, Tar apuni uporte morom thaka nimite Tar apuni khan kun bi harai najabo nimite bhabona kore, aru sob manu mon ghurai kene thakibole nimite echa ase.
Kintu sabi, Probhu ahha laga din tu ekta chor ahha nisina hobo, aru tetiya sorgo pora dangor awaj khan ulabo. Kintu sob saman khan juie pora julai dibo, aru prithibi te ki kam korise etu khan sob tu dikhai dibo.
Isor ahha laga din tu mon khuli kene rukhi thakibi, kelemane sorgo khan bhi juie pora julai kene khotom kori dibo, aru sob saman khan juie laga gorom pora goli jabo.
Kintu Tar pora kosom diya nisina, moi khan notun sorgo aru notun prithibi nimite rukhi ase, kun jaga te khali dharmik khan hai thakibo.
Etu nimite, morom laga bhai khan, apuni khan etu sob tu rukhi thaka nisina, shanti pora Tar laga usorte dag nathaki kene aru beya kam pora dur hoi kene bhal kam kori thakibi.
Aru, probhu laga morom aru dhorjo moi laga anonto jibon pabole nimite ase koi kene bhabi bi, jeneka moi khan laga morom laga bhai Paul pora apuni khan ke likhise, gyan di kene likhibole diya nisina,
aru tai laga sob chiti te likha nisina, etu kotha khan tai khan logote koi ase. Etu kotha khan majote kunba kotha khan bujibole dikdar ahse gyan nathaka aru beya manu khan pora ulta rasta te loi jai, etu nisina tai khan Isor laga pobitro kotha bhi eneka kore, tai khan nijor he dukh pabole nimite.
Etu nimite, bhai khan, apuni khan etu sob tu aghe pora jani loise, nijor ke bhal pora sai lobi aru beya manu khan laga misa kotha khan pora pap laga rasta te najabi aru apuni khan laga bisas tu ketiya bhi harabole nidibi.
Kintu Probhu aru bachai diya Jisu Khrista laga morom aru gyan te dangor hoi kene thakibi. Sob mohima Tar laga hobole dibi etiya pora loikene hoidai tak. Amen!
Kuntu suru pora thakise- moi khan ki hunise, aru suku pora ki dekhise, moi khan ki tu saise, aru moi khan laga hath pora dhorise, eitu khan sob jibon laga kotha ase.
Aru, eitu jibon moi khan ke janibole dise, aru moi khan dekhise, aru eitu laga moi khan gawahi ase. Moi apuni khan ke ananta jibon laga kotha koi ase, kun tu Baba Isor logote ase, aru eitu kotha moi khan ke janibole nimite dise.
Moi khan ki hunise aru dekhise eitu sob apuni khan ke koi di ase, eitu pora moi khan sob mili kena morom kori thakibo. Aru,moi khan laga morom Baba Isor aru Tar laga Putro, Jisu Krista logote ase.
Aru, moi khan apuni khan nimite eitu kotha khan likhi ase eitu pora apuni khan khusi kori thaka tu pura hoi jabo.
Eitu kotha khan Tar logot pora hunise aru apuni khan ke koi ase: Isor tu puhor ase, aru Tar logote eku andhera nai.
Jodi moi khan Tar ke morom ase koi aru andhar laga rasta te berai jai, moi khan misa koi ase aru hosa laga kotha khan mani kena thakanai.
Kintu jodi moi khan ujala te berai jeneka Teo ujala te thake, moi khan ekjon-ekjon logote morom ase, aru Tar laga Putro Jisu laga khun pora moi khan laga sob paap tu sapha kori dise.
Jodi moi khan paap nai koi, moi khan nijor ke thokai ase, aru hosa tu moi khan logote nai.
Kintu jodi moi khan paap tu maph mangi loi, Tar bhal ase aru moi khan laga paap pora maph kori dibo aru sob beya kaam khan pora sapha kori dibo.
Jodi moi khan paap koranai koi, moi khan Tar ke misa bonai di ase, aru Tar laga kotha moi khan logote nai.
Moi laga bachha khan, moi apuni khan ke eitu likhi ase apuni khan paap nokoribo nimite. Kintu jodi kunba paap kore, moi khan laga Baba Isor logote kotha kori diya ekjon ase, Jisu Khrista, eitu ekjon kun dharmik ase.
Tar moi khan laga paap maph kori diya ekjon ase, aru khali moi khan nimite nohoi, kintu pura prithibi nimite.
Eitu pora moi khan Tar ke jani loise, jodi moi khan Tar laga kotha mani kene thake.
Kun manu koi, “Moi Isor ke jane,” kintu kotha mani kena nathake, tai misa kuwa manu ase, aru hosa tu tai logote nai.
Kintu kun manu kotha tu mani kena thake, Isor laga morom hosa pora tai logote thake aru tai ke sob phale pora bhal bonai dise. Eitu pora moi khan jane moi khan Tar logote ase:
kun manu koi tai Isor logote ase Tar keneka beraise eitu nisina hai berabole lage.
Morom laga bhai khan, moi apuni khan ke notun niyom likha nai, kintu pura niyom kun tu apuni khan logote suru pora ase. Eitu purana niyom hei apuni khan huni thaka laga kotha ase.
Moi apuni khan nimite notun niyom likhi di ase,Tar aru apuni usorte hosa ase, kelemane andhera tu jai ase, aru hosa laga puhor tu ujala di ase.
Kun manu koi tai ujala te ase koi kena aru nijor laga bhai ke morom nokore tai etiya bhi andhera te ase.
Kintu kun manu tai laga bhai ke ghin kore tai andhera te ase aru andhera te berai ase.Tai kote jai ase tai nijor bhi najane, kelemane andhera pora tai laga suku andha kori dise.
Moi apuni khan ke likhi ase, morom laga bachha khan, kelemane Tar laga naam pora apuni khan laga paap tu maph hoise.
Moi apuni khan ke likhi ase, baba khan, kelemane apuni khan jane eitu ekjon ke kun suru pora ase. Moi apuni khan nimite likhi ase,j uwan manu khan, kelemane apuni khan beya ekjon logote jiti loise.
Moi apuni khan ke likhi dise, chutu bachha khan, kelemane apuni khan Baba Isor ke jane. Moi eitu apuni khan ke likhise, baba khan, kelemane apuni khan jane eitu ekjon ke kun suru pora ase. Moi apuni khan ke likhise, juwan manu khan, kelemane apuni khan takot ase, aru Isor laga kotha apuni khan logote ase, aru apuni khan beya uporte jiti loise.
Eitu prithibi ke morom nokoribi aru eitu prithibi te thaka saman khan ke morom nokoribi. Jodi kunba manu eitu prithibi ke morom kore, Baba Isor laga morom tai logote nai.
Kelemane ki tu eitu prithibi te ase- mangso laga echha, aru suku laga echha, aru jibon laga phutani- eitu Baba Isor pora nohoi kintu prithibi laga ase.
Eitu prithibi laga echha khan jai ase. Kintu kun manu Isor laga echha pora thake tai hodai thakibo.
Chutu bachha khan, eitu khotom laga homoi ase. Apuni khan anti Khrista tu ahi ase koi kena hunise, aru etiya bisi anti Khrista khan ahise. Eitu pora moi khan jane khotom laga homoi tu ahise.
Tai khan moi khan pora ulai kena jaise, kintu tai khan moi khan laga nohoi. Jodi tai khan moi khan laga ase koile moi khan logote thakibo. Kintu jetiya tai khan ulai kena jaise, eitu pora janise tai khan tai khan kun bhi moi khan logote nai.
Kintu apuni khan Pobitro ekjon pora asirbad paise, aru apuni khan sob hosa tu jane.
Moi apuni khan hosa tu najane koi kena eitu likha nai, kintu apuni khan jane aru hosa te eku misa nai.
Kun misa koi ase kintu tai ekjon kun Jisu hai Khrista ase koi kena mana kore? Eitu manu anti Khrista ase, kelemane tai Baba laga chokora Jisu ke mana kore.
Kun manu Jisu ke mana kore tai logote Baba Isor nai. Kun manu Jisu ke loi tai logote Isor ase.
Aru apuni khan nimite, suru pora ki kotha hunise eitu apuni khan logote thakibole dibi. Jodi apuni khan suru pora ki hunise eitu mon te rakhe, apuni khan hodai Baba laga Putro Jisu logote thakibo.
Eitu kosom Tar pora moi khan ke dise- ananta jibon laga kotha.
Moi eitu kotha apuni khan nimite likhi ase utu manu karone kun apuni khan ke beya rasta te loi jabo.
Aru apuni khan nimite, ki tu asirbad apuni khan Tar pora paise eitu apuni khan logote thakibo, aru apuni khan ke manu pora shikai dibole nimite dorkar nai. Kintu Tar laga asirbad pora ki shikai dise eitu hosa ase aru misa nohoi, aru apuni khan ke shikai diya nisina,Tar logote thakibi.
Etiya, bachha khan,Tar logote thakibi, jetiya Tar ahibo, moi khan mon dangor koribo aru Tar aha homoi te sorom nakhabo.
Jodi apuni jane Tar dharmik ase koi kena, tetiya hoile apuni khan eitu bhi jani thakibo kun manu thik kaam kore tai Isor pora jonom hoise.
Sabi kena morom Isor pora moi khan ke dise, moi khan Isor laga bachha ase kobole nimite, aru moi khan eitu hai ase. Eitu karone, prithibi pora moi khan ke najane, kelemane tai khan Isor ke najane.
Morom thaka bhai khan, moi khan etiya Isor laga bachha ase aru moi khan ki hobo etiya bhi eitu dekhai diya nai. Moi khan jane jetiya Khrista ahibo, moi khan Tar nisina hoi jabo, kelemane Tar keneka ase eitu nisina moi khan Tar ke dekhibo.
Kun manu Tar uporte akha kori kena thake Tar sapha thaka nisina tai khan nijor ke sapha kori loi.
Kun paap kaam kori ase tai niyom kanun khan mani kena thaka nai, kelemane paap te niyom kanun nai.
Apuni jane Khrista ke dekhai dise eitu paap khan hatai dibole nimite, aru Tar logote eku paap khan nai.
Kun manu Tar logote thake tai aru paap kaam kori nathake. Aru kun manu paap kaam kore tai Isor ke dekha nai, aru Tar ke janibole para nai.
Morom laga bacha khan, kun pora bhi apuni ke beya rasta te loi jabole nidibi. Kun manu bhal kaam kore tai dharmik ase, Khrista dharmik thaka nisina.
Kun manu Isor pora jonom loise tai beya kam kori kena nathake kelemane Isor laga bijon tai logote ase.Tai paap kori kena thakibole napare kelemane tai Isor pora jonom hoise.
Eitu pora Isor laga bachha aru Saitan laga bachha khan ke dekhai diye: Kun manu dharmik kaam nokore tai Isor laga nohoi, aru kun manu tai nijor laga bhai ke morom nokore tai bhi Isor laga nohoi.
Kelemane apuni khan suru pora eitu kotha huni kena ahise, moi khan ekjon-ekjon ke morom koribole lage.
Moi khan Cain nisina nohobole lage, kun beya ekjon pora thakise aru nijor bhai ke morai dise. Ki nimite tai ke morai dise? Kelemane tai laga kaam khan beya thakise aru tai laga bhai Abel ekjon dharmik manu thakise.
Apuni khan asurit nalagibi, moi laga bhai khan jodi apuni ke eitu prithibi pora ghin kore.
Moi khan jane mora pora ulai kena jibon paise, kelemane moi khan bhai ke morom kore. Kun manu morom te nathake tai mori kena ase.
Kun manu nijor bhai ke morom nokore tai manu morai diya manu ase. Apuni jane manu morai diya manu ketiya bhi ananta jibon tai logote thakibole naparibo.
Eitu pora moi khan morom tu jane, kelemane Khrista moi khan nimite Tar laga jibon tu dise. Moi khan bhi nijor laga bhai khan nimite jibon tu dibole lage.
Kintu kun manu logote prithibi laga sob saman ase, aru tai laga bhai dukh te ase koi kena, kintu bhai nimite mon tu bon kori kena rakhe, tetiya hoile tai logote Isor laga morom tu kote ase?
Moi laga morom bachha khan, moi khan khali kotha aru mukh pora morom nokoribo, kintu kaam aru hosa pora.
Eitu pora jane moi khan hosa te ase koi kena, aru moi khan laga mon Tar usorte rakhi diye.
Jodi moi khan laga mon pora moi khan ke beya ase koi, Isor tu moi khan laga mon pora bhi dangor ase, aru Tar sob kotha tu jane.
Morom bhai khan, jodi moi khan laga nijor mon pora moi khan ke beya nokoi, moi khan Isor uporte bharosa ase.
Moi khan ki mange eitu pai jabo, kelemane moi khan Tar laga kotha mani kena thake aru Tar ki khusi pai eitu khan kora nimite.
Eitu Tar laga kotha khan ase: moi khan Tar laga Putro Jisu Khrista ke bisas koribo aru ekjon-ekjon ke morom koribo,Tar pora eitu kotha moi khan ke diya nisina.
Kun manu kotha khan mani kena thake Tar logote ase, aru Tar bhi tai khan logote ase. Eitu pora jane Tar moi khan logote ase, eitu Aatma pora kun ke moi khan nimite dise.
Morom laga bhai khan, sob atma ke bisas nokoribi. Kintu, kuntu tu atma Isor pora ase eitu bhal pora sai lobi, kelemane bisi misa laga bhawadi khan prithibi te ulai kena ase.
Eitu pora apuni khan Isor laga Aatma tu janibo- kun manu Jisu Khrista mangso te Isor pora ahise koi kena shikar kore,
aru kun atma Jisu Isor pora ase koi kena shikar nokore. Eitu anti krista laga atma ase, kun tu apuni khan ahi thaka tu hunise, aru etiya tai prithibi te ase.
Apuni khan Isor pora ase, morom laga bachha khan, aru tai khan ke jiti loise, kelemane eitu ekjon kun apuni logote ase Tar eitu prithibi te thaka ekjon pora bhi sob se dangor ase.
Tai khan prithibi laga ase; eitu nimite tai khan ki koi eitu prithibi laga hai ase, aru prithibi laga manu khan tai khan laga kotha hai hune.
Moi khan Isor pora ase. Kun manu Isor ke jane moi khan laga kotha hune. Aru kun manu Isor pora nohoi moi khan laga kotha nahune. Eitu pora moi khan jane hosa laga atma aru misa laga atma.
Morom laga bhai khan, moi khan ekjon-ekjon ke morom koribo, kelemane morom tu Isor pora hai ahhe, aru kun manu morom kore tai Isor pora jonom loise, kelemane Isor tu morom ase.
Kun manu morom koribole najane tai Isor ke najane, kelemane Isor tu morom ase.
Kelemane Isor laga eitu morom moi khan ke dekhai diya nimite, Isor pora Tar laga ekta bachha ke prithibi te pothai dise aru eitu pora moi khan sob Tar logote jinda hoi jabo.
Eitu morom te, moi khan pora morom kora laga nohoi, kintu Tar pora morom kora laga ase, aru Tar laga ekta bachha ke pothai se moi khan ke paap pora bachha bole nimite.
Kun manu bhi Isor ke ketiya bhi dekha nai. Jodi moi khan ekjon-ekjon ke morom kore, Isor moi khan logote ase, aru Tar laga morom moi khan ke bhal bonai dise.
Eitu pora Tar moi khan logote ase koi kena jane, kelemane Tar laga Aatma moi khan ke dise.
Aru, moi khan dekhise aru eitu laga gawahi ase Baba Isor pora Tar laga Putro ke eitu prithibi te pothaise paap pora bacha bole nimite.
Kun manu nijor mukh pora shikar kore Jisu hai Isor laga bachha koi kena,Isor tai logote ase aru tai bhi Isor logote ase.
Aru, Isor pora moi khan ke morom kora tu janise aru bisas korise. Isor tu morom ase, aru kun manu eitu morom te thake tai Isor logote ase,aru Isor bhi tai logote ase.
Eitu nimite, morom tu moi khan laga majote bhal bonai dise, eitu pora moi khan bichar kora laga din te bharosa kori kena thakibo, kelemane Tar thaka nisina, jeneka moi khan eitu prithibi te thaki ase.
Morom te eku bhoi nai. Kintu, hosa morom sob bhoi tu phelai diye, kelemane bhoi tu sajai pabole nimite ase. Kintu kun manu bhoi kore morom tu tai logote nai.
Moi khan morom kore kelemane Isor pora pohila moi khan ke morom korise.
Jodi kunba manu koi, “Moi Isor ke morom kore,” kintu nijor laga bhai ke ghin kore, tai misa koi ase. Kun manu tai laga nijor bhai ke morom nokore, kun tai dekhise, Isor ke ketiya bhi morom koribole naparibo, kun ke tai dekha nai.
Aru, eitu hai shikai diya kotha ase kun tu moi khan Tar nimite rakhise, kun manu Isor ke morom kore tai nijor laga bhai ke bhi morom koribole lage.
Kun manu Jisu he Khrista ase koi kene bisas kore tai Isor pora jonom loise, aru kun manu Baba Isor ke morom kore Tar pora jonom kora bacha ke bhi morom kore.
Etu pora jane moi khan Isor laga bacha khan ke morom kore.
Kelemane etu he Isor nimite morom ase: moi khan Tar laga kotha mani kene thaka tu. Tar laga kotha khan bhari nohoi.
Kun manu Isor pora jonom loise tai prithibi ke jiti loise. Etu pora moi khan prithibi te jiti loise, aru moi khan laga bisas bhi.
Kelemane kun Isor pora ahise tai prithibi tu jiti loise, tetiya hoile etu ekjon ke kun bisas kore Tar Isor laga bacha Jisu ase koi kene.
Etu ekjon ase kun pani aru khun pora ahise: Jisu Khrista. Tar khali pani pora ahha nai, kintu pani aru khun pora ahise. Etu Aatma pora he gawahi dise kelemane Aatma tu hosa ase.
Kelemane tate tinjon ase kun eiu laga gawah ase:
etu Aatma, aru pani, aru khun. Etu tinta eke logote mili kene ase.
Jodi moi khan manu laga gawahi loi, Isor laga gawahi etu pora bhi dangor ase. Kelemane Isor laga gawahi eneka ase, Tar laga Putro Jisu laga gawahi dise.
Kun manu Isor laga bacha ke bisas kore tai nijor laga gawahi ase. Kun manu Isor ke bisas nokore Tar ke misa bonai dise, kelemane tai Isor pora Tar laga Putro laga gawahi diya tu bisas kora nai.
Etu gawahi ase: Isor moi khan ke anonto jibon dise, aru etu jibon Tar laga Putro Jisu logote ase.
Kun manu logote Jisu ase tai jibon paise. Kintu kun manu logote Isor laga Putro Jisu nai tai jibon panai.
Moi apuni khan ke etu kotha khan likhi ase etu pora apuni khan anonto jibon ase koi kene janibo- apuni khan kun Isor laga Putro Jisu Khrista laga nam te bisas kore.
Aru, etu bharosa moi khan Tar logote ase koi kene jane, jodi Tar laga echa hisab te moi khan mange, Tar moi khan ke hunibo.
Aru, jodi Tar moi khan ke hune koi kene jane- moi khan Tar logote ki mangibo- Tar logote moi khan ki mangise etu sob paise koi kene jane.
Jodi kunba manu tai laga bhai ke pap kam kori thaka dikhe aru etu pora mora nai koile, tai prathana koribole lage, aru Isor pora tai ke jibon dibo. Moi etu khan ke koi ase kun pap kori kene mora tu dikha nai. Kunba pap tu mora dikhi pai; Moi etu nimite prathana koribole lage koi kene kuwa nai.
Moi khan jane kun manu Isor pora jonom hoise tai pap nokore. Kintu tai ekjon kun Isor pora jonom hoise tai ke bachai kene rakhe, aru saitan pora tai ke dukh dibole naparibo.
Moi khan Isor pora ase koi kene jane, aru moi khan jane pura prithibi tu ekjon beya thaka laga shakti te ase.
Kintu moi khan jane Isor laga Putro pora ahhi kene moi khan ke gyan dise, etu pora Tar hosa ase koi kene moi khan janibo. Aru, moi khan Tar logote ase kun hosa ase, Tar laga Putro Jisu Khrista. Etu ekjon hosa Isor aru anonto jibon ase.
Bacha khan, nijor ke murti khan pora bachai kene rakhibi.
Cholauta khan pora loi kene bachi luwa maiki khan aru tai laga bacha khan, kun ke moi hosa te morom kore- aru moi ekela nohoi, kintu kun manu hosa tu janise tai khan bhi morom kore-
kelemane hosa tu moi khan logote thaki ase aru etu hodai nimite moi khan logote thakibo.
Morom, daya, aru shanti Baba Isor aru Jisu Khrista laga asirbad apuni khan logote thakibo, Baba laga Putro, hosa aru morom te.
Moi bisi khusi kori ase etu huni kene apuni khan laga kunba bacha khan hosa laga rasta te berai ase, jeneka moi khan Baba Isor pora moi khan etu niyom tu paise.
Etiya moi apuni ke anurodh kori ase, maiki- moi apuni khan ke notun niyom likhi kene dibole nimite nohoi, kintu shuru pora ekta niyom thaka tu- moi khan ekjon-ekjon ke morom koribole lage.
Etu morom ase, Tar laga niyom kanun hisab te berai kene jabole lage. Etu niyom ase, shuru pora apuni huna nisina, apuni etu rasta te he berabole lage.
Kelemane prithibi te manu khan ke thokai diya bisi jai kene ase, aru tai khan etu shikar nokore Jisu Khrista manu khan nimite gaw mangso hoi kene ahise. Tai khan thokai diya manu aru Khrista birodh ANTICHRIST te ase.
Nijor ke sai lobi, moi khan ki nimite kam korisele apuni etu naharabo karone, kintu etu pora apuni pura asirbad tu pabo.
Kun manu Jisu Khrista pora ki shikai dise etu noloi kene age te jai ase tetiya hoile tai logote Isor nai. Kun manu etu kotha khan mani kene thake, tai logote Baba Isor aru bacha Jisu Khrista bhi ase.
Kun manu apuni laga usorte ahhe aru eneka nishikai, tai ke ghor bhitor te namati bhi aru tai ke salam nidibi.
Kun tai ke salam diye, tai laga beya kam khan te tai bhi bhag loi kene ase.
Moi apuni khan logote bisi kotha likhi bole ase, kintu moi kagos te aru ink pora etu kotha khan likhi bole mon nai. Hoilebhi, moi apuni khan logote ahhi kene ekjon-ekjon logote kotha koribole mon ase, etu pora apuni khan laga khusi aru bhi bisi dangor hobo.
Apuni khan pora bachi luwa bhoini laga bacha khan pora bhi salam di ase.
Morom thaka Gaius ekjon cholawta, kun ke moi hosa pora morom kore.
Morom laga bhai, Moi prathana kore apuni logote sob thakibo aru apuni laga gaw bhi bhal thakibo, apuni laga aatma bhal kori kene thaka nisina.
Kelemane moi khusi pai jetiya bhai khan pora ahhi kene apuni hosa te bera laga gawahi diye, apuni hosa te berai thaka nisina.
Moi etu pora aru dangor khusi nai, jetiya moi laga bacha khan hosa rasta te berai ahse koi kene hune.
Morom laga bhai khan ,apuni bisas pora ki kori ahse etu apuni bhai khan nimite aru bahar manu khan nimite kori ahse
kun pora apuni khan laga morom kora laga gawahi girja manu khan laga usorte dise. Isor laga usorte bhal mohima hobole nimite apuni khan manu ke bhal pora sai kene tai khan ke pothai dibi,
kelemane Isor laga nam nimite tai khan ulai kene jaise, aru dusra jat manu khan pora eku luwa nai.
Moi khan bhi tai khan ke matibole lage, etu pora moi khan bhi hosa te kam kora sathi hoi jabo.
Moi manu khan nimite kiba likhise, kintu Diotrephes, kun manu laga ahge te thakibole nimite bhal pai, moi khan ke mati bole mon nai.
Morom laga bhai khan, beya kam khan nokoribi kintu ki tu bhal kam ahse etu he koribi. Kun manu bhal kam kore tai Isor laga ahse; aru kun manu beya kam kore tai Isor ke dikha nai.
Demetrius hosa pora tai nijor laga gawah diye. Kintu moi khan bhi gawahi diye, aru apuni khan jane moi khan laga gawahi tu hosa ahse.
Moi apuni khan ke bisi kotha likhi bole ahse, kintu moi kolom aru ink pora etu kotha khan apuni khan ke likhi bole mon nai.
Kintu moi apuni khan ke joldi lok pabole echa kori ahse, tetiya moi khan ekjon-ekjon logote bohi kene kotha koribo.
Apuni khan logote shanti thaki bole dibi. Sathi khan bhi apuni khan ke salam di ahse. Nam loi kene tate thaka sathi khan ke salam di dibi.
Jude, Jisu Khrista laga ekjon sewak, aru James laga bhai, kun khan ke mati loise, Baba Isor laga morom bhai khan, aru Jisu Khrista nimite rakhise:
Daya aru shanti aru morom apuni khan logote bhorta hoi thakibole dibo.
Morom thaka bhai khan, moi khan laga anonto jibon pabole laga kotha apuni khan logote likhi bole kosis korise, moi apuni khan ke mon dangor kori dibole nimite eitu likhi ase pobitro manu khan nimite ki kaam koribole dise eitu bisas aru mon pora dukh uthai kena hoile bi kori kena thakibi.
Kelemane apuni khan majot pora kunba manu khan lukai kena beya rasta te jaise, kun ke pohila pora khotom kori dibole nimite koi dise, beya manu khan pap laga kam pora Isor laga morom tu bodli kori dise, aru tai Jisu Khrista Probhu aru malik ase koi kene namane.
Etiya moi apuni khan ke etu kobole nimite echa kori ase- apuni khan etu pura jani kene thakile bi- Jisu pora Egypt laga jaga pora manu khan ke bachai loise, kintu pichete kun manu Tar laga kotha namane tai khan ke khotom kori dise.
Aru sorgoduth khan kun nijor laga adhikar diya tu bhal pora cholanai, kintu tai laga asol thaka jaga tu chari dise- Isor pora tai khan ke ketiya bi khulibole napara laga loha rusi pora bandhi dise, andhera jaga te, jetiya tak bichar laga din ahhi kene napunche.
Sodom aru Gomorah laga nagar tai khan laga age te thaka nisina, tai khan pora kori kena thaka nisina aru tai khan bhi nijor ke beya beyobichari laga kam te dhali dise, aru ki tu Isor pora koribole diya nai etu laga beya echa kam khan he korise. Tai khan dusra manu khan nimite ekta sakhi hoise kun norok laga juie te dukh pai kene jolibo.
Etu nisina he sapna dikhi thaka manu khan nijor laga gaw tu letera kori ase. Kintu tai khan Isor laga adhikar tu namane, aru tai khan orgo te thaka Isor laga beya kotha khan kori thake.
Kintu sorgoduth Michael bi, jetiya tai saitan logote lorai kori thakise aru Moses laga gaw nimite kotha nimili kene thakise, tai uporte ek dum beya laga bichar ani diya nai. Kintu tai koise, “Probhu he tumi ke tumi ke gali dibi!”
Kintu etu manu khan tai khan ki nubuje etu laga ulta koi kene berai thake, aru tai khan nijor laga bhabana pora ki janise, etu hoile eku najana ekta janwar nisina he ase, etu pora tai khan khotom hoi jai.
WOE tai khan ke! Kelemane tai khan Cain laga rasta te berai se aru murti puja kori kene kiba laab pabole nimite bisari se. Tai khan Korah pora kotha namani kene thaka logote he harai jaise.
Etu khan tu hoile apuni khan morom laga kha luwa jagate lukai kene thaka tate ulai thaka jongol nisina ase, jetiya apuni khan logote sorom nathaki kene eke logote kha luwa kore-bhera rukha manu kun tai nijor he khai. Tai khan badal nathaki kene pani gira nisina he ase, aru hawa pora loi jai. Tai khan sukha mohina laga ghas te phol ulabole napara nisina he ase- duibar morise, aru jor pora ulai kene phelai dise.
Tai khan samundar te beya hawa jai thaka nisina ase, tai khan nijor laga sorom tu ulai kene dikhai ase.Tai khan eku akha nathakikene berai thaka tara nisina he ase, aru tai nimite dukh laga andhera tu hodai nimite rakhi dise.
Kintu Enoch bi, Adam laga pichete ahha ekjon, tai khan nimite eneka bhawani korise, aru koise, “Sabi! Probhu Tar laga hazar-hazar pobitro khan pora thaka khan ke loi kene ani ase.
Tar sob uporte bichar koribole nimite ahhi ase. Tar ahhi ase etu manu khan nimite kun Isor ke noloi kene pap laga beya kam kori kene thakise, aru kiman Isor ke bhoi nokori kene tai laga uporte beya kotha khan korise etu khan laga bichar koribole nimite Tar ahhi ase.”
Tai khan dusra logote khusi pora nathaka manu, hodai manu laga beya kotha koi thaka manu, kun nijor laga beya echa te berai thake. Tai khan laga mukh pora phutani laga kotha ulai thake, kun, nijor laga laab nimite dusra manu ke phusla laga kotha korikene berai thake.
Kintu apuni, morom laga bhai khan, Probhu Jisu Khrista laga pasonir khan pora aage te ki koi dise etu khan sob yad koribi.
Tai khan apuni ke koise, “Duniya khotom hobole thaka homoi te misa kuwa manu khan ulabo aru tai khan nijor laga beya echa pichete he jabo.”
Eitu khan nimite sob alag hoi jai ase; tai khan duniya laga ase aru tai khan logote Aatma nai.
Kintu apuni, morom laga bhai khan, dangor pobitro bisas pora apuni nijor ke bonai lobi, aru Pobitro Aatma pora prathana koribi.
Apuni nijor ke Isor laga morom te rakhibi, aru Jisu Khrista laga anonto jibon aru daya nimite rukhi thakibi kun tu apuni khan nimite ahni ase.
Kintu dusra manu khan ke jui pora ulai kene bachai loi. Isor ke bhoi koribi aru dusra khan uporte daya koribi. Aru mangso laga echa pora letera kora kapra ke ghin koribi.
Etiya ekjon kun apuni ke giri bole thaka pora bachai kene rakhe aru Tar laga mohima usorte eku golti aru letera nathaki kene khusi pora khara koribole diye,
moi khan laga Isor aru bachai diya Probhu Jisu Khrista ke, mohima hobole dibi, Tar laga sundarta, aru sob uporte raj koribole pora, aru takot, sob homoi te, etiya aru hodai tak thakibole dibo. Amen.
Etu Jisu Khrista laga jonai diya kotha ahse Isor he tai laga sewak khan ke etu kotha dise ki tu joldi pura hobole ahse. Etu kotha khan Tai laga sewak John ke Tai laga sorgoduth pothai kene janibole dise.
John Isor laga kotha tu gawah dise aru Jisu Khrista ki kam korise etu laga gawahi bi dise, etu khan tai sob dikhaise.
Asirbad ahse jun etu kotha pure aru etu kotha laga PROPHECY hune aru ki likha ase etu mani thake, kelemane homoi tu usor ahhi ase.
John, Asia te sat-ta girja thaka khan ke koi ase: Isor laga daya tumi khan logote thakibole dibi aru tai laga shanti jun ase, aru thakise, aru jun ahhibole ase, aru sat-ta aatma jun tai laga sinhasan usorte ase,
aru Jisu Khrista pora, ekjon bisas te thaka gawahi, mora pora prothom ekjon jonom luwa, aru duniya laga raja khan ke cholai kene thaka aru ekjon kun moi khan ke morom kore aru tai laga khun pora moi khan laga sob pap tu maph kori dise-
Tai moi khan ke ekta raijyo bonai dise, Isor aru baba laga ekta moha purohit tai laga mohima aru takot hodai nimite hobole dibi. Amen.
Sabi, Tai badal logote ahhi ahse;
Sob suku pora tai ke dikhibo,
Jun manu Tai ke marise tai khan be etu dikhibo.
Duniya te jiman jat ahse etu khan sob Tai nimite mon dukh hoi kene kandibo.
Hoi, Amen.
“Moi Alpha aru Omega ahse,” Probhu Isor he koise, “Jun etiya ase, aru aage pora thakise, aru kun ahhibole ahse, sob pora Mohan.”
Moi, John- apunikhan laga bhai aru ekjon jun Tai laga raijyo nimite eke logote mili kene dukh korise, aru nomro kori kene Jisu nimite sob kam korise- Moi Patmos laga ekta majuli majote ekta jaga te thakise kelemane Isor laga kotha aru Jisu laga gawahi nimite.
Moi aatma te thakise Probhu laga din te, aru moi laga piche pora ekta bigul nisina jor awaz hunise.
Aru koise, “Tumi ki dikhi ahse etu kitab te likhibi, aru sat-ta girja khan te pothai dibi- Ephesus, Smyrna, Pergamum, Thyatira, Sardis, Philadelphia, aru Laodicea khan ke.”
Moi pichete ghuri kene kun pora moi ke kotha kori ahse etu saise, aru jitiya moi ghuri kene saise ta te sat-ta suna laga MOMBATI rakha laga saman dikhise.
Aru etu lampstand laga majote ekjon manu laga bacha nisina thakise, tai lagai kene thaka kapra tai laga paw niche tak thakise aru suna laga ekta kapur chati te lagai kene thakise.
Tai laga matha aru chuli ekta norom kapur bona rusi nisina boga thakise aru borop nisina boga thakise aru tai laga suku juie julai thaka nisina thakise.
Tai laga paw bhal pora sapha kori kene thaka ekta pitol nisina thakise, juie pora pitol ke bonai diya nisina, aru tai laga awaz nodi te pani jai thaka laga awaz nisina thakise.
Tai laga dyna hath te sat-ta tara thakise aru ekta talwar jun tu dui phale pora dhar ahse etu tai laga mukh pora ulai thakise. Tai laga chehera suryo nisina ujala di thakise.
Jitiya moi tai ke dikhise, Moi Tai laga paw nichete ekta mora manu giri juwa nisina giri jaise. Tai laga dyna hath moi uporte rakhise, aru koise, “Tumi bhoi nokoribi. Moi he shuru aru moi he antim ahse,
Aru etiya moi jinda ahse. Moi mori jaisile, kintu sabi, moi hodai aru hodai nimite jinda ahse! Aru moi logote mora aru etu prithibi nichete thaka Hades laga chabi ahse.
Etu nimite tumi ki dikhai ahse etu sob likhi lobi aru etiya ki ahise aru ki tu pichete hobole ahse.
“Ephesus girja laga sorgoduth nimite likhibi:
‘Etu jun manu laga dyna hath te sat-ta tara dhori ahse aru kun etu sat-ta suna laga LAMPSTAND uporte berai ahse, enika koi ahse:
“Moi jani ahse tumi khan laga kam aru dukh kori thaka tu aru tumi khan nomro pora dukh uthai kene thaka tu, aru tumi beya kam kori thaka manu khan ke bhal napai. Tumi, khan bhal kori kene sai kun manu tai pasonir ahse koi kene tumi khan usorte ahhe kintu tai khan nohoi, aru tai khan misa koi ahse koi kene tumi khan jani loi.
Moi jane apuni khan dorjo korikene sob dukh khan uthai thakise, aru apuni khan moi laga nam nimite bisi dukh paise, hoilebi apunikhan alchi hoa nai.
Kintu moi apuni khan ke birodh kori ahse kelemane tumi khan laga prothom morom tu pahori kene chari jaise.
Kintu etu yad koribi kuntu jaga pora tumi khan girise. Mon ghurabi aru ki kam prothom te kori thakise etu koribi. Kintu eneka nohoi koile, Moi ahibo aru tumi khan laga jaga pora etu lampstand tu hatai dibo- jodi tumi khan mon naghurai.
Kintu etu tumi logote ahse: Tumi Nicolaitan khan para kam kora tu ghin kore, moi bi etu ghin kore.
Jun manu logote kan ahse, hunibi ki tu aatma pora koi ahse girja khan ke. Kun manu sob tu pari kene jiti loi tai ke moi jibon laga ghas pora khabole nimite dibo aru etu Isor laga paradise te ahse.’””
“Smyrna girja laga sorgoduth khan ke likhibi:
‘Etu ekjon kun prothom aru antim ahse, jun mori jaisile aru kun mora pora jinda hoi jaise, enika koi ahse:
“Moi jani ahse tumi khan dukh pai kene thaka tu (kintu tumi khan dhuni ahse) aru moi jane kun manu misa koi kene taikhan Yahudi ahse koi, kintu tai khan nohoi. Kintu tai khan Satan laga synagogue ahse.
Bhoi nokoribi dukh pabole thaka nimite. Sabi! Satan pora tumi khan kunba ke kaidi-ghor te phelai dibole ahse tumi khan laga mon tu sabole nimite, aru tumi khan dos din tak dukh pabo. Nomora tak bisasi hoi thakibi, aru titiya moi tumi khan ke jibon laga mukut dibo.
Kun manu logote kan ahse, huni lobi aatma pora girja khan ke koi ahse. Kun manu sob tu pai kene jiti loi tai aru duibar dukh pai kene nomoribo.’””
“Pergamum girja laga sorgoduth khan ke likhibi:
‘Eitu ekjon kun logote dui phale dhar thaka talwar ahse enika koi ahse.
“Moi jane tumi kote thaki ahse, jun jaga te Satan laga sinhasan ahse tate. Holebi tumi khan moi laga nam tu loi thake aru tumi khan moi uporte bisas kori thaka tu bi chara nai. Moi laga gawah kori kene thaka Antipas laga homoi te bi, moi laga ekjon bisasi, tumi khan majote mori dise, jun jaga te Satan thake.
Kintu moi tumi khan laga birodh te ahse: Tumi khan majote Balaam laga shikai diya kotha etiya bhi kunba dhori kene ahse, kun pora Balak ke Israel laga bacha khan usorte dukh digdar anibole nimite dise, tai khan ke murti puja kori kene diya laga khan khilai kene biya kam koribole dibo nimite.
Etu nimite, etu nisina he tumi khan majote bi Nicolaitan khan pora shikai diya tu eneka dhori kene ahse.
Mon ghurabi, etu nimite! Kintu jodi tumi khan eneka nokore, moi tumi khan usorte joldi ahhibo aru moi laga mukh te talwar thaka loi kene tumi khan logote lorai koribo.
Kun manu logote kan ahse, hunibi kintu aatma pora girja khan ke koi ahse kun manu sob kori kene jiti loi, moi lukai kene rakhi thaka manna tai khan ke dibo, aru moi taike ekta boga pathor dibo aru tate ekta nutun nam pathor te likhi kene thakibo, etu nam kun pora bi najanibo khali kun ke etu pathor dibo tai pora he janibo.’”
“Thyatira girja laga sorgoduth khan ke likhibi:
‘Isor laga Putro, kun laga suku juie juli thaka nisina ahse, aru tai laga paw sapha kori kene rakhi thaka ekta pitol nisina ahse, eneka koi ahse:
“Moi tumi khan laga kam jani ahse, tumi khan laga morom, tumi khan laga bisas, tumi khan laga kam, aru nomro pora sob dukh loi kene thaka. Tumi khan aage te kora kam pora tu etiya kori thaka kam he dangor ahse.
Kintu moi tumi khan logote etu birodh kori ahse: Tumi khan mon biya paile bi Jezebel ke eku kuwanai, kun tai nijor ke ekta bhaobadi koi. Tai pora shikai diya kotha khan moi laga sewak khan ke beyobichar kam koribole dibo nimite chalak kore aru murti ke puja kori kene khana kha luwa khan anikene tai khan ke khabole diye.
Moi tai ke mon ghurabole nimite homoi dise, kintu tai laga beya kam tu chari kene mon ghurabole nimite echa nai.
Sabi! Moi tai ke bimar laga bisna te phelai dibo, aru kun manu tai logote mili kene beya kam kore tai khan ke bi dangor dukh dibo, jodi tai khan laga pap aru beya pora mon noghurai le.
Kintu jiman manu Thyatira te ahse aru manu khan jun etu kotha khan mani kene nathake, aru kiman manu Satan laga bhitor kotha aru kam khan najane- Tumi khan ke moi koi ahse, ‘Moi tumi khan uporte aru dusra bhar nadhalibo.’
Kintu moi naha tak bhal kori kene sob kotha khan mani kene thakibi.
Kun manu hekh tak sob kam te jiti kene, aru kun manu moi laga kam khotom nahuwa tak kore, tai ke moi desh khan uporte adhikar dibo.
‘Tai loha laga lathi pora tai khan uporte raj koribo,
Mati pora bonai diya kolsi nisina, tai etu sob tukra kori kene bhangai dibo.’
Jeneka Moi laga Baba pora moi paise, Moi bhi tai ke phujur laga tara dibo.
Kun manu logote kan ahse, hunibi ki tu Aatma pora girja khan ke koi ahse.’””
“Sardes girja laga sorgoduth khan ke likhibi:
‘Etu ekjon kun Isor laga sat-ta aatma dhori kene ahse aru sat-ta tara dhori kene ahse eneka koi ahse: “Moi tumi khan laga kam jane. Tumi khan jinda ahse koi kene bhal nam pora thaki ahse, kintu tumi khan mora ahse.
Uthibi aru ki tu bachi kene ahse etu ke takot kori lobi kun tu moribole ahse, kelemane moi laga Isor laga suku usorte tumi khan laga kam pura kori kene thaka dikha nai.
Yad koribi, etu karone, tumi khan ki paise aru hunise. Mani thakibi, aru mon ghurabi. Kintu tumi khan ghumai thaka pora nauthile, Moi chor nisina ahibo, aru tumi khan najanibo moi kuntu homoi te tumi khan laga birodh te ahhibo.
Kintu kunba manu Sardis te ahse tai khan laga kapra letera koranai, aru tai khan moi logote berabo, boga kapur lagabo, kelemane tai khan etu pabole nimite layak ase.
Kun manu tai khan nisina sob kotha tu mani kene jiti loi tai khan bi boga kapur lagai dibo, aru tai laga nam tu ketiya bi Jibon laga Kitab pora hatai nidibo, aru tai laga nam Moi Baba usorte lobo, aru tai laga pobitro sorgoduth majote kobo.
Kun manu logote kan ahse, hunibi ki tu Aatma pora girja khan ke koi ahse.’””
“Philadelphia girja laga sorgoduth khan ke likhibi:
‘Pobitro ekjon, hosa ekjon
David, laga chabi dhori kena thaka ekjon,
Tai para khulile aru kun para bhi bon nokore,
aru jetiya tai bon kori diye kun para bhi aru nukhule, Tai hai eneka koi ahse:
“Moi tumi khan laga kam jani ahse. Sabi, Moi tumi khan usorte ekta khula dorja khuli kene rakhi di ahse kun pora bi etu bon koribole naparibo. Kelemane tumi khan logote takot komti ahse, hoilibi tumi khan moi laga kotha mani kene thakise aru moi laga nam kobole charanai.
Sabi! Moi Satan laga synagogue uporte bichar koribo tai khan kun Yahudi ahse koi. Hoilebi tai khan nahoi, kintu, tai khan misa kuwa manu ahse- Sabi, Moi taikhan tumi khan laga paw nichete ahhi kene tumi khan ke pranam koribole dibo, titiya tai khan janibo moi tumi khan ke kiman morom korise.
Tumi khan moi laga kotha nomro hoi kene mani thaka nimite, Moi bi tumi khan ke porikhya kora laga homoi pora bachai kene rakhibo kuntu pura prithibi nimite ahibole ahse, kun manu duniya te thaki ahse tai khan ke porikha koribole nimite.
Moi joldi ahhi ahse. Tumi khan logote ki ahse etu dhori kene rakhibo kun pora bi tumi laga mukut tu loi najabole nimite.
Kun manu sob mani kene jiti loi, moi taike Isor laga ghor te ekta bhal KHAMBA bonai kene rakhibo. Aru etu jaga pora tai ketiya bi bahar te ulai kene najabo, aru tai uporte moi Isor laga nam likhi dibo, moi laga Isor laga desh nam tu likhidibo (Notun Jerusalem, kuntu sorgo pora nichete ahhe, Moi laga Isor pora) aru Moi laga notun nam.
Kun logote kan ahse, hunibi ki tu Aatma pora girja khan ke koi ahse.’””
“Laodicea girja laga sorgoduth khan nimite likhibi: ‘Hosa ekjon bisasi aru ekta hosa te thaka manu, sob ke shuru pora cholai kene loi juwa Isor hai eneka koi ahse:
Etu karone tumi khan olop gorom ahse- ekdom gorom aru ekdom thanda bi nohoi- Moi laga mukh pora tumi khan ke ulti kori kene phelai dibole ahse.
Kelemane tumi khan koise, ‘Moi dhuni ahse moi logote bisi dhun sampati ahse, aru moi ke eku dorkar nai.’ Kintu tumi khan nijor najane ki halat te tumi khan thaki ahse, tumi khan sob se dukh te thaka manu ahse, bechara, gorib, andha aru lengta ase .
Moi tumi khan ke juie pora mari kene bonai rakha suna kini bole nimite koise aru etu pora tumi khan dhuni hobole nimite, aru ekdom bhal sapha boga kapur nijor lagai kene tumi khan laga sorom tu manu ke nedikha bole nimite koisile, aru suku sapha kori kene dikhi bole nimite bhal molom lobole korisile.
Moi morom kora manu khan ke bhal rasta te anibole nimite shikai diye. Etu karone, hosa pora mon ghurabi.
Sabi, Moi dorja usorte khara kori kene khot-khotai ahse. Jodi kunba moi laga awaz tu huni kene dorja tu khule, Moi tai logote ahhibo, aru tai logote khabo, aru tai bi Moi logote thakibo.
Kun manu sob tu mani kene jiti loi, Moi laga sinhasan usorte bohibole nimite adhikar dibo, Moi Baba laga sinhasan te bohibole nimite moi bi sob tu mani kene jiti loise.
Kun manu logote kan ahse, hunibi kitu Aatma pora girja khan ke koi ahse.’””
Etu sob huwa pichete moi saise, aru sabi- sorgo te ekta khula dorja! Juntu prothom awaz moi hunise moi logote bigul nisina kotha koi thakise, aru koise, “Yate uporte ahibi, aru moi tumi ke etu pichete ki hobole ahse etu sobtu dikhai dibo.”
Etu homoi te moi aatma te thakise aru sabi- ekta sinhasan sorgo te rakhi dise! Aru kunba ekjon etu sinhasan te bohi thakise.
Etu ekjon kun tate bohi thakise tai ekta ujala diya jasper aru carnelian pathor nisina dikhi thakise. Tai laga sinhasan usorte dhanush thakise kun tu sabole alag-alag rong thaka emerald pathor pora bonai kene rakha nisina dikhise.
Aru etu sinhasan usorte aru bi twenty-four sinhasan thakise, aru etu sinhasan te twenty hour dangor cholawta khan boga kapur lagai kene bohi thakise, aru tai khan laga matha te suna laga mukut lagai kene thakise.
Aru etu sinhasan pora bijili laga ujala ulai thakise, awaz di kene, aru THUNDER nisina dangor awaz ulai thakise. Sat-ta juie laga diya tai khan laga sinhasan usorte jolai thakise, etu khan Isor laga sat-ta aatma thakise.
Aru etu sihasan agete shisa laga samundar nisina thakise, crystal pathor nisina. Aru etu sinhasan majote aru etu sinhasan usorte charte jinda janwar thakise, aghe pichete suku pora bhorta hoi kene thaka dikhise.
Pohila jinda thaka janwar tu bagh nisina thakise, dusra jinda thaka janwar chutu goru laga bacha nisina thakise, tisra jinda janwar manu laga chehera nisina thakise aru charta ula jinda thaka janwar uri thaka chil chiriya nisina thakise.
Sob charta janwar laga choita pankha thakise, tai laga upor aru bhitor te bi suku pora bhorta thakise. Rati aru din tai khan koi thake,
“Pobitro, pobitro, pobitro Probhu Isor Mohan ahse,
Tai thakise, Tai ahse, aru kun ahibole ahse.”
Jitiya jinda thaka janwar khan para tai ke mohima diya, adar, aru dhonyabad ekjon kun sinhasan te bohi ahse tai ke diye, ekjon kun jinda ahse hodai aru hodai nimite,
aru twenty-four cholawta khan ekjon sinhasan te bohi thaka agete giri jai, aru Tai ke aradhana kore kun hodai aru hodai nimite jinda ahse. Tai khan laga mukut ulai kene Tai laga sinhasan agete rakhi kene koi thake,
“Sob mohima apuni laga ahse, moi khan laga Probhu aru Isor,
Sob adar, aru mohima aru takot,
Apuni sob tu bonai dise,
Aru Apuni laga echa pora sob tu hoise aru bonai dise.”
Titiya moi dikhise ekjon sinhasan te bohi kene tai laga dyna hath te kitab juntu aghe aru pichete bi likhi kene thakise, sat-ta chin pora marikene thakise.
Aru moi dikhise ekta takot sorgoduth dangor awaz pora koi thakise, “Kun etu kitab laga chin tu bhangi bole nimite yogi ahse?”
Kintu kunbi sorgo aru prithibi aru prithibi laga nichete etu kitab tu khuli kene puri bole napare.
Kintu ekjon cholawta moi ke koise, “Tumi nakandibi. Sabi! Judah jat laga Bagh, David laga Jor, Tai hai etu sob tu jiti loise. Tai he etu kitab tu khulibole pare aru tate lagai kene thaka sat-ta chin Tai he khuli bole pare.”
Titiya moi ekta Mer laga bacha dikhise sinhasan laga majote khara hoi kene thakise aru charta janwar khan majote khara hoi thakise aru burah manu khan majote thakise, Tai ke morai diya nisina dikhise. Tai laga sat-ta sieng thakise aru sat-ta suku aru juntu ase sat-ta aatma Isor laga kun tu prithibi laga sob jaga te pothai dise.
Tai jai kene ekjon sinhasan te bohi thaka laga dyna hath pora etu kitab tu loise.
Jitiya Tai etu kitab tu loise, charta jinda thaka janwar aru twenty-four burah manu Mer laga bachha usorte giri jaise. Tai khan logote nijor laga veena/HARP/BAJANA aru suna laga bati te joli kene bhal gundai thaka pora bhorta hoi kene thaka dhakise, etu dharmic manu khan laga prathana thakise.
Tai khan notun gana korise,
“Apuni etu kitab tu lobole nimite yogya ase,
Aru tate chin mari kene thaka khuli bole nimite takot ahse.
Kelemane apuni ke morai disele aru apuni laga khun pora Isor manu khan ke kini loise.
Aru sob jati, bhasa, manu aru desh pora.
Apuni tai khan ke ekta raijyo aru Isor laga purohit bonai dise,
Aru tai khan duniya te raj koribo.”
Titiya moi saise aru bisi sorgoduth laga awaz hunise tai khan etu sinhasan usorte thakise aru jinda thaka janwar aru bura manu khan, sob mili kene dos hazar aru hazar-hazar thakise.
Tai khan dangor awaz pora koise,
“Etu mer bacha yoge ahse kun manu pora morai dise takot aru sob dhun pabole nimite aru gyan, takot, adar aru sonman pabole nimite.”
Titiya moi hunise sob bonai diya saman jun tu sorgo aru prithibi te thakise, aru prithibi laga bhitor te thakise, aru samundar te aru kiman saman tate thakise, tai khan koi thakise,
“Etu ekjon kun sinhasan te bohi ahse aru etu Mer bacha Mohan aru adar aru prasansa aru raj koribole takot thaka ekjon, hodai aru hodai nimite.”
Aru charta jinda thaka janwar para koise, “Amen!” Aru titiya cholawta khan giri kene Tai ke aradhana korise.
Titiya moi saise jitiya Mer bachha pora etu sat-ta chin tu khulise, aru moi hunise ekjon charta janwar majot pora dangor THUNDER laga awaz nisina pora koise, “Ahibi!”
Titiya moi saise aru tate ekta boga ghora thakise! Aru etu uporte bohi thaka ekjon pora dhanush nisina dhori thakise, aru tai ke ekta mukut di kene thakise. Tai ekta jiti luwa manu nisina jiti bole jaise.
Jetiya Memna pora dusra chin tu khulise, moi hunise dusra jinda thaka janwar pora koise, “Ahibi!”
Titiya aru ekta ghora ulai kene ahise-juie nisina lal kori kene juli thaka ekta. Aru etu uporte bohi thaka ke prithibi pora shanti uthai loi jabole nimite takot dise, etu pora manu khan ekon-ekjon ke morai dibole nimite. Etu ghora chola ke dangor ekta talwar dise.
Jitiya etu Mer baccha pora tisra chin tu khulise, Moi janwar pora kowa hunise, “Ahibi!” Moi saise aru tate ekta kala ghora dikhise! Aru etu ghora uporte bohi thaka ekjon tai laga hath te palah nisina dhori thakise.
Titiya moi hunise etu charta janwar khan majote pora kuwa hunise,
Aru jetiya mer bacha pora charta chin tu khulise, Moi charta jinda thaka janwar pora koi thaka hunise, “Ahibi!”
Titiya moi saise, aru tate komjor ghora ekta thakise! Aru etu uporte bohi thaka laga nam tu mora thakise, aru mora aatma khan tai laga pichete jai thakise. Prithibi laga char bhag laga ek bhag tu tai ke adikhar dise, talwar pora morai dibole nimite, aru akal pora, aru bimar pora, aru jongol te thaka janwar khan pora morai dibole nimite.
Aru jitiya Mer bacha pora pasta ula chin tu khulise moi dikhise kiman manu Isor laga kotha aru kam kora nimite morai dise tai khan laga aatma etu ALTER nichete thakise.
Titiya tai khan sob ke boga kapur dise, aru tai khan ke aru olop deri rukhibole koise jetiya tak aru bi bhai kokai khan tai khan nisina morai nidiye, jeneka tai khan ke bi morai disele.
Jetiya Mer bacha pora choutha ula chin tu khulise, Moi dikhise aru titiya dangor mati hilise. Suryo tu chuli pora bonai diya bosta nisina kala hoi jaise, aru chand tu khun nisina lal hoi jaise.
Aru sorgo te thaka tara khan prithibi te giri jaise, dimori ghas te napaki kene thaka phol jetiya dangor hawa pani marile giri jai, etu nisina tara khan giri jaise.
Aru akash tu ekta kitab ke lipi luwa nisina lipi jaise aru harai jaise. Sob pahar aru samundar usorte thaka mati khan alag-alag hoi jaise.
Tetiya duniya laga raja aru dangor manu khan, aru sahab khan, dhoni manu khan, aru takot pora thaka khan, aru sob manu, sewak aru azad pora thaka khan, tai khan nijor ke pahar nichete aru pahar laga pathor nichete lukaise.
Tai khan etu pahar aru pathor khan ke koise, “Moi khan uporte giribi! Lukai dibi tai laga chehera usor pora etu ekjon kun sinhasan te bohi ahse aru Mer bacha laga khong pora.
Kelemane tai khan uporte etu dangor khong tu ahi jaise, aru kun manu etu usorte khara koribole pare?”
Etu pichete moi charta sorgoduth ke prithibi laga charta kinar te khara kori thaka dikhise, duniya laga charta hawa jor pora dhori thakise kelemane etu hawa pora duniya tu urai kene loi najabo nimite, aru samundar ke bi nourabole nimite, aru ghas khan ke urai loi najabole nimite.
Titiya moi aru ekta sorgoduth ke purab pora ahhi thaka dikhise tai logote jinda Isor laga chin thakise. Tai kandi kene dangor awaz pora charta sorgoduth khan ke prithibi aru samundar te dukh dibole nimite adesh dise,
koise, “Prithibi ke dukh nidibi, aru samundar ke bhi, aru ghas khan ke bi jetiya tak moi khan Isor laga sewak khan ke matha te chin mari nadiye.”
Titiya moi hunise kun manu khan ke etu chin tu dise: 144,000, kiman Israel laga bacha khan laga ahse etu chin dise:
Baroh hazar Judah laga jat ke chin dise,
Baroh hazar Reuben laga jat ke,
Gad laga Baroh hazar jat ke chin dise,
Asher laga baroh hazar jat ke chin dise,
Baroh hazar Naphtali,
Baroh hazar manasseh laga jat ke,
Simeon laga Baroh hazar jat ke chin dise,
Baroh hazar Levi laga jat ke,
Baroh hazar Issachar laga jat ke chin dise,
Baroh hazar Zebulun laga jat ke dise,
Joseph laga baroh hazar jat ke chin dise,
Aru baroh hazar Benjamin laga jat ke chin mari dise.
Etu khan sob huwa pichete moi saise, aru tate bisi manu thakise kun bi gonti koribole napara thakise- sob desh, jat, manu, aru alag kotha kuwa manu thakise- sinhasan aru Memna usorte khara kori thakise. Tai khan boga kapur pindhi kene thakise aru palm laga pata hath te loi kene thakise,
Aru tai khan dangor awaz pora mati kene koise,
“Anonto jibon moi khan Isor laga ahse, etu ekjon kun sinhasan te bohi ahse, aru Mer ke laga bi!”
aru koise,
“Amen! Adar aru mohima aru gyan aru dhonyabad aru prosansa aru hokti aru takot hodai aru hodai nimite moi khan laga Isor ke hobo dibi! Amen!”
Titiya ekjon cholawta moike hudise, aru koise, “Etu khan kun ahse, kun boga kapur lagai kene ahse, aru tai khan kote pora ahise?”
Titiya moi tai ke koise, “Moi laga Probhu, Apuni jane.” Titiya tai moi ke koise, “Etu khan sob se dangor dukh pora ulai kene aha khan ahse. Tai khan laga kapur dhulai loise aru Mer laga khun pora boga kori loise.
Etu nimite, tai khan Isor laga sinhasan usorte khara kori ahse
Aru Tai laga ghorte din aru rati tai ke mohima di ahse.
Tai laga tambu khuli kene tai khan uporte lagai dibo.
Tai khan aru ketiya bi bhuka nathakibo, aru ketiya bi piyas nalagibo,
aru suryo laga gorom tai khan uporte kitiya bi nalagibo.
Etu Mer kun sinhasan laga majote bohi ahse tai khan ke cholai kene loi jabo
aru tai khan ke jinda pani usorte thakibole dibo,
aru Isor he tai khan laga sob suku pani mushai dibo.”
Aru jetiya Mer pora sat-ta chin tu khulise, pura sorgote adha gonta tak ekdom chup thakise.
Tetiya moi dikhise sat-ta sorgoduth kun Isor usorte khara hoi thakise, aru sat-ta bigul tai khan ke dise.
Dusra ekjon sorgoduth ahise, tai suna laga bati bhal gundh pora bhorta kori kene thaka dhori thakise, aru ALTAR usorte khara hoi kene thakise. Bisi bhal gundh tai ke dise kelemane tai pora he prathna pora etu dan koribo sob dharmic manu khan nimite kuntu sinhasan usorte suna laga ALTAR ahse etu jagate.
Etu bhal gundh laga dhuwa, sorgoduth laga hath pora uthi kene Isor usor pora jaise.
Titiya sorgoduth etu bhal gundh laga bati loi kena alter laga juie para bhorta kori loise. Tai prithibi te etu phelai dise, aru tetiya THUNDER nisina dangor awaz ulaise, ujala hoise aru mati khan hilise.
Tetiya sat-ta sorgoduth kun ke sat-ta bigul dise awaz koribole nimite tayari korise.
Prothom sorgoduth pora tai laga bigul bojaise, aru titiya pathor aru khun logote juie milai kene ulaise. Titiya etu ke prithibi te phelai dise, aru prithibi laga tin bhag juli jasie, aru tin bhag laga ghas khan juli jaise, aru jiman bhi hara ghas khan ahse etu sob juli jaise.
Tetiya dusra sorgoduth pora tai laga bigul bojaise, aru kiba ekta dangor pahar juie pora juli thaka nisina samundar te phelai dise. Aru tin bhag laga samundar khun hoi jaise,
aru tin bhag samundar te jinda thaka janwar khan sob mori jaise, aru tin bhag jahas khan sob khotom hoi jaise.
Titiya tisra sorgoduth pora tai laga bigul bojaise, aru dangor ekta tara akash pora girise, ujala kori kene ahse, aru etu tin bhag laga nodi te girise aru sapha pani te giri jaise.
Etu tara laga nam tu Wormwood thakise. Aru etu laga tin bhag pani pura tita hoi jaise, aru bisi manu mori jaise.
Titiya choutha sorgoduth tai laga bigul bojaise, aru suryo laga tin bhag te lagi jaise, aru chand laga tin bhag eneka hoise aru tara khan laga tin bhag bhi eneka hoi jaise, etu pora tin bhag pura andhera hoi jaise. Dintu laga tin bhag te ujala nathaka hoise, aru etu nisina rati bi eneka hoi jaise.
Titiya moi saise, aru moi chil chiriya laga awaz hunise tai matha uporte uri kene dangor awaz pora mati kene koi thakise, “WOE, WOE, WOE jun manu prithibi te thaki ahse, kelemane aru bi tin ta sorgoduth taikhan laga bigul bajabole ahse.”
Titiya pansta ula sorgoduth tai laga bigul bojaise aru moi dikhise sorgo pora ekta tara prithibi te giri jaise. Etu tara ke ketiya bi kotom nokora mati niche laga chabi di dise.
Titiya etu dhuwa pora puka khan prithibi te ahise, aru tai khan ke bichoo nisina prithibi te takot dise.
Aru tai khan ke koi dise prithibi laga ghas aru phul khan eku nuksan nokoribo nimite, kintu kun manu tai khan laga matha aghe te china laga nai tai khan ke hai nuksan koribo.
Aru tai khan ke manu ke morai dibole nimite kuwa nai, kintu khali tai khan ke panch mohina tak dukh dibole koise. Aru tai khan laga dukh toh hoile jetiya ekta bichoo pora kamure aru bikhai eneka he tai khan dukh pabo.
Aru etu laga din khan te manu khan mori bole mon jabo, kintu moribole naparibo. Tai khan mori jabole nimite echa koribo, kintu mora tai khan pora polai jabo.
Aru etu puka ahha tu hoile lorai te jabole ghora te tayari kora nisina ahse. Aru tai khan laga matha te suna laga mukut lagai kene thaka nisina ahse, aru tai khan laga chehera manu laga chehera nisina ahse.
Aru tai khan laga chuli maiki manu laga chuli nisina ahse, aru tai khan laga dath bagh laga dath nisina he thakise.
Tai khan laga chati te laga thali khan loha laga thali nisina ahse, aru tai khan laga pankha laga awaz lorai te polai kene jai thaka ghora khan nisina thakise.
Aru tai khan laga puchur bichoo pora dunk mari bole nimite thaka nisina tai khan laga puchur te bi thakise, aru tai khan laga puchur te manu khan ke panch mohina tak dukh dibole nimite takot thakise.
Tai khan uporte raj kora laga raja thakise aru tai mati bhitor laga duth ahse.Tai laga nam Hebrew te Abaddon ahse, aru Greek te tai laga nam Apollyon thakise.
Pohila dukh tu par korise. Sabi! Etu pichete aru bhi duita dukh ahibole baki ahse.
Titiya choita ula sorgoduth tai laga bigul bojaise, aru moi ekta awaz janwar laga sieng pora ahhi thaka hunise kun tu Isor laga usorte ekta suna pora bona ISOR KE ARADHANA kura jaga te thakise.
Titiya etu awaz pora choita sorgoduth ke koise kun logote bigul tu thakise, “Etu charta sorgoduth Euphrates laga nodi te bandhi kene rakha khan ke chari dibi.”
Etu karone charta sorgoduth kun etu din nimite tayari kori thakise, etu din, etu mohina, aru etu sal, tai khan ke chari dise kelemane tai khan jai kene tin bhag manu jat khan ke morai dibole nimite.
Ghora pichete thaka siphai khan sob mili kene 200,000,000 thakise. Moi tai khan laga ginti hunise.
Etiya moi ghora laga sapna dikhise aru tai khan uporte te bohi kene thaka ke bi dikhise, chati te lal rong laga thali lagai kene asile, nila rong te, aru juie nisina haldi rong. Ghora khan laga matha sabole bagh laga matha nisina thakise, aru tai khan laga mukh pora juie aru dhuwa ulai thakise.
Tin bhag manu khan etu laga tinta dukh pora mori jaise: Juie pora, dhuwa pora aru tai khan laga mukh pora ula juie pora adha manu mori jaise.
Kelemane etu ghora laga takot tu tai laga mukh te aru puchur te thakise- Kelemane tai khan laga puchur tu hoile sap pora matha thaka nisina, aru etu pora tai khan manu ke jokhom diye.
Kun manu etu sob dukh pora nomori kene bachi jaise, tai khan laga hath pora ki pap kam korise etu pora mon ghuranai, tai khan ke satan aru suna, chandi, pitol, pathor aru khuri pora bonai diya murti ke puja nikoribole nimite- Etu khan eku dikhibole napare, aru hunibole bi napare, aru tai khan bera bole napare.
Aru, tai khan manu ke morai diya pora mon ghura nai, aru jadu kora pora bi ghura nai, beya letera kam, aru chor kori kene ahha pora bi tai khan mon ghura nai.
Titiya moi aru ekta takot thaka sorgoduth ke dikhaise sorgo pora ahhi thaka. Tai badal pora bon kori kene thakise, aru tai laga matha uporte dhanush thakise. Tai laga chehera suryo nisina aru Tai laga paw khan juie juli thaka khamba nisina thakise.
Tai ekta chutu kitab dhori thakise, aru etu tai laga hath te khulise. Tai laga dyna paw samundar te rakhise aru tai laga baya paw mati te rakhise.
Titiya Tai bagh pora hala kora nisina dangor awaz pora hala korise. Jitiya tai hala korise, sat-ta bijili nijor laga awaz te kotha kobole shuru hoise.
Jitiya sat-ta bijili kotha koise, moi likhibole thakise, kintu moi sorgo pora ekta awaz hunise aru koise, “Sat-ta bijili pora ki koise etu lukai kene rakhibi. Etu kitab te nilikhibi.”
Aru moi kuntu sorgoduth samundar aru prithibi te khara hoi thaka dikhise tai laga dyna hath tu sorgo te uthaise.
Aru Tai kun hodai aru hodai nimite jinda ase Tai laga nam kosom khaise, aru kun hai etu sob aru tate thaka sob saman bonaise, etu prithibi aru sob saman khan, aru samundar te ki ahse, “Aru olop bi deri nahobo.
Kintu sat-ta sorgoduth laga awaz din te, jetiya Tai laga bigul tu bajabo, titiya Isor laga asurit kam tu pura hoi jabo, keneka kori kene Tai laga sewak aru bhaobadi khan ke etu bhal kotha tu koi disele.”
Titiya moi logote jai kene moi ke eitu kitab tu dibole nimite koise. Tai moike koise, “Lobi aru khai lobi. Etu pora tumi laga peth tu tita koribo, kintu tumi laga mukh madhu nisina mitha kori dibo.”
Titiya moi sorgoduth laga hath pora etu kitab tu loi kene khai loise. Aru moi laga mukh tu madhu nisina mitha hoi jaise, kintu moi jetiya eitu khaise, moi laga peth tita hoi jaise.
Titiya kunba pora moi ke koise, “Tumi aru bisi manu ke etu prophesy kobi, desh khan ke, alag bhasa kuwa manu khan ke, aru raja khan ke.”
Titiya ekta patla lathi nisina moi ke nap koribole nimite dise. Moi ke koise, “Uthibi aru Isor laga ghor aru alter tu nap lobi, aru kun manu tate aradhana kore tai khan laga bi nap lobi.
Kintu bahar laga jaga tu nap nolobi, eitu Isor najana manu khan ke di dise. Tai khan etu pobitro citi forty-two mohina tak paw pora chipabo.
Aru moi laga duita gawahi khan ke adhikar dibo, aru tai khan 1,260 din tak prophesy kobo, bosta laga kapur lagai kene.”
Eitu duita olive ghas aru duita saaki jola laga khuri ahse juntu prithibi laga Probhu usorte khara ahse.
Kunba manu eitu ke nuksan koribole bisarile, tai khan laga mukh para juie ulai kene dusman khan ke khotom kori dibo.
Tai khan logote akash tu bon kori dibole nimite adhikar ahse kelemane jetiya tai khan prophesy kobo eitu homoi te pani nigiribo tai khan logote pani ke khun bonai dibole nimite takot ahse aru etu prithibi te alag kisim laga dukh pora bhorta koribole nimite tai khan logote adhikar ahse.
Jetiya tai khan laga gawahi kora tu khotom hobo, eitu mati nichete thaka janwar tai khan uporte lorai koribo. Tai khan ke morai di kene sob jiti lobo.
Tai khan laga mora gaw tu dangor citi laga rasta te giri thakibo (Kuntu ke Sodom aru Egypt koi) jun jaga te tai khan laga Probhu ke Crus te mari disele.
Aru tin din adha tak sob jat, desh aru alag kotha kuwa manu khan tai khan laga mora gaw tu sabo aru tai khan laga gaw tu kobor te dhali bole nimite nidibo.
Aru kiman manu etu prithibi te ahse tai khan etu dikhikene khusi koribo. Tai khan ekjon-ekjon ke tofa dikene duita bhaobadi kun duniya te thakise eitu nam pora khusi koribo.
Kintu tin din adha pichete Isor laga sas tu tai khan uporte di dibo, aru tai khan laga paw te khara hobo aru kun manu etu dikhibo tai khan bisi bhoi koribo.
Titiya sorgo pora dangor awaz pora tai khan ke koi thaka hunibo, “Yate uporte ahibe!” Titiya tai khan badal pora sorgote jai jabo, aru tai khan laga dushman khan sai thakibo.
Etu homoi te dangor mati hilibo, aru citi laga dos bhag khotom hoi jabo. Sat-ta hazar manu etu homoi te moribo, aru kun manu bachi jai tai khan bhoi lagibo aru etu dikhikene Isor ke mahima dibo.
Aru dusra mon-dukh kotha bi par hoise. Sabi! Tinta mon-dukh kotha tu joldi ahi ahse.
Tetiya sat-ta sorgoduth pora tai laga bigul tu bajaise, aru sorgo te dangor awaz pora koise,
“Etu duniya laga raijyo tu Probhu aru Khrista laga raijyo hoise,
Aru Tai hodai nimite raj koribo.”
Titiya twenty-four burah manu khan, kun Isor laga usorte sinhasan te bohi ahse tai khan laga chehera girikene Isor ke aradhana koribo.
Tai khan koise,
“Moi khan apani ke dhonyabad di ahse, Mohan Probhu Isor, kun thakise, aru hodai ahse,
Apuni dangor takot tu loi loise aru raj korise.
Eitu desh khan khong uthise,
Kintu apuni laga khong tu ahise,
Aru apuni laga sewak khan ke enam dibole nimite,
Aru kun manu apani laga nam te bhoi kori kene thake,
Chutu aru dangor,
Aru kun manu eitu prithibi tu khotom kore tai khan ke khotom kori dibole nimite.”
Titiya Isor laga ghor sorgoduth thaka tu khuli jaise aru Probhu pora ki kosom dise etu sob tai laga ghor te dikhise. Etu homoi te dangor bijili ujala ahise, jor pora hala kori kene, aru mati hilise aru dangor pathor khan girise.
Titiya ekta dangor chin sorgote ulaise: ekta maiki suryo pora kapur lagai kene, aru chand tai laga paw nichete, aru barohta tara laga mukut tai laga mathate pindhise.
Tai bacha bhuki thakise, aru bacha jonom dibole laga bikha pora kandi thakise, aru bacha ula bole nimite dukh pai thakise.
Tetiya aru dusra ekta chin sorgote ulaise: Sabi, ekta dangor dragon tai laga dosta matha aru dosta seing, aru sat-ta mukut tai laga matha te ahse.
Aru tai laga puchur pora tin bhag tara sorgo te jhari kene hatai dise aru prithibi phale phelai dise. Aru eitu dragon bacha pabole thaka maiki usorte khara kori thakise, jitiya tai bacha pabo, eitu dragon pora eitu maiki laga bacha tu khai dibo.
Titiya eitu maiki pora ekta mota bacha jonom dise, aru tai eitu desh ke loha laga rod pora raj cholabole thakise. Tai laga bacha ke Isor aru sinhasan usorte chingi kene loi jaise,
aru eitu maiki jongol te polai jaise, tai nimite Isor pora ekta jaga tayar kori kene rakhi dise, tai ke 1,260 din tak bhal kori kene sai dibole.
Etiya sorgo te dangor lorai hoise. Michael aru tai laga sorgoduth khan eitu dragon logote lorai korise; aru eitu dragon bhi tai laga duth khan ke loi kene lorai korise.
Kintu eitu dragon aru tai laga duth khan takot thakanai aru tai khan nimite sorgo te thakibole jaga bhi thakanai.
Eitu karone dangor dragon ke nichete phelai dise- purana ekta saph, tai ke beya aatma aru satan koi, tai pura duniya ke thokai diye- tai ke prithibi te phelai dise, aru tai laga duth khan bhi tai logote phelai dise.
Titiya moi sorgo pora dangor awaz te koi thaka hunise,
“Etiya moikhan laga poritran aru takot
Aru Isor laga raijyo tu ahise,
Aru tai laga Khrista laga adhikar ahse.
Moi laga bhai khan ke dukh diya ekjon ke nichete phelai dise,
Kun pora Isor usorte din aru rati tai khan ke dukh dise.
Tai khan Mer bachha laga khun aru gawahi pora sob tu jiti loise,
Kelemane mori bole thaka homoi te bhi tai khan nijor laga jibon tu morom koranai.
Eitu nimite sorgo khan khusi koribi, aru
Kiman manu tate thaki ahse! Kintu prithibi aru samundar khan dukh hobo,
Kelemane satan tu tumi khan majote ahse! Tai pura khong pora bhorta hoi ahse, tai jani ahse tai logote olop homoi hai bachi kene ahse!
Aru jetiya dragon tu janise tai ke prithibi niche te phelai dise, tai jai kene eitu maiki ke digdar dise kun hai mota bacha ekjon ke jonom dise.
Eitu nimite sap pora tai laga mukh pora nodi nisina pani eitu maiki laga pichete jabo dise, eitu pani pora maiki ke loi jabole nimite.
Kintu eitu prithibi pora maiki ke modot korise. Eitu prithibi pora mukh khuli kene sob pani tu khai loise.
Titiya eitu maiki uporte bisi khong uthise aru eitu maiki laga khandan khan uporte lorai koribole nimite jaise, kun manu Isor laga kotha mani thakise aru Jisu laga gawahi dhori kene thakise tai khan ke khotom koribole nimite lorai korise.
Titiya tai samundar usorte khara korise.
Titiya moi ekta janwar samundar pora ulai kene ahha dikhise. Eitu janwar laga dosta seing aru sat-ta matha thakise. Aru matha khan ke dosta mukut thakise, aru ekta-ekta matha uporte Isor ke bodnam kora nam khan thakise.
Aru etiya kuntu janwar moi dikhise eitu sabole ekta chetak nisina thakise. Tai laga theng tu bhalu laga theng nisina thakise, aru tai laga mukh ekta bagh janwar laga mukh nisina thakise. Dragon pora tai ke takot dise aru tai laga sinhasan dise, aru sob adhikar khan manu ke raj cholabole nimite dise.
Ekta janwar laga matha tu morai diya nisina dikhise, kintu tai laga bahar jokhom khan bhal hoi jaise. Pura prithibi tu asurit hoikene tai laga pichete jaise.
Tai khan etu dragon ke puja korise, kelemane tai pora tai laga adhikar etu janwar ke dise. Aru taikhan etu janwar ke puja korise aru koi thakise, “Etu janwar nisina aru kun ahse?” Aru “Kun hai tai logote lorai koribole paribo?”
Etu janwar ke phutani laga kotha khan aru Isor ke bodnam diya kotha khan kobole nimite mukh dise, aru fourty-two mohina etu sob kam khan koribole nimite adhikar dise.
Tetiya etu janwar tai laga mukh khuli kene Isor laga beya kotha koise, Tai laga nam tu sorom khelai dise, aru Tai kun jaga te thake eitu beya koribole nimite, aru jiman manu sorgo te thake tai khan laga beya kobole.
Aru eitu janwar ke bisasi aru purohit manu khan uporte lorai koribole nimite aru tai khan uporte jiti lobole nimite takot dise. Aru, sob jat, desh, aru manu khan uporte adhikar dise.
Aru jiman manu prithibi te thake tai khan sob etu ke puja koribo, aru kun khan laga nam kitab te likha nai taikhan bi, duniya bona laga suru pora, Jibon laga Kitab te, juntu Mer laga ahse, kun ke morai disele.
Jodi kunba manu kan ahse koile, tai huni lobi.
Kunba manu ke bandhi kene loi jabole ase koile,
Tai ke eneka he loi jabo.
Jodi kunba manu ke talwar pora morabole ase koile,
eitu talwar pora hai tai moribo.
Yate nomro aru dukh kosto aru Isor manu khan laga bisas ahse.
Titiya moi aru bhi ekta janwar prithibi pora ulai kene ahhi thaka dikhise, aru tai tu dragon nisina kotha koi.
Tai laga usorte pohila ulai ahha janwar laga kiman adhikar ahse sob tu dikhai dise, aru etu prithibi aru tate thaka kiman manu ahse sob ke etu pohila janwar ke puja koribole nimite dise- etu ekjon kun laga bahar laga jokhom tu bhal hoi jaisile.
Tai bisi dangor asurit kam khan korise, aru tai manu usorte sorgo pora juie prithibi te bi ahhi bole dise aru manu khan ke dikhai dise.
Aru juntu sob chinha khan janwar laga usorte koribole nimite monjur dise, jiman manu prithibi te ahse tai khan ke thokai dise. Aru tai khan ke janwar laga murti bona bole nimite koise kun logote talwar laga jokom ahse, kintu jinda ahse.
Aru etu janwar laga murti ke sas dibole nimite monjuri dise, kelemane etu janwar laga murti kotha kobole paribo, aru kun manu etu janwar laga murti ke puja nokoribo tai ke morai dibo.
Tai khan joborjost korise, chutu aru dangor, dhoni aru gorib, sewak aru aram pora thaka manu, tai khan laga matha agete nohoile dyna hath te chin maribole nimite.
Aru etu karone, kun manu bhi etu chin nathakile eku bhi bikiri aru kinibole naparibo jetiya tak tai khan logote etu laga chin nathakibo- etu janwar laga nam, nohoile tai laga nam laga ginti tu.
Yate gyan ahse: kun manu buji bole pare, tai etu janwar laga ginti tu ongkho kori lobi. Kelemane etu ekta manu laga ginti ahse, aru tai laga ongkho tu hoile 666 ase.
Aru sorgo pora ekta awaz, juntu bisi pani laga awaz nisina aru dangor pani ahibole awaz ahhi thaka nisina moi hunise. Aru moi huna tu hoile baja bajai thaka khan pora taikhan laga bajana te awaz ulai diya nisina hunise.
Aru tai khan cholawta aru charta jinda thaka janwar aru sinhasan usorte notun gana kori kene gai thakise. Kun para bhi etu gana kori bole najane, khali 144,000 junkhan ke prithibi pora anise, tai khan hai etu gana koribole pare.
Aru tai khan maiki logote nijor ke paap te girai kene ahha manu nahoi, tai khan ekdom sapha ahse. Aru tai khan kun jaga te Mer jai tai laga piche jai thaka khan ahse. Tai khan ke manu laga majot pora bachai kene loi ahna ahse Isor laga pohila bacha khan aru Memna nimite.
Tai khan laga mukh te eku misa kotha panai, kelemane tai khan ekdom sapha ahse.
Titiya moi aru ekta sorgoduth ke hawa te uri thaka dikhise, aru tai logote prithibi manu khan nimite ketiya bi khotom nokora susamachar tu thakise- sob desh, jati, bhasha, aru manu nimite.
Tai dangor awaz pora matise, “Isor ke bhoi koribi aru Tai ke Mohima dibi. Kelemane bichar kora laga homoi ahise. Kun pora sorgo aru prithibi, samundar aru sapha pani bonaise.”
Aru ekta sorgoduth pora etu sorgoduth pichete ahise, aru koise, “Girise, dangor Babylon tu girise, kun he sob deshkhan ke tai laga beyobichari draikhya ros tu khabole dise.”
Aru dusra sorgoduth taikhan laga piche korise, aru dangor awaz pora koise, “Kunba manu etu janwar aru tai laga murti ke puja korile, aru jodi tai laga chinah matha aru dyna hath te loile,
tai bhi Isor laga khong tu dikhibo, etu ros Tai laga khong laga cup te ki logote bi namilai kene dhali dise. Tai ke Mer aru Tai laga sorgoduth usorte ketiya bi khotom nokora laga juie te phelai kene dukh dibo.
Aru tai khan laga dukh pa laga dhuwa uporte hodai nimite jabo aru tai khan din aru rati aram napabo- etu janwar aru tai laga murti ke puja kora manu khan, aru kun manu etu laga nam laga chin tu loi.
Yate dikhibo pare purohit khan pora dukh kosto aru nomro kori kene thaka, kun manu Isor laga kotha mane aru Jisu uporte bisas kori kene thake.”
Titiya moi sorgo pora ekta awaz koi thaka hunise, “Eitu likhibi: Asirbad ahse eitu mora manu khan kun etiya pora Probhu nimite moribole ahse.” “Hoi,” Aatma pora koi ahse, “Tai khan laga dukh pora aram pabo, kelemane tai khan ki kam korise etu tai khan laga pichete ahibo.”
Titiya moi saise aru tate ekta boga badal thakise. Badal te bohi thaka ekjon manu laga bacha nisina thakise. Tai laga hath te ekta dhar hashua hatyar thakise aru Tai laga matha te suna laga mukut thakise.
Titiya alag sorgoduth mondoli pora ulai ahhikene badal te bohi thaka ke dangor awaz pora koise: “Tumi laga hashua lobi aru katibole shuru koribi, kelemane kata laga homoi ahise, prithibi laga dhan tu paki jaise.”
Titiya badal te bohi thaka pora tai laga hashua-hatiyar ulai kene prithibi te cholai se, aru titiya prithibi laga kata homoi pura hoise.
Titiya aru ekta sorgoduth sorgo laga mondoli pora ulai kene ahise, tai logote bhi dhar thaka hashua-hatiyar thakise.
Aru dusra ekta sorgoduth juli thaka ALTAR pora ulai kene ahise tai logote juie laga adhikar thakise. Tai dangor awaz pora kun laga hath te dhar hashua-hatiyar ahse tai ke matise, aru koise, “Tumi laga dhar hashua-hatiyar lobi aru prithibi pora angur khan joma koribi, kelemane tai khan laga angur khan sob pakise.”
Titiya etu sorgoduth tai laga hashua-hatiyar loi kene prithibi te kiman angur paki kene ahse eitu khan ke uthaise. Tai angur joma korikene angur mihin kora jaga te Isor laga khong nimite phelai dise.
Tetiya citi laga bahar te angur mihin kora laga khuri dhali kene thakise, aru eitu khuri pora khun ulai thakise aru eitu khun ghora laga matha tak ponchise 1,600 tak.
Titiya aru bhi asurit chin sorgo te dekhise: sat-ta sorgoduth sat-ta dukh loi kene- khotom laga dukh, etu pora Isor laga khong pura hoi jabo.
Titiya moi dikhise shisa laga samundar juie te milai kene kun manu etu janwar aru murti ke jiti loise, aru tai laga nam laga ginti uporte jiti loise, tai khan eitu shisa laga samundar te khara hoi thakise, Isor pora diya baja laga saman loi kene khara hoi thakise.
Tai khan Moses laga gana gai thakise, Isor laga sewak aru Mer laga gana aru koi thakise,
“Dangor aru asurit ahse apuni laga kam
Probhu Isor, sob se Mahan.
Apuni laga rasta bhal aru hosa ahse,
oh dharmic manu laga raja.
Kelemane apni pobitro ahse.
Sob desh khan ahibo
aru apuni usorte mohima koribo
Kelemane apuni laga bhal kam khan sob dekhai dise.”
Eitu sob huwa pichete moi saise, aru mondoli te gawah khan laga tambu sorgo te khuli jaise.
Aru mondoli bahar te ulai ahhi kene sat-ta sorgoduth sat-ta dukh dhori kene thakise. Tai khan laga kapur sapha thakise, ujala kapur aru tai khan laga chati te suna pora bonai kene thaka huru kapor khan lagai kene thakise.
Charta janwar majot pora ekjon he sat-ta sorgoduth ke sat-ta bati Isor laga khong pora bhorta thaka tai khan ke dise, Tai jun hodai aru hodai nimite jinda ahse.
Titiya Isor laga Mohima aru takot pora mondoli tu dhuwa pora bhorta hoi jaise. Kun bhi tate jabole napare jitiya tak sat-ta dukh sat-ta sorgoduth khan pora pura nokare.
Titiya moi hunise ekta dangor awaz mondoli pora sat-ta sorgoduth khan ke koi thaka, “Jabi aru sat-ta bati pora Isor laga khong tu prithibi te dhali dibi.”
Titiya pohila sorgoduth jai kene tai laga bati pora prithibi te dhali dise. Titiya beya aru bikhai thaka ghaw kun manu khan janwar laga chin loi kene thakise tai khan uporte ahise aru kun manu etu murti ke puja kori thakise tai khan uporte ahise.
Aru dusra sorgoduth pora tai laga bati pora samundar te dhali dise. Eitu khun hoi jaise, ekta mora manu laga khun nisina, aru kiman jinda saman samundar te thakise sob mori jaise.
Titiya tisra sorgoduth tai laga bati sapha pani aru nodi te dhali dise aru eitu khun hoi jaise.
Aru pani laga duth pora koi thaka moi hunise,
“Apuni dharmic ahse-Ekjon kun ahse aru kun thakise, Pobitro ekjon-
Kelemane apani eitu sob bichar korise.
Kelemane tai khan bhaobadi khan aru dharic khan laga khun dhali dise,
apuni tai khan ke khun khabole nimite dise;
tai khan eitu pabole nimite layak ahse.”
Titiya moi ALTAR pora koi thaka hunise,
“Hoi, Mohan Probhu Isor,
Apuni laga bichar dharmic ahse.”
Titiya choutha sorgoduth tai laga bati suryo te dhali dise, aru manu khan ke juie pora jolai dibole nimite koise.
Etu pora manu kobo napara gorom pora julise, aru tai khan Isor laga nam tu beya koise, kun sob dukh uporte adhikar ahse. Tai khan mon ghuranai aru Tai ke Mohima diya nai.
Titiya pansta sorgoduth pora tai laga bati loi kene janwar laga sinhasan te dhali dise, aru etu para tai laga raijyo andhar hoi jaise. Tai khan bikhai kene nijor laga jiba kamuribole shuru hoise.
Etu pora tai khan sorgo te thaka Isor ke beya koise, tai khan laga bikhai thaka aru ghaw nimite, kintu eneka korile bi tai khan laga beya kam pora mon ghura nai.
Titiya choi-ta sorgoduth pora tai laga bati dangor nodi te dhali dise, juntu Euphrates ase. Itu laga pani sukhi jaise, purab pora ahhibole tayar kori thaka raja khan nimite.
Tai khan OHUSI laga aatma thakise kun khan asurit chin dikhai thakise. Mohan Isor laga dangor din te lorai koribole nimite duniya laga raja khan ke joma kori thakise.
(“Sabi! Moi chor nisina ahi ahse! Asirbad ahse etu manu kun tai laga kapur lagai kene sai ahse aru rukhi ahse, kelemane tai khan kapur nalagai kene berai nathakibo aru tai khan laga sorom khan tu nadikhibo.”)
Titiya tai khan sob ke eke logote anise ekta jaga juntu laga nam Hebrew te Armaggedon koi.
Titiya sat-ta ula sorgoduth tai laga bati hawa te dhali dise. Titiya mondoli laga bahar pora dangor ekta awaj ulaise, sinhasan pora koise, “Eitu sob hoise!”
Titiya tate bijili laga ujala marise, awaz dise, aru THUNDER korise, aru dangor mati hilise- jeneka ketiya bi huwa nai jun tu din pora manu ke prithibi te bonaise, etu mati hila eman dangor thakise, ekdom dangor thakise.
Dangor citi tinta bhag hoi jaise, aru desh laga citi khan khotom hoi jaise. Titiya dangor Babylon Isor usorte yad korise, aru tai laga khong laga cup tai ke dise.
Titiya sob majuli khan polaise, aru pahar khan aru tate pa nai.
Aru manu khan uporte dangor pathor, ekdom bhari, sorgo pora ahhikene tai khan uporte girise. Titiya manu khan Isor laga nam tu beya koise kelemane eitu pathor khan tai khan uporte girise, kelemane eitu dukh bisi beya thakise.
Tetiya sat-ta sorgoduth khan majote ekjon kun laga hath te sat-ta bati thakise, ahhi kene moi ke kotha korise, aru koise, “Ahibi, Moi tumi ke dikhai dibo etu dangor beyobichar ke jun laga bichar hoise aru kun bisi pani te bhoi ahse.
Etu duniya laga raja khan tai logote beya kam korise, aru etu prithibi te thaka khan ke tai laga beyobichari laga draikhya-ros tu khabole dise.”
Titiya sorgoduth pora moi ke aatma pora ekta jongol te loi jaise, aru moi dikhise ekta maiki ke kun ekta lal rong janwar uporte bohi thakise jun laga uporte Isor ke bodnam kora laga nam khan pora bhorta ahse. Etu janwar laga sat-ta matha aru dosta sieng thakise.
Eitu maiki beguni rong kapur lagai kene thakise aru moti, suna aru dam laga pathor lagai kene sabole sundur dikhi thakise. Tai laga hath te suna laga cup thakise juntu te beyaobichari laga kam pora bhorta hoi kene thaka dhori thakise.
Aru tai laga matha aghe te nam likhi kene thakise, buyibole napara ekta: “Dangor Babylon beyobichar laga ama aru prithibi ke kothom kori diya ekjon.”
Moi dikhise etu maiki bisasi dharmic aru Jisu laga gawah khan laga khun khai kene thakise. Jitiya moi taike dikhise, moi bisi asurit hoise.
Kintu sorgoduth pora moike koise, “Kele tumi asurit lagi ahse? Moi etu maiki laga lukai thaka khan kobo aru etu janwar kun tai ke dhori ahse, etu janwar kun laga sat-ta matha aru dosta singh ahse.
Eitu janwar tumi pora dikha tu hoile jinda thakise, tai etiya jinda nai, kintu tai aru bi mati niche pora ulai kene ahibole ahse. Titiya etu pora pura khotom kori dibo. Kun manu eitu prithibi te thaki ahse, kun manu laga nam duniya bona homoi pora Jibon laga Kitab te nam likha nai- tai khan etu janwar ke dikhi kene asurit lagibo, kelemane tai pohila te thakise, aru etiya nai, hoilebi tai ahibole ahse.
Etu gyan thaka khan nimite bhabona koribole laga ahse: etu sat-ta matha sat-ta pahar ahse kun jaga te maiki bohi ahse. Tai khan sat-ta raja bhi ahse:
pansta raja giri jaise, ekjon ahse dusra ekjon ahha nai. Kintu jetiya tai ahhibo, tai olop din nimite he thakibole lagibo.
Etu janwar kun thakise, kintu etiya nai, tai nijor bhi ath ginti laga raja thakise; kintu tai bhi sat-ta raja majote ekjon thakise, aru tai pura khotom kori dibole nimite jai ahse.
Dosta sieng thaka tu hoile dosta raja ahse kintu tai khan ek ghonta janwar logote raja hobole nimite adhikar pabo.
Etu khan sob ekta bhabona ahse, aru tai khan laga adhikar aru takot sob janwar ke dibo.
Tai khan Mer logote lorai koribo. Kintu Mer pora tai khan uporte jiti lobo, tai he Probhu laga Probhu aru Raja laga Raja ahse- aru Tai logote thaka khan ke, bachi luwa aru biswasi koi.”
Titiya sorgoduth pora moi ke koise, “Etu pani kuntu tumi dikhise, kun jaga te beyobichari khan bohe, etu khan manu desh aru alag kotha kuwa manu khan ahse.
Tumi kuntu dosta sieng aru janwar dikhe- tai khan beyobichari khan ke ghin koribo. Tai khan pora tai laga kapur khuli kene sorom khelai dibo, tai laga gaw mangso bi tanibo, aru juie pora tai ke pura julai dibo.
Kelemane Isor pora tai khan laga mon te eneka koribole koi dise, aru ekta kam he koribole dise, aru tai khan laga raijyo janwar ke dibole nimite, jitiya tak Isor laga kotha tu pura nahoi.
Etiya kun tu maiki ke tumi dikhise etu dangor citi te prithibi laga raja khan uporte raj cholai.”
