bahar pora anah suna, chandi, dam laga pathor, moti, sundar saman, beguni rong kapur, reshum kapur, lal rong laga kapur, sob kisim laga bhal aru dam laga khuri, bhal para bona bati khan, pitol, luha, aru marble,
masala khan, bhal ghun thaka tel, angur ros, kisim laga tel, sapha kori kene rakha atta dhan, saguli aru goru, ghora aru ghora gari, sewak aru manu laga aatma khan.
Tumi laga paki juwa phal, tumi laga aatma laga echa, sob tumi pora jai-jaise. Sob aram aru dikhawa tumi pora jai jaise, aru etu ketiya bhi wapas napabo.
Eitu saman laga malik khan kun tai ke sai kene dhoni hoisile etiya tai pora dur hoi jaise, kelemane tai laga dukh pai kene thaki thaka tu sai kene bhoi lagise aru dur te jai kene khara hoi jaise.
Tai khan kobo,
