Titiya twenty-four burah manu khan aru charta janwar athukarhi kene Isor kun sinhasan te bohi thakise taike aradhana korise aru koise,
“Amen. Hallelujah!”
Tetiya sinhasan pora ekta awaz ahhi kene, koise,
