aru kun Tar ke bhoi kore, chutu aru dangor sob.”
Tetiya moi bisi manu laga awaz nisina hunise, aru nodi te pani jai thaka nisina, aru akash te bijili mara nisina aru koise,
“Hallelujah!
Moi khan laga Mohan Probhu Isor raj kore.
Moi khan nam untcha uthai kene khusi koribo
