(Kelemane sapha kapur lagai kene thaka tu hoile pobitro manukhan laga dharmic kam khan ahse).
Tetiya sorgoduth pora moi ke koise, “Eitu likhibi: Asirbad ahse kun ke Memna laga sadhi te matise.” Tai eneka aru moi ke koise, “Eitu khan sob Isor laga hosa kotha khan ahse.”
Tetiya moi Tar laga paw te giri kene aradhana korise, kintu tai moi ke koise, “Eneka nokoribi! Moi bhi tumi nisina ekta sewak ahse tumi aru sathi bhai khan logote Jisu laga gawahi dhori kene ahse. Isor ke mohima dibi. Kelemane Jisu laga gawahi aatma laga prophesy ahse.”
Tetiya moi sorgo khula dikhise, aru tate ekta boga ghora thakise, aru etu uporte bohi thaka ke bhal aru hosa matise, aru Tai bichar kore aru dharmic pora lorai kore.
Tar laga suku juli thaka jui nisina ahse, aru Tai laga matha te bisi mukut thakise. Tai laga nam likha thakise aru etu nam kun bhi najane khali tai pora he jane.
Tai lagai thaka kapur khun te dhali kene thaka nisina ahse, aru tai laga nam tu Isor laga kotha ahse.
Sorgo laga siphai khan sob boga ghora te uthi kene tai laga pichete jai thakise, aru tai khan sundur, aru sapha boga kapur lagai kene thakise.
Aru tai laga mukh pora dhar talwar ulai kene jai thakise, etu pora desh khan ke mari dibo, aru saguli rukha manu pora tai laga bhera khan ke lathi pora mara nisina tai khan ke bi eneka koribo. Tai angur laga ros uporte chipai diya nisina Mohan Isor laga khong bhi tai khan uporte ahibo.
Tetiya moi ekta sorgoduth ke suyro te khara hoi thaka dikhise. Tai jor awaj pora matise, kiman chiriya akash te uri thakise tai khan koise, “Ahibi! Isor laga kha luwa kora din nimite sob eke logote joma kori lobi,
tumi khan raja laga mangso khabole nimite, dangor sahab khan laga mangso khabole nimite, aru takot thaka manu khan aga mangso ghora aru kun tai laga uporte bhoi ahse tai khan laga mangso khabole nimite, aru sob manu laga mangso, kuli kene berai thaka aru sewak khan laga, chutu aru dangor khan laga mangso khabole nimite.”
Tetiya moi janwar aru prithibi laga raja khan ke dikhise aru tai khan laga sipahi khan ke tai khan ghora te bohi kene thaka uporte aru tai laga sipahi khan logote lorai koribole nimite joma kori thakise.
Titiya janwar ke dhori loise, aru tai logote kiman misa kuwa bhaobadi khan kun tai usorte chin khan dikhayai thakise, eneka kori kene tai bisi ke thokai dise kun janwar laga chin loise aru kun murti ke puja korise. Duijon ke jui juli thaka te jinda pora phelai dise kun tu ketiya bi khotom nahoi.
Aru kiman manu bachi kene thakise tai khan sob talwar pora morai dise kun ghora te bohi thakise, kun tu tai laga mukh pora ulaise aru pura chiriya tai khan laga mangso pora bhorta hoi jaise.
Tetiya moi ekta sorgoduth sorgo pora ahhi thaka dikhise. Tai logote mati niche laga chabi thakise, aru tai laga hath te luha laga rosi dangor dhurikene thakise.
Tai dragon ke dhori loise, pohila pora thaka saph ke, kun tu devil, aru Satan ahse, aru hazar sal tak tai bandi loise.
Tetiya tai ke mati nichete phelai dise, aru bon kori kene tai uporte chin mari dise, aru eitu pora tai uporte chin mari dise, aru eitu pora tai hazar sal khotom nahuwa tak aru desh khan ke thokai nidibole nimite. Etu pichete, tai ke olop homoi nimite chari dibo.
Tetiya moi sinhasan khan deikhise. Tate tai khan bohise- sob aatma khan kun laga matha khan Jisu laga gawahi aru kotha nimite kati dise, aru kun manu janwar aru tai laga murti ke puja koranai aru matha agete aru hath te tai laga chin luwanai- tai khan ke bichar korise tai khan jinda hoise, aru Khrista logote hazar sal tak raj korise.
(Aru dusra khan jinda huwanai aru jibon panai jetiya tak hazar sal tu pura huwanai). Etu PROTHOM PUNURUSTHAN ahse.
Etu manu ahsirbad aru pobitro ahse kun poila resurrection te bhag ahse! Etu te dusra bar mora laga eku takot nai, kintu tai khan Isor aru Khrista laga purohit hobo, aru Tai logote hazar sal raj koribo.
Kintu jetiya sal pura hoi jabo, Satan ke tai laga pora chari dibo.
Aru Tai prithibi laga charta kinar laga desh te jai kene bisi manu khan ke thokai dibo- manu khan aru tai khan laga jaga te- aru tai khan ke lorai koribole nimite joma koribo. Aru tai khan balu aru samundar nisina bisi manu thakibo.
Tai khan prithibi laga dangor aru plain jaga te jabo aru dharmic manu aru tai khan laga morom citi ke gheri lobo. Kintu sorgo pora juie ahhi kene tai khan ke khotom kori dibo.
Tetiya Satan he, kun tai khan ke thokai dise, juie laga nodi te phelai dise, kun jaga te janwar aru tai laga misa bhaobadi khan ahse. Tai khan ke din aru rati hodai nimite dukh dibo.
Tetiya moi dangor boga sinhasan dikhise aru tate bohi thaka ekjon, Tai laga usor pora prithibi aru sorgo poila jai thakise, kintu tai khan nimite kot te bi jaga panai.
Aru tetiya moi mora dikhise- sob chutu aru dangor- sinhasan usorte khara kori thakise, aru kitab khan khuli jaise. Tetiya aru dusra kitab ekta khulise, kun tu Jibon laga Kitab ahse. Mora khan ke kitab te ki likha ahse eitu pora bichar korise, tai khan laga kam hisab te.
Samundar bhitorte mori kene thaka khan bi uthise. Mora aru beya aatma khan majote mori kene thaka khan bi uthise, aru sob manu khan ke tai khan laga kam hisab te bichar korise.
Tetiya mora aru beya aatma khan ke juie laga nodi te phelai dise. Etu dusra bar mora ahse- juie laga nodi.
Kun laga nam Jibon laga Kitab te likha nai, tai ke juie laga nodi te phelai dise.
Tetiya moi notun sorgo aru notun prithibi dikhise, pohila prithibi aru pohila sorgo tu harai jaise, aru samundar khan nathaka hoi jaise.
Aru moi pobitro citi dikhise, notun Jerusalem Isor laga sorgo pora ahhi thakise, ekta shadi kora maiki tai laga mota ke tayari kori kene lok pabole ahha nisina.
Aru tetiya moi dangor awaz sinhasan pora koi thaka hunise, “Sabi! Isor laga ghor to manu khan logote ahse, aru Tar tai khan logote thakibo. Tai khan Tar laga manu hobo, aru Isor Tai nijor bi tai khan logote thakibo.
Tar tai khan laga suku pani musi dibo, aru tate mora nathikibo, aru mon dukh nokoribo, nakandibo, aru nibikhabo. Etu khan aru ketiya bi nahobo kelemane pohila laga sob tu harai jabo.
Tetiya ekjon kun sinhasan te bohi thakise Tai koise, “Sabi! Moi sob tu notun kori dise.” Tai moike koise, “Etu likhibi kelemane etu kuwa khan sob hosa aru bisas koribole laga kotha ahse.”
Tai aru bhi moike koise, “Etu sob kam pura hoise! Moi alpha aru omega ahse, suru aru khotom ase. Kun manu piyas lagi ahse moi tai ke eku dam noloi kene sapha jibon laga pani dibo.
Kintu mon chutu khan, bisas nathaka khan, ghin kam kora khan, manu ke morai diya khan, beyobichar kam kora khan, jadu montar kora khan, murti puja kora khan, aru sob kisim misa koi thaka khan, tai khan laga jaga jui para hodai juli thaka nodi te hobo. Etu dusra bar mora ahse.”
Tetiya sat-ta majote ekjon sorgoduth moi usorte ahise, etu ekjon kun logote sat-ta bati te antim dukh pora bhorta kori kene dhori thakise, aru tai moi logote kotha korise, aru koise, “Yate ahibi. Moi tumi ke shadi kora maiki ke dikhai dibo, Mer laga maiki.”
Tetiya tai moi uthai kene aatma pora dangor aru untcha pahar te loi jaise aru moi ke pobitro Jerusalem citi Isor laga sorgo pora ahhi thaka dikhise.
Isor laga mohima tate thakise, aru etu sundur bisi bhal thakise, ekta dam aru sapha sundur pathor nisina.
