Purab te tinta dorja thakise, uttor te tinta dorja, daksin te tinta dorja, aru pachim te tinta dorja thakise.
Aru citi laga dewar te barohta majbut FOUNDATION thakise, aru etu khan te Mer laga barohta pasonir khan laga nam thakise.
Kun pora moi logote kotha korise tai logote nap luwa laga suna pora bona laga NOL thakise aru etu pora citi, aru tai laga dorja, aru dewar khan nap koribole nimite.
Etu citi laga jaga bisi dangor thakise; aru etu citi laga lamba phale aru chora phale eke thakise. Tai nap kora laga NOL pora nap korise. Baroh hazar laga dangor thakise (Lamba, dangor, aru untcha sob eke thakise.)
