Aru etu citi laga dewar laga FOUNDATION khan bisi sundur aru sob kisim laga dam pathor pora bonai kene rakhise. Prothom FOUNDATION tu jasper asile, dusra FOUNDATION sapphire laga thakise, tinta ula tu agate, aru charta ula tu emerald laga thakise,
pansta ula oynx thakise, choita tu carnelian, sat-ta tu hoile chrysolite laga thakise, anth ta tu hoile beryl, nou ta tu topaz, aru dosta tu hoile chrysoprase, egaroh tu hoile jacinth aru baroh ta tu hoile amethyst.
Aru barohta dorja tu hoile baroh moti laga thakise; ekta dorja khan ekta moti pora bonai kene thakise. Citi laga rasta khan ahsli suna laga thakise, ekdom sapha glass nisina thakise.
Aru moi etu citi te ekta bi mondoli dikha nai, kelemane Mohan Probhu Isor aru Mer he tate laga mondoli ahse.
Etu citi te suryo aru chand laga ujala eku dorkar thaka nai. Kelemane Isor laga mohima tate ujala diye, aru tai laga saaki tu Mer he ahse.
Aru desh khan etu citi laga ujala te berabo, aru prithibi laga raja khan sob mohima tate he ani kene dibo.
Aru tate dorja khan din te ketiya bi bon nohobo, tate aru rati ketiya bi nathakibo.
Tai khan sob desh laga adar aru mohima tate he anibo,
kintu eku letera saman tate jabole naparibo, aru kun manu chalak aru beya kam koribo tate jabo naparibo, kintu khali kun laga nam Memna laga jibon laga kitab te likhi kene ahse tai hai tate jabole paribo.
Tetiya sorgoduth pora moike jibon laga pani dikhai dise, crystal nisina sapha thakise. Aru etu Isor laga sinhasan aru Mer laga sinhasan pora giri thakise.
Citi laga rasta majot pora aru nodi laga duita kinar te jibon laga ghas thakise, aru eitu ghas te barotha alag-alag phol ulai aru sob mohina te ekta ekta phal dhori thakise. Aru ghas laga pata khan desh ke changai koribole lagai kene thakise.
Aru tate eku beya pap khan nai. Tate Isor aru Mer laga sinhasan etu citi te thakibo, aru tai laga sewak khan tai ke sewa koribo.
Tai khan Tar laga chehera dikhibo, aru Tar laga nam tai khan laga matha aghe te likhibo.
Tate aru rati ketiya bi nohobo, aru tai khan saaki laga ujala aru suryo laga puhor nalagibo kelemane Isor he tai khan ke ujala dibo, aru tai khan Isor logote hodai aru hodai nimite raj koribo.
Tetiya sorgoduth pora moike koise, “Etu sob kotha khan hosa aru bisas koribole laga ahse. Etu Probhu, aatma khan aru bhaobadi khan laga Isor, Tar laga sorgoduth ke tai laga sewak usorte pothai dise aru dikhai dise ki tu joldi hobole ahse.”
Moi, John etu sob kotha dikhise aru ki hobole ahse etu sob moi hunise. Jetiya moi etu hunise aru dikhise, moi nichete aradhana koribole nimite girise etu sorgoduth usorte kun he moike etu sob tu dikhai thakise.
Kintu Tai moike koise, “Tumi eneka nokoribi! Moi bi tumi nisina ekta sewak ahse, tumi laga bhai bhaobadi khan nisina aru tai khan kun etu kitab laga kotha mani thake. Isor ke mohima dibi!”
Tetiya Tai moike ke koise, “Etu kitab laga PROPHECY aru kotha bon kori nidibi, kelemane homoi tu usorte ahhi ahse.
Kun manu beya pora thaki ahse, tai ke eneka he beya pora thakibole dibo. Kun manu mon letera kori kene thaki ahse, tai ke eneka he thakibole dibi. Kun manu bhal pora thaki ahse, tai aru bhi bisi bhal pora thakibi. Aru kun manu pobitro hoi kene ahse, tai aru bhi bisi pobitro hoi kene thakibi.”
“Sabi! Moi joldi ahhi ahse, aru moi laga enam moi laga hath te ahse, kun ki kam korise eitu hisab dibole nimite.
Moi hai alpha aru omega ahse, PROTHOM aru antim/HEKH bi moi he ahse, suru aru khotom bi moi ase.
Ashirbad ase kun tai laga kapur dhulai kene raki ahse etu pora tai khan moi logote jibon laga ghas khabole paribo aru etu citi te dorja pora ghusibole paribo
Bahar te kuta khan ahse, mangso laga echa kori thaka khan, manu morai diya khan, murti puja kora manu, aru sob manu kun misa tu mani kene morom kori kene thake.
Moi, Jisu sorgoduth khan ke etu kotha khan kobole nimite aru gawahi dibole nimite girja khan te pothai dise. Moi jor ahse aru David laga khandan, ujala phojir laga tara.”
Aatma aru shadi koribole thaka pora koi, “Ahhibi!” Etu nimite kun huni ahse kobi, “Ahhibi!” Kun pyas lagi ahse, tai ke ahhibole dibi kun echa kori ahse, tai khusi pora eitu jibon laga pani lobole dibi.
Moi etu kitab laga PROPHECY sob manu kun etu kotha hunibo tai khan ke gawahi di ahse: Jodi kunba etu kotha te aru bisi kotha dhale, Isor he tai uporte sob dukh khan dhali dibo kun tu etu kitab te likhi kene ahse.
Aru jodi kunba PROPHECY laga kitab te ki likhi kene ahse etu hatai diye, Isor he jibon laga ghas pora tai laga bhag hatai dibo, aru etu pobitrio citi pora bi kuntu laga kotha etu kitab te likhi kene ase.
Kun manu etu sob kotha laga gawahi dibo kobi, “Hoi! Moi joldi hi ahse. “Amen! Ahibi, Probhu Jisu!
Probhu Jisu laga anugrah Tai laga dharmic manu khan logote thakibole dibi. Amen.
